lujvo n1 are instructions by c1 teaching audience c2 ideas/methods/lore c3 (du'u) about subject(s) c4 by method c5 (event). Cf. ctufau, ctucku, cilre.
lujvo n1=c5 is a lecture / an event of verbal teaching by t1=c1 to audience t2 = c2 about subject t3 = c4 in language t4 with facts taught c3. Cf. ctuca, nu, tavla, ckule, cilre.
cmavo CU elidable marker: separates selbri from preceding sumti, allows preceding terminator elision.
cmavo VUhU3 unary mathematical operator: absolute value/norm |a|.
lujvo cm1=cu1 is a member of electorate cm2, which votes/selects cu2 [choice] from set/sequence of alternatives cu3. Gismu deep structure is "cuxna gi'e cmima"; Cf. turni, cmicu'a, gubycu'a, jecta.
lujvo k1=c1 is a gaming die, with sides k3=c3, with side c2 facing up and having dimensions k2. Cf. kelkubli.
cmavo CAI attitudinal: neutral scalar attitude modifier.
cmavo MOI convert number to probability selbri; event x1 has probability (n) of occurring under cond. x2.
cmavo BAI cusku modal, 1st place (attribution/quotation) as said by source ...; used for quotation.
cmavo cluster BAI* tagged sumti: can be used for embedded: it-1 said, "...", with editorial unquote and insert.
lujvo p1 is a businessman/business woman involved in business c1. Cf. cuntu, prenu, kagni, briju, banxa.
lujvo m1 is a skate carrying m2 on surface/medium m3. Cf. carcycutci, bisli, xislu, cucyxelkla, xilcutci, xilcucli'u.
lujvo t1 is the heel of shoe t2=c1 for covering/protecting feet c2, and of material c3. Cf. jmati'e, cucni'a.
lujvo cl1 is barefoot/not wearing shoes. Cf. smoka, karcutci, tupcutci.
lujvo x1=k5 is a roller skate to destination k2 from origin k3 via route k4, transporting x5=k1. Cf. carcycutci, xilcucli'u.

gismu rafsi: cuk x1 is round/circular [2-dimensional shape/form]; x1 is a disk/circle/ring. Normally used for a filled-in circle/disk, but emphasis on roundness means that the concept may include 'ring'. See also djine, ranji, bolci, tarmi.
lujvo l1 goes/moves around/[in a circle] using means l3. Cf. cukla, litru.
lujvo v4=m1=c1 is a computer disk/hard disk/floppy disk storing v2 (data/facts/du'u) about v3 (object/event) in file(s) v1. Cf. vreji, datni, skami, makyvelvei, srimakyvelvei, cukmirvelvei.
lujvo v4=m1=c1 is a compact disc/optical disc storing v2 (data/facts/du'u) about v3 (object/event) in file(s) v1. Cf. vreji, datni, skami, cukmakyvelvei, cukyku'ovelvei, srimakyvelvei.
lujvo m1=c1 (object) is completely round/full. Cf. mluni, lunra, nicte.
lujvo j1 plays ultimate frisbee against j2 in competition j3 for prize/title j4. See also cukla, renro, kavbu, jivna.

gismu rafsi: cku x1 is a book containing work x2 by author x3 for audience x4 preserved in medium x5. [x1 is a manifestation/container A physical object or its analogue. of a work/content, not necessarily using paper (= selpapri)]; See also cfika, prina, prosa, tcidu, papri.
lujvo t1=c1 is a circle. Cf. cukmirvelvei.
lujvo v4=g2=c1 is a compact disc/optical disc storing v2 (data/facts/du'u) about v3 (object/event) in file(s) v1. Cf. cukmirvelvei, vreji, datni, skami, cukmakyvelvei, cukyku'ovelvei, srimakyvelvei.
lujvo v4 is a gramophone record of v2. Cf. cukmirvelvei, zgike, sance, snaveitci, srimakyvelvei.
lujvo x1 is a compass for drawing circles x2. Cf. makfartci, caltaicmaci.
lujvo cp1 humbly asks for/implores cp2 from cp3 in manner/form cp4. Cf. pikci, tolcumla.
gismu rafsi: clu x1 is full/completely filled with x2. See also tisna, kunti, mulno, setca, tisna.
gismu rafsi: cum cu'i x1 (event/state/property) is possible under conditions x2; x1 may/might occur; x1 is a maybe. Also possibility. See also lakne.
gismu rafsi: cul x1 is humble/modest about x2 (abstraction); x1 displays humility about x2. See also cinmo, jgira.
lujvo n1 is a sales lead/opportunity for v1 to sell v2 to v3 for amount v4. Cf. cumki, nu, vecnu, vencu'u, velventerzu'e.
lujvo x1=p2=c1 (subject/concept) is conceivable under conditions c2. Cf. xanri, lojycpa.
lujvo cf1 is science fiction about possible universe cu1=m1 by author cf3. Cf. skefi'a, mi'irlarfi'a.
lujvo k1 gambles/plays the lottery k2. Gambling/lottery = nuncundinkei.
lujvo f1 is shuffled/randomly distributed/cut among f2 with shares/portions f3. Cf. cunfaigau, karda, kelci.
lujvo g1 shuffles/randomly distributes/cuts x2=f1 among x3=f2 with shares/portions x4=f3. Cf. cunfai, karda, kelci.
gismu x1 is a quantity of millet [grain] of species/strain x2. See also gurni.
lujvo p1 bumps into/randomly encounters p2 at/in location p3.

gismu rafsi: cun cu'o x1 is random/fortuitous/unpredictable under conditions x2, with probability distribution x3. Also accidental, chancy, by chance, adventitious, arbitrary (also = cuncu'a, cunselcu'a, cunjdi, cunseljdi; based on "unpredictable"). See also cnici, lakne, funca, kalsa, snuti.

gismu rafsi: cu'u x1 is an affair/organized activity involving person(s) x2 (ind./mass); x1 is x2's business. Also matter, concern; x2 is engaged in x1 (which is usually an abstraction) (= selcu'u for reordered places). See also jikca, srana.
lujvo n1=c1 (li) is a random number (noun), random under conditions c2, with probability distribution c3. Cf. cundinkei, cunfaigau, lakne.
lujvo l1 makes a round trip via route l2 using means/vehicle l3.
gismu rafsi: pra x1 produces x2 [product] by process x3. See also zbasu, farvi, gundi, jukpa.
lujvo p1=c1 is a circularly ordered sequence by rule p2 on unordered set p3. Cf. clupa, porsi.
lujvo c1=f1 is an eel of species/breed c2=f2. Cf. curnu, finpe, xasycurnu.

gismu rafsi: cru x1 (agent) lets/permits/allows x2 (event) under conditions x3; x1 grants privilege x2. Sufficient condition (= crutcini), agent that permits a situation (= tcinycru). See also rinju, banzu, ralte, jimte, jaspu, zifre.

gismu rafsi: cur x1 is a worm/invertebrate animal of species/breed x2. Also mollusk, snail (= cakcurnu), shellfish (= xaskemcakcurnu, xaskemcakydja); the generalization to invertebrate is because many multicellular invertebrates are indeed wormlike. See also since, silka.
gismu rafsi: cuv x1 is pure/unadulterated/unmitigated/simple in property x2 (ka). x1 is simply/purely/unmitigatedly/solely x2. See also prane, jinsa, manfo, sampu, sepli, traji, lumci, xukmi.

gismu rafsi: cus sku x1 (agent) expresses/says x2 (sedu'u/text/lu'e concept) for audience x3 via expressive medium x4. Also says. See also bacru, tavla, casnu, spuda, cmavo list cu'u, bangu, dapma, jufra, pinka.
lujvo x1 edits/revises/adapts text x2 by x3 for audience x4 in medium x5. Cf. cusku, kurji, sa'a.
lujvo z3 is a condition for free expressive activity z2 by agent z1=c1. Cf. nunzi'e.
gismu rafsi: cuc x1 is a shoe/boot/sandal for covering/protecting [feet/hooves] x2, and of material x3. Also boot (= tupcutci). See also smoka, taxfu, skiji.
gismu rafsi: cut x1 is a/the chest/thorax/upper trunk/[rib cage/breast] [body-part] of x2. See also cnebo, betfu, xadni, tanxe.
lujvo b1 is a/the sternum/breastbone of body b3=c2. From greece sternum=chest. See also cutne and srubo'u (=rib).
lujvo g1=c1 is the ribcage of c2. Cf. cutyti'e, cutybo'u.
lujvo t1 is the upper back [body-part] of c2. Cf. cutygreku, cutybo'u, betfu, xadni.

lujvo s1=j1=c1 is bacteriology of bacteria s2 based on methodology s3. Bacteriology is the study of bacteria. Because of the similarity of thinking and working with microorganisms other than bacteria, there has been a tendency for the field of bacteriology to extend as microbiology (=jumske). Bacteriology can be classified as a distinct science.
lujvo j1=c1 is an (eu)bacterium of species/defining property j2. Bacteria are a large domain of single-celled, prokaryote (=pruslemijyji'e) microorganisms. See also jurme, tceprujurme.
gismu rafsi: cux cu'a x1 chooses/selects x2 [choice] from set/sequence of alternatives x3 (complete set). Also prefer (= nelcu'a). See also jdice, pajni, nelci.
lujvo p2=c1 filters p1=c2 to destination side p3 from origin side p4. Cf. julne.
cmavo rafsi: dav dza KOhA1 logically quantified existential pro-sumti: there exists something 1 (usually restricted).
cmavo rafsi: daz PA4 digit/number: all except n; all but n; default 1.
lujvo c1=d2 is a fighting expert in fighting against c2 over issue c3 (abstract), expert by standard c3. Cf. dabytadji.
cmavo cluster MOI* quantified selbri: converts all-but-(1) to ordinal selbri; x1 is penultimate among x2 by rule x3.
cmavo cluster MOI* quantified selbri: converts all-but-2 to ordinal selbri; x1 is antepenult. among x2 by rule x3.
lujvo s1 fight [each other] over issue d3 (abstract). Cf. damba, simxu, simda'a, da'asnu, dausnu, da'arta'a.
lujvo t1=d1 quarrels with t2=d2 about issue t3=d3 in language t4. Cf. damba, tavla, dausnu, da'arsi'u.
lujvo c1 (mass normally, but 1 individual/jo'u possible) argues/quarrels about topic/subject c2=d3 with opponent x3=d2. Cf. darlu, casnu, dausnu, da'arsi'u, simda'a.
cmavo KOhA2 pro-sumti: remote future utterance; "He'll tell you tomorrow. IT will be a doozy.".
cmavo UI3 discursive: supposing - in fact. See also sruma.
cmavo cluster UI*3 discursive: supposing - in fact.
cmavo KOhA2 pro-sumti: a remote past utterance; "She couldn't have known that IT would be true.".
lujvo c1 is armor around c2 composed of c3 against opponent x4=d2. Cf. gunta, jamna, danti, jakne, xarci.
lujvo f1 (event) is a wargame, simulating combat by d1 against d2 over issue d3 (abstract). Cf. jamna, bilni.
lujvo t1 is a fighting technique / martial art used under conditions t3 by d1. t2 subsumed. d2 and d3 not usually relevant to technique. Made from damba + tadji.
gismu rafsi: dac x1 is a drawer/file in structure x2, a [sliding compartment] container for contents x3. See also nilce, tanxe.
gismu rafsi: dai x1 is a material object enduring in space-time; x1 is a thing. See also marji, xanri.
lujvo g1 hangs/suspends d1 from d2 with/by means d3.
gismu rafsi: daj x1 pertains to the Taoist culture/ethos/religion in aspect x2. See also lijda, jegvo.
lujvo t1 is a necktie for wearing by t2=c2 serving purpose t3. Cf. nebysrijge.
lujvo c1 hangs/lynches c2=d1 by hanging them from/on d2 by means of d3. x2 is killed by this action. Use dadgau if x2 is already dead.
lujvo c1=d1 is a hammock of material c2 hung from d2. Cf. daklycka.
lujvo s1=d1 is a pendulum oscillating at rate/frequency s2, suspended from d2 by/at/with joint d3.
lujvo c1 (agent) answers x2=d1 to question/problem x3=d2.
lujvo s1 is pavement of road/highway x2=d1.
lujvo s1 is a road sign meaning s2 to observer/driver/pedestrian s3. Cf. klaji, tcita.
cmavo UI5 attitudinal modifier: marks empathetic use of preceding attitudinal; shows another's feelings. See also cnijmi.
gismu rafsi: dak x1 is a knife (tool) for cutting x2, with blade of material x3. See also denci, balre, katna, tunta, forca, smuci, kinli.
gismu x1 is a sack/bag with contents x2, and of material x3. See also daski for pouch, bakfu.
lujvo c1=d1 is a sleeping bag of material c2=d3 for holding c3=d2. Cf. dadycka.
lujvo x1=d1 is a dagger / knife weapon for use against x2=d2 by x3 with blade of material d3. Cf. dakfu, xarci, cladakyxa'i, damba, catra, zekri.
lujvo c1 is a ranch at c2, of rancher c3 raising animals c4=d1. Cf. danlu, cange, jipci, bakni, xarju, ladru, sovda.
lujvo p1=d1 is a pet belonging to p2 of species d2. Cf. danlu, pendo.
lujvo s1 is zoology concerned with animals of type d2 based on methodology s3. Cf. mivyske, mivdalmuzga, mrodalmuzga, spaske.

gismu rafsi: dab da'a x1 fights/combats/struggles with x2 over issue x3 (abstract); x1 is a fighter/combatant. Use x3 tu'a for fight over an object/objective. See also bradi, gunta, talsa, darlu, fapro, jamna, sonci.
gismu x1 is a drum/cymbal/gong [percussion musical instrument] with beater/actuator x2. See also rilti, zgike.
lujvo t1 is a chimney made of of material t2 for emitting/expelling smoke/gas/steam/magma t3=d1 from source d2. Cf. tubnu, danmo, fanri, molki.
lujvo t1 is a chimney made of of material t2 for emitting/expelling smoke/gas/steam/magma t3=d1 from source d2. Cf. tubnu, danmo, fanri, molki.
lujvo v1 smokes/inhales v2. v1 is a smoker. not necessarily tobacco. Cf. danmo, vasxu. See also tankyva'u, sigva'u, marnyva'u.
gismu rafsi: dad x1 hangs/dangles/is suspended from x2 by/at/with joint x3. Pendant (= dadja'i); also dependent (original meaning). See also lasna, jorne.
gismu rafsi: daf x1 is the answer/response/solution/[reply] to question/problem x2. (cf. ciksi, frati, preti, nabmi, spuda for agentive response/reply, cpedu)
gismu rafsi: dal da'u x1 is an animal/creature of species x2; x1 is biologically animate. See also banfi, cinki, cipni, finpe, jukni, respa, since, mabru, bakni.
lujvo p1 is a trajectory of ballistic projectile d1 fired by gun/launcher d2, to destination p2 from p3 via p4. Cf. vofli, voikla, gunta.
gismu rafsi: dam x1 is made of/contains/is a quantity of smoke/smog/air pollution from source x2. x2 may be a fire. See also pulce, gapci, sigja, bumru.
gismu rafsi: da'e x1 (force) puts pressure on/presses/applies force to x2. Agentive press/depress (= da'ergau, da'erzu'e). See also catke, bapli, prina, tinsa.
fu'ivla x1 pertains to Denmark/Danish culture/nationality/language is aspect x2
lujvo s1 is ballistics with methodology s2. Cf. cecla, danlu'a.
gismu x1 (individual, mass) dances to accompaniment/music/rhythm x2. See also bende, zgike, zajba.
lujvo c1 is a dance/ball involving participants c2=d1, to accompaniment/music/rhythm d2. Cf. dansu, cuntu, zgike, salci, jikca.
gismu rafsi: dan x1 is a ballistic projectile [e.g. bullet/missile] for firing by [gun/propelling launcher] x2. Also cannonball, catapult stone, shot pellet(s). See also cecla, renro, jakne.
lujvo x1 is a quiver/magazine for arrows/bullets x2.
gismu rafsi: plu x1 is an island/atoll/key of [material/properties] x2 in surroundings/body x3; x1 is insular. See also lalxu, rirxe, xamsi, dirgo.
gismu rafsi: dap x1 curses/damns/condemns x2 to fate (event) x3. Curse with a specific expression (= dapsku). See also mabla, dimna, cnemu, sfasa, dunda, cusku, cirko, jdima, di'ai.
fu'ivla x1 is an armadillo of species/breed x2. Cf. mabru, foldota.
lujvo t1=d2 is a hell/cursed territory cursed by t2=d1. Cf. pacraistu, pacruxtutra, ceirselxa'u, ceizda, lijda.
lujvo b1 carries/hauls/bears/transports cargo b2 far away to b3=d1 from b4=d2 over path b5. Cf. darno, bevri.
lujvo b1 carries/hauls/bears/transports cargo b2 far away to b3=d1 from b4=d2 over path b5. Cf. darno, bevri.
lujvo t1 is a telescope for examining c2=d1 which is far from d2. Cf. darvistci, cmactatci, le'otci.
lujvo du1=da1 is too far/distant from da2 in property da3 (ka) by the standard of du3. Cf. darno, dukse.
gismu rafsi: dag x1 is a road/highway to x2 from x3 with route x4 (x2/x3 may be unordered). A regularly used, improved-for-use surface for travelling. See also naxle, tcana, pluta, klaji.
lujvo j1=d1 is the end of j2 at j3 far from d2
gismu rafsi: dau x1 argues for stand x2 against stand x3; [an opponent is not necessary]. See also fapro, jamna, sarji, talsa, sumti, tugni, casnu, damba, bradi, tavla.
lujvo z1=d1 is farther from z2=d2 in property z3=d3 by amount z4. Cf. darno, zmadu.
gismu rafsi: dar da'o x1 is far/distant from x2 in property x3 (ka). See also jibni.
lujvo p1 long jumps to p2 from p3 reaching height p4. Cf. darpi'ejvi, xadyplijvi, zajba.
lujvo j1=p1 long jumps with opponent(s) j2 in contest/competition j3 (event) for gain j4. Cf. darpi'e, xadyplijvi, zajba.
gismu x1 shows audacity/chutzpah in behavior x2 (event/activity); x1 dares to do/be x2 (event/ka). x1 is bold. See also virnu.
lujvo s1=d1 stays/keeps back with s2, distant from d2. Cf. darno, stali.
lujvo x1 encourages x2 to do/be x3. Cf. darsi, gasnu, e'e.
lujvo z1=d1 becomes bolder/more audacious in behaviour d2 (event/activity) by amount z3. Cf. darsi, zenba.
lujvo t1 is a telescope for seeing v2=d1 which is far from d2. Cf. darno, viska, vistci, darctatci, cmactatci, le'otci, barkalyle'o.
gismu rafsi: dax da'i x1 hits/strikes/[beats] x2 with instrument [or body-part] x3 at locus x4. See also bikla, gunta, jenca, tunta, tikpa, janli, jgari, pencu.
gismu x1 is a pocket/pouch of/in garment/item x2. See also dakli, taxfu, bakfu.
lujvo b1 is a handkerchief of type/material b2 in pocket x3=d1. For example worn in suit front pockets. Cf. zbibu'u.
lujvo c1=da1 is a Pokémon/Pocket Monster of species da2
lujvo x1=c1 is a koala (Phascolarctos cinereus) of breed x2=c2
lujvo m1 is a marsupial mammal of species m2. Cf. daski, mabru, daskycribe, kanguru.
gismu rafsi: das x1 wears/is robed/garbed in x2 as a garment of type x3. x2 need not be intended for use as a garment (unlike taxfu). See also taxfu.
gismu rafsi: spo x1 (event) destroys/ruins/wrecks/despoils x2; x1 is destructive. See also spofu, xrani, marxa, zalvi, xaksu.
gismu rafsi: sri x1 is a ribbon/tape/strip/band/stripe of material x2. See also djine.
lujvo x1=t2 is a cross-dresser/transvestite wearing dress/garment/clothing x2=t1 serving purpose t3. Cf. cingafpre, palku, pastu, dadne'ota'u.
lujvo c1=d1 is an alias/nickname of c2 used by c3 instead of name d2, differing from it by standard d3. Cf. drata, cmene, cmebasti.
gismu x1 is a duck/[drake] of species/breed x2. See also cipni.
lujvo p1 is eiderdown/feather/plume of duck species/breed d2. Cf. datka, gunse, cipni, kicne, ranti.

lujvo z1=d1 is a plurality of/more than all other subgroups of z2 as seperated/classified by property z3=d3 by amount z4. Made from drata + zmadu. Seems like both this and xabmau should have klesi in them, but it can be argued that the combination imports the idea of classification. See also xabmau.
gismu x1 (du'u) [fact/measurement] is data/information/statistic(s) about x2 gathered by method x3. Evidence (= velji'i datni or just velji'i, sidydatni). See also fatci, saske, vreji.
lujvo x1 is a pipe carrying data x2 to x3 from x4. Cf. datnyxle, skami.
lujvo n1=d1 is a report about n2=d2 from reporter n3 to intended audience n4. Cf. datni, notci, djuno, nuzba, lanli.

lujvo x1=das1 is a signal recording and playback tape-type medium (cassette/DAT/tape drive) containing data/sound/image x2=dat1 with data storage mechanism/method x3 (analog/digital) Cf. srimakyvelvei, veisri.
lujvo v1 is a computer variable/register/memory cell with contents v2=d1. Cf. datnyvaugunma, skami.
lujvo g1 is computer memory, consisting of parts x2=g2=v1. Cf. datnyvau, skami.
lujvo x1=v1 is a file consisting of information x2=d1=v2 about x3=d2=v3 in medium x4=v4. Cf. datnyveiste, skami.
lujvo l1=v1 is a directory of files l2 in order l3 in medium l4=v4. Cf. datnyvei, skami, ckusro.
lujvo n1 is a socket connecting n3 to n2 along route n4 carrying data x5=d1. x1 is the end opened with listen(); Cf. datnyfle.
lujvo v1 is a tourist/foreign visitor, visiting v2 at place/event v3 from country x4=g1. Cf. litru, klama.
lujvo c1 debate on topic/subject c2. Cf. darlu, casnu, da'asnu, simda'a, da'arsi'u, da'arta'a.
lujvo f1=d1 fails to hit d2 with instrument d3 at locus d4. Cf. fliba, darxi.
cmavo KOhA1 logically quantified existential pro-sumti: there exists something 2 (usually restricted).
cmavo ZAhO event contour for a temporary halt and ensuing pause in a process.
cmavo KOhA2 pro-sumti: a near future utterance.
fu'ivla x1 is denim of material x2. Cf. bukpu.
cmavo BAI detri modal, 1st place (for letters) dated ... ; attaches date stamp.
cmavo VUhU3 binary mathematical operator: logarithm; [log/ln a to base b]; default base 10 or e.
lujvo x1 is a jicama of species/variety x2. Cf. samcu, dembi.

gismu rafsi: dec x1 is a tenth [1/10; 1*10^{-1}] of x2 in dimension/aspect x3 (default is units). (cf. grake, mitre, snidu, stero, delno, molro, kelvo, xampo, gradu. litce, merli, centi, dekto, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, xexso, zepti, zetro)
lujvo j1 is a ring on finger j2=d1. Cf. djine, jadypijne.
lujvo j1=d3 points to j2 (property) to audience j3 with finger x4=d1. Cf. farja'o, farsni.
gismu rafsi: deg x1 is a/the finger/digit/toe [body-part] on limb/body site x2 of body x3; [metaphor: peninsula]. Finger (= xandegji), toe (= jmadegji). See also nazbi, tamji, tance, xance.,
lujvo g1=c1=d2 is a mitten of material g2. Cf. gluta.
lujvo c1 is a knuckle on limb d2 of body c3=d3. Cf. bircidni.
lujvo l1=d3 plucks l2 at locus l3. For example also pizzicato etc.
lujvo g1 is a thimble. Cf. degji, gacri, tajgai.
lujvo g1 is g2 inch/inches (length unit). Cf. degji, gutci, jmagutci, cibjmagutci, birgutci, minli.
lujvo p1 is a fingerprint on surface p2 made by finger/toe p3=d1
gismu rafsi: dej x1 owes x2 in debt/obligation to creditor x3 in return for x4 [service, loan]; x1 is a debtor. See also jbera, janta, zivle.
lujvo n1 is an invoice/bill to debtor d1=n4 for amount owed d2 to creditor d3=n3 for goods/services d4. Cf. dejni, notci, janta.
lujvo s1=d1 wagers d2 to creditor d3 on s2 (du'u). Cf. sruma, smadi, kanpe.
lujvo z3 is the interest on debt z1=d2 of debtor d1 to creditor d3. Cf. dejni, zenba, terdejni, kagyseldejni, ze'i zei seldejni, ze'u zei seldejni, paurseldejni, fairprali, jbera, jdini, banxa.

gismu x1 is x2 (default 1) local volume unit(s) [non-metric; e.g. bushel], standard x3, x4 subunits. Gallon (= likydekpu), quart (= likseldekpu), barrel (wet = likybradekpu, dry = sudbradekpu), bushel (= sudydekpu), peck (= sudyseldekpu), cupful (= kabrydekpu), tablespoon (= mucydekpu); teaspoon (= mucyseldekpu); (all of these lujvo may need gic- to distinguish the English measurement system in contrasting with some local system; the English system is otherwise presumed to be the default non-metric system). (additional subunit places may be added as x5, x6, ...); See also canlu, litce, rupnu, fepni, gutci, minli, merli, bunda, kramu.

gismu rafsi: dek x1 is ten [10; 1*10^1] of x2 in dimension/aspect x3 (default is units). See also grake, mitre, snidu, stero, delno, molro, kelvo, xampo, gradu, litce, merli, centi, decti, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, xexso, zepti, zetro
fu'ivla x1 is a dolphin of species/breed x2. Cf. mabru, xamsi, flecu.

gismu rafsi: del de'o x1 is x2 candela [metric unit] in luminosity (default is 1) by standard x3. See also centi, decti, dekto, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, xexso, zepti, zetro.
gismu rafsi: deb x1 is a bean/pea/leguminous seed from plant [legume] x2. See also grute, sobde, tsiju.
fu'ivla x1 is a garbanzo/chickpea of species/variety x2. see also boldembi
lujvo c1=d1 pours to c2 from c3. c1=d1 is torrential rainfall.
lujvo r1 (event/state) compacts/compresses/concentrates/packs/condenses x2=d1 in property x3=d2 (ka) at location/locus x4=d3. Cf. lunsa.
lujvo d1=s1 is a bush of species/strain/cultivar s2. Cf. dzitricu.
lujvo z1 crouches/cowers/squats on surface z2. Cf. cidytse, mipypu'i, dzibi'o, krosa'i.
lujvo b1 is a toothbrush with bristles b3. Cf. denjisygau, denpesxu, brulu'i.
gismu rafsi: den de'i x1 is a/the tooth [body-part] of x2; (adjective:) x1 is dental. (for metaphor: see dakfu, pagre, jgalu); See also moklu, dakfu, pagre, jgalu, batci, bongu.
lujvo c1=d2 has a toothache in tooth d1=c2.
lujvo g1 (agent) brushes/cleans the teeth of d2. Cf. denburcu, denpesxu, denmikce.
gismu rafsi: dem x1 is dense/concentrated/packed/intense in property x2 (ka) at location/locus x3. See also carmi, midju, viknu.
lujvo m1 is a dentist treating patient m2 with dentistry m4. Cf. densrumikce.

gismu rafsi: dep de'a x1 awaits/waits/pauses for/until x2 at state x3 before starting/continuing x4 (activity/process). (x2 is an event, usually a point event); also: resuming x4. See also dicra, fanmo, sisti, fliba, pandi.
lujvo p1 is a quantity of tooth-paste, of composition p2. Cf. denburcu, denjisygau.
lujvo x1 is the gum/cementum of animal x2. Cf. densrumikce.
lujvo m1 is a periodontist treating patient(s) m2 for ailment m3 involving cure m4. Cf. denmikce, densru.
lujvo s1=d2 is a zip fastener for sealing s2 by mechanism d1. Cf. stela, tolfendi.
lujvo c1 feels patience about c3. Cf. o'o.
lujvo k1 is a waiting room/break room in structure x2 surrounded by partitions/walls/ceiling/floor x3 (mass/jo'u). Cf. depypoi, depstu.
lujvo x1 causes x2 to wait for x3 at x4 before continuing x5. Cf. sisti.
lujvo s1 is a hesitation sound produced by s2=d1 while for/until d2 at state d3 before starting/continuing d4 (activity/process). Cf. denpa, sance, y.
lujvo s1 is a waiting room/place where d1 waits for d2. Cf. depkumfa.
lujvo x1 is the Lojban dot character
lujvo j1=d1 is patient, unyielding to force j2=d2 under condition j3=d3. Cf. jdari, denpa, tinsa, xarnu.
lujvo p1 is a waiting queue ordered by rules p2 on unordered set p3 waiting for x4=d2. Cf. depkumfa, depstu.
lujvo b1 initially grows b2 beyond the soil; b1 sprouts b2 from the ground. dertu+banro
lujvo x1 is a peanut of variety x2.
lujvo j1 sprouts from x2=d1. Cf. spati, banro.
lujvo d1=p1 is a quantity of mud of composition d3=p2, made from dirt from source d2 Water soaked soil, soft wet earth. See also dertu, pesxu
lujvo s1 buries/sinks/embeds s2 in ground s3=d1. Cf. lolni'apu'i, lolni'a.

lujvo s1=d1 is soil science [science about earth/soil] based on methodology s3. dertu2, dertu3 and saske2 subsumed. Soil science studies the soil that occupies the pedosphere, one of Earth's spheres. This is not the same as geology (the lujvo for this should mean planetary+composition+science). The two main branches of soil science are pedology (=terderske; the study of soil in its natural setting) and edaphology (the study of soil in relation to soil-dependent uses). See also tedske, rokske and kunske.

gismu rafsi: der de'u x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of dirt/soil/earth/ground from source x2 of composition x3. Also: x1 is earthen; x3: composition including x3, which need not be exhaustive of composition. See also kliti, terdi, loldi.
gismu rafsi: dre x1 is a heap/pile/stack/mound/hill of materials x2 at location x3. See also cmana.

gismu rafsi: des x1 shakes/quakes/trembles/quivers/shudders/wobbles/vibrates from force x2. Also (expressible either with desku or slilu): side to side, to and fro, back and forth, reciprocal motion. See also slilu, janbe.

lujvo m1 is a vibrator/vibrating device for use/function m2. not necessarily sex toy; could for example also be a "Jumping Jack" compactor; Cf. runpinji, gletci. See xremi'i for shaking machines with the purpose of mixing.
lujvo g1 (person/agent) shakes x2=d1. Cf. desku, gasnu, desyzu'e, slilu.
lujvo z1 shakes. Cf. desku, zukte, desygau, slilu.
lujvo x1 is a calendar showing dates x2 and events x3. x2 is normally a time interval; see detci'e
lujvo x1 is a calendar with rules x2, days/weeks/months/years x3, and properties x4. e.g. Gregorian calendar, Hebrew calendar; see detcartu
lujvo x1 allows copying/has copyright of x2 under conditions x3 dated x4.
lujvo k1 is the k3'rd anniversary (date recurrence) of event k2=d1 that took place at location d3 by calendar d4. Cf. detri, krefu.
fu'ivla x1 is the date [day,{week},{month},year] of event/state x2, at location x3, by the Gregorian calendar.

gismu rafsi: det x1 is the date [day,{week},{month},year] of event/state x2, at location x3, by calendar x4. (time units in x1 are specified as numbers separated by pi'e or are unit values massified with joi); See also cmavo list de'i, djedi, jeftu, masti, nanca, tcika.
lujvo g1 schedules time t1[hours, {minutes}, {seconds}] and date d1[day,{week},{month},year] for event t2=d2 at location d3. Cf. detri, tcika, gasnu, tcikygau, tcikyga'i, bavypunji, prupu'i.
cmavo KOhA1 logically quantified existential pro-sumti: there exists something 3 (usually restricted).
cmavo ZAhO event contour for resumption of a paused process.
cmavo TAhE tense interval modifier: regularly; subjective tense/modal; defaults as time tense.
cmavo cluster TAhE* tense interval modifier: irregularly/aperiodically; tense/modal; defaults as time tense.
cmavo BAI diklo modal, 1st place at the locus of ...
lujvo z1 is/are the foundation(s) of building/edifice/structure d1 of/for type/purpose d2, made of/with materials/properties z3. Cf. dinju, zbepi.
lujvo t1=d1 is dearest/most precious to d2 among set/range x3=t4.
lujvo f1=d1 is an electrical current / flow in / on / through f2 = d2 flowing in direction to / towards f3 from direction/source f4. Cf. dicflecru, dicka'u. dicka3 is not sensical.

lujvo c1 is a transistor / electrical regulator which allows electric current c2 = df1 to flow under conditions c3 in / on / through df2 flowing in direction to / towards df3 from direction/source df4. Cf. dicfle, dicka'u.
lujvo x1 is an electron. Cf. lektoni, dicfle.
gismu rafsi: dir x1 (event) interrupts/stops/halts/[disrupts] x2 (object/event/process) due to quality x3. Also disturbs (one sense). See also zunti, fanza, raktu, denpa.
lujvo g3=d2 is an electric lamp illuminating g2 with light g1. Cf. dikca, gusni, rastergu'i, laktergu'i, fagytergu'i.
lujvo d1=c1 is electrically uncharged. Cf. seldikca
lujvo s2 is a loudspeaker emitting sound s1. Cf. snaveitci.
lujvo s1 is a battery in containment s3.
lujvo k1 is a dropstone/stalagmite/stalactite/icicle/rusticle of material k2=s2=d2. Cf. bakri, kevna, bogjinme.
lujvo p1 is a plaza managed by community/polity/company p2 for purpose p3.
lujvo s1 is a story/level/floor of building x2=s3=d1.

gismu rafsi: dic x1 is electricity [electric charge or current] in/on x2 of polarity/quantity x3 (def. negative). (x3, a quantifier, can be expressed as a simple polarity using the numerals for positive and negative ma'u and ni'u); (explicitly) negative (= dutydikca), positive (= mardikca); current (= (sel)muvdikca; again default negative/electron current), charge (= klodikca, stadikca). See also lindi, xampo, flecu, maksi, tcana.
lujvo c1 consumes c2 as part of their staple diet.
lujvo p1 regularly pays salary p2 to p3 for goods/services p4.

gismu rafsi: klo x1 is local to x2; x1 is confined to locus x2 within range x3; x1 is regional Indicates a specific location/value within a range; e.g. a hits b. What is the locality on b that a hits? Thus x1 is associated with a specific narrow region/interval x2 of wider space/range x3. See also cmavo list di'o, jibni, zvati, cpana, nenri, lamji, stuzi, tcila.
gismu rafsi: dik x1 is regular/cyclical/periodic in property (ka)/activity x2 with period/interval x3. Also uniform; resonant (= dikslicai). See also slilu, rilti, xutla, manfo, boxna.
gismu x1 is a quotient of 'x2/x3' [dividend x2 divided by divisor x3], leaving remainder x4. See also frinu, fendi, katna, parbi, mekso.
gismu rafsi: dil x1 is a cloud/mass of clouds of material x2 in air mass x3 at floor/base elevation x4. See also carvi, tcima.
gismu rafsi: dim x1 is a fate/destiny of x2; [doom, curse are mabla-forms]; x2 is fated/predestined/doomed to x1. Fated/destined/doomed (= seldimna). See also dapma.
lujvo c1 is a monetary affair involving c2
lujvo jb1 borrows money jb2=jd1 from jb3 for interval jb4. Cf. jdini, jbera, seldejni, dejyterze'a.
gismu rafsi: dij di'u x1 is a building/edifice for purpose x2. See also ginka, zdani, zarci.
gismu rafsi: di'o x1 is a nail/tack [pointed driven/frictional fastener] of type/size x2 (ka), made of material x3. (x2 also can be ni abstraction); See also pijne, lasna.
fu'ivla x1 is a rivet of type x2 made of x3
fu'ivla x1 is a dinosaur of type x2 living in era x3.
lujvo g1 is a/the industry sector in which s1 provides financial services g2=s3 to s2 by process g3 From jdini, selfu, gundi. Omit j2.
lujvo s1 is a treasury of money d1=s2.
lujvo c1 is a/the financial management function/activities involving persons c2=ji1, of money/currency issued by jd2; c1 is finance. Cf. jdini, jitro, cuntu, dinveicu'u, janta.

lujvo c1 is an/the accounting function/activities involving persons c2, using currency issued by j2, recording v2 (data/facts/du'u) about v3 (object/event); c1 is accounting. Cf. jdini, vreji, cuntu, dintrocu'u, janta.

gismu rafsi: dib x1 is dear/precious/darling to x2; x1 is emotionally valued by x2. x1 may be a specific object, a commodity (mass), an event, or a property; pedantically, for objects/commodities, this is sumti-raising from ownership of the object/commodity (= posydirba for unambiguous semantics). See also tcika, kargu, vamji, vajni, pleji, jadni, jemna.
gismu rafsi: di'e x1 radiates/emits x2 under conditions x3. See also gusni.
lujvo x1 is radium. see also dircynavni
gismu rafsi: dig x1 is a drop [small, cohesive shape] of material [liquid/vapor] x2 in surrounding material x3. See also daplu, bidju.
lujvo t1 is an interrupt causing d1 to happen, interrupting d2 due to quality d3, hooked onto conditions t3.
lujvo v1 chokes on/because of d3. Cf. dicra, vasxu, vaxydicra.

gismu rafsi: diz dzi x1 is low/down/downward in frame of reference x2 as compared with baseline/standard height x3. Also lower; x3 is generally some defined distance above a zero point/baseline, or is that baseline itself. See also cnita, galtu, gapru, farna, loldi.
fu'ivla d1 is jazz music performed at/by z2 (event) with characteristics z3. Cf. te'ekno, naizgi, sopselneizgi, nolzgi.
lujvo b1 is a waiter, carrying food c1=b2 to b3 from b4 over path b5.
lujvo p1=b1 is a waitress/waiter serving food b2=c1 to x3=c2=b3. Cf. barjyse'u.
lujvo m1=c2 starves to death from lack of food/nutrition c1
lujvo cip1=cid1 is an edible bird of species cip2. Cf. jipci, gunse, datka, xruki.
gismu rafsi: jac jau x1 is made of/contains/is a quantity/expanse of water; (adjective:) x1 is aqueous/[aquatic]. Aquatic (= jaupli). See also lalxu, rirxe, xamsi, limna, litki, lumci, bumru, jinto.
lujvo g1=c1 is grain from plant/species g2, edible/giving nutrition to x3=c2. Cf. bavmi, cunmi, mavji, maxri, mraji, rismi, zumri, sorgu.
lujvo r1=c1 (food) is digested in solvent r2. Cf. djaruntygau, djaruntyrango.
lujvo g1=c2 digests food x2=r1=c1 in solvent x3=r2. Cf. djarunta, djaruntyrango.
lujvo ra1 is a stomach/digestive organ of body/species ra2=c2 for digesting food/feed/nutriment x3=ru1=c1. Cf. djarunta, djaruntygau.
lujvo x1=cr2 is a crop/harvest, harvested by x2=cr1, for use as food x3=ci1, to be eaten by x4=ci2.
lujvo s1 is a morsel/piece of food s1=c1 for x3=c2.
fu'ivla g1 is g2 joule(s) of energy (default is 1) by standard g3. Cf. Cf. klanrdjuli, klanrniut,ni, klanrxuati.

gismu rafsi: dje dei x1 is x2 full days in duration (default is 1 day) by standard x3; (adjective:) x1 is diurnal. Today (= cabdei); tomorrow (= bavlamdei); yesterday (= prulamdei). See also donri, detri, jeftu, masti, nanca, nicte, tcika.
lujvo k1 is a daily newspaper with content k2 published by k3 for audience k4.

gismu rafsi: dji x1 desires/wants/wishes x2 (event/state) for purpose x3. If desire is for an object, this is sumti-raising; use tu'a in x2 (or use lujvo = po'edji). See also taske, xagji, mukti, nitcu, nelci, pacna, prami, rigni, trina, xebni, xlura.
lujvo c1=d1 is/feels eager for d2 =c3 (event/state) for purpose d3. Cf. djica, cinmo, sutydji.

gismu rafsi: jin x1 is a ring/annulus/torus/circle [shape/form] of material x2, inside diam. x3, outside diam. x4. Also ellipse, oval (= jincla); (usage has been for near-circles, such as tight spirals, even if not closed loops). Also band, belt, encircle (= jinsru). See also clupa, cukla, dasri, karli, sovda, sruri, konju.

lujvo x1=d1=c1 wants to say/express x2=c2 (sedu'u/text/lu'e concept) for audience x3=c3 via expressive medium x4=c4, and this is desired for purpose x5=d3. Generally used to correct another's perceived mistake, i.e. "mi klami" followed by ".i pe'i du djisku zo klama". See also djica, cusku.
lujvo m1=b1 is the Saudi Arabic language used by b2 to express/communicate b3 (si'o/du'u, not quote). Cf. sadjo, bangu, rabybau, bangaru'a, bangarubu.
fu'ivla x1 is a quantity of yogurt made from x2 milk by process x3. Cf. ladru, cirla, kruji.
lujvo x1=g1=s1 is happy/merry/gay about helping/assisting/aiding object/person x2=s2 to do/achieve/maintain event/activity x3=s3 cf. gleki and sidju

gismu rafsi: jun ju'o x1 knows fact(s) x2 (du'u) about subject x3 by epistemology x4. Words usable for epistemology typically have a du'u place; know how to - implying knowledge of method but not necessarily having the ability to practice (= tadjyju'o). (cf. know/familiar with: se slabu, na'e cnino, na'e fange; cmavo list du'o, cilre, certu, facki, jijnu, jimpe, senpi, smadi, kakne, birti, mipri, morji, saske, viska)
lujvo n1 is an instruction/advice from x2=n3 to help/assist/aid x3=s2=n4 do/achieve/maintain event/activity x4=s3.
lujvo c1=s1 gives advice c2 (sedu'u/text/lu'e concept) to c3=s2 about doing/achieving/maintaining s3, on medium c4. Cf. sidju, cusku.
cmavo rafsi: don doi KOhA3 pro-sumti: you listener(s); identified by vocative.
cmavo UI3 discursive: generously - parsimoniously. See also dunda.
cmavo KOhA3 pro-sumti: you the listener & others unspecified.
cmavo DOhU elidable terminator: end vocative (often elidable).
cmavo DOI generic vocative marker; identifies intended listener; elidable after COI.
cmavo cluster DOI* generic vocative address to intended listener;.
lujvo c1 is a second person pronoun in language c4. Cf. do, do'o, cmavo, mibma'o.
gismu rafsi: dor do'i x1 is the daytime of day x2 at location x3; (adjective:) x1 is diurnal (vs. nocturnal). See also nicte, djedi, tcika.
fu'ivla x1 is a gazelle of species x2. see also bajbakni, antilope
lujvo m1 is the noon (midday) of day d2 at location d3. djemidju is too vague. Cf. donri, midju, ctemidju.
lujvo b1 is later than noon of day d2 at location d3. donri+midju+balvi; see also vanci, lerci, cerni, nicte, dormidju, lecydo'i
lujvo s1 (mass) is a lunch composed of dishes including s2. Cf. cersai, vacysai, dormidju, sanmi.
gismu rafsi: dot do'o x1 reflects German/Germanic culture/nationality/language in aspect x2. See also ropno.
lujvo d1=b1 is the German used by b2 to express/communicate b3 (si'o/du'u, not quote). Cf. dotco, bangu, bandu'e'u.
lujvo g1 is Germany. Cf. dotco, gugde, gugdedu'e.
gismu x1 is a drama/play about x2 [plot/theme/subject] by dramatist x3 for audience x4 with actors x5. x2 may also be a convention. See also finti, cukta, lisri, cfika.
lujvo di1 is a theater for performing plays with theme di2=dr2 for audience x3=dr4 with actors x4=dr5. Cf. tsina, tigni.

lujvo x1=d1=k1 is a role-player / player of role playing game / RPG / LARP or dramatic / acting game x2=d5=k2 about x3=d2 created by author/ company x4=d3 for audience x5=d4. Audience defaults to the players themselves. See also draci, kelci, dracyselkei.

lujvo x1=d1=sk1 is a role-playing game/ RPG/ LARP or dramatic/ acting game played by performer(s)/ player(s) x2=d5=sk2 about x3=d2 created by author/ company x4=d3 for audience x5=d4 . Audience defaults to the players themselves. See also draci, kelci, dracykei.
lujvo g1 (event) corrects g2 into g3=d1, correct in property/aspect x4=d2 (ka) in situation x5=d3 by standard x6=d4. Cf. dragau, draga'igau, drari'a.
lujvo g1 (person/agent) corrects d1. Cf. draga'i, drari'a, draga'igau, cusku, fapro, sidju, madysku.
gismu rafsi: dra x1 is correct/proper/right/perfect in property/aspect x2 (ka) in situation x3 by standard x4. See also srera, mapti.
gismu rafsi: dat x1 isn't the-same-thing-as/is different-from/other-than x2 by standard x3; x1 is something else. See also mintu, frica.
lujvo g1 comforts j1=b1 about b2 from badri jdika gasnu
fu'ivla x1 is an albatross [member of the family Diomedeidae] of species/breed x2

gismu rafsi: rud dru x1 is a roof/top/ceiling/lid of x2. (cf. bitmu, stedu, galtu, gapru, loldi, marbi, gacri, mapku; a drudi is (designed to be) over/above something and shelters it from other things above the drudi, mapku)
cmavo rafsi: dub du'o GOhA identity selbri; = sign; x1 identically equals x2, x3, etc.; attached sumti refer to same thing.
cmavo FAhA1 location tense relation/direction; east of.
cmavo cluster MOI* quantifier selbri: convert too many to cardinal selbri; x1 is a set with too many members x2.
cmavo cluster ROI* tense interval modifier: too many times objective tense, defaults as time tense.
cmavo BAI dunli modal, 1st place (equalled by) equally; as much as ...
cmavo BAI djuno modal, 1st place (info source) authoritatively; according to ...; known by ...
cmavo rafsi: dum NU abstractor: predication/bridi abstractor; x1 is predication [bridi] expressed in sentence x2.
gismu rafsi: dug x1 is the logarithm of x2 with base x3. See also tenfa.
lujvo m1 is a freezer/freezing machine for freezing x2=d1 at temperature x3. Cf. lekmi'i, dujyku'a, bisli, lenku, kelvo.
lujvo k1 is a cooling room for cooling x2=d1 at temperature x3=d2. Cf. dujmi'i, lekmi'i.
lujvo r1 (event/state) anguishes/causes distress to x2=d1. Cf. seldu'u.
gismu rafsi: dus du'e x1 is an excess of/too much of x2 by standard x3. Cloying (= maldu'e, tolpu'adu'e). See also bancu, banzu, ricfu, zmadu.
gismu rafsi: dut x1 is polar opposite from/contrary to x2 in property/on scale x3 (property/si'o). See also ranxi, ragve, fatne.

gismu rafsi: dud du'a x1 [donor] gives/donates gift/present x2 to recipient/beneficiary x3 [without payment/exchange]. Also grants; x3 is a receiver (= terdu'a for reordered places); the Lojban doesn't distinguish between or imply possession transfer or sharing; x2 may be a specific object, a commodity (mass), an event, or a property; pedantically, for objects/commodities, this is sumti-raising from ownership of the object/commodity (= posydu'a, posyseldu'a for unambiguous semantics). See also benji, muvdu, canja, pleji, vecnu, friti, sfasa, dapma, cnemu, prali.
gismu rafsi: duj x1 freezes/jells/solidifies at temperature x2 and pressure x3. See also febvi, lunsa, runme, sligu.
gismu rafsi: duk du'u x1 is anguished/distressed/emotionally wrought/stressed by x2. See also fengu, surla.
lujvo x1 is an equivalence class within x2 defined by equivalence relation x3.

gismu rafsi: dun du'i x1 is equal/congruent to/as much as x2 in property/dimension/quantity x3. Same in quantity/quality (not necessarily in identity); 'analogy' may be expressed as the equivalence of two properties of similarity (ka x1 simsa x2) and (ka x3 simsa x4). See also cmavo list du'i, satci, frica, simsa, mintu.
gismu rafsi: dur x1 is winter/wintertime [cold season] of year x2 at location x3. See also citsi, crisa, critu, vensa.
fu'ivla x1 is a douroucouli of species x2. see also smani, kermipri
lujvo x1 is satiated/overwhelmed by x2 with property x3 by standard x4; x2 is too much for x1 in property x3 by standard x4. See also be'unai
lujvo p1 is prejudiced about matter p2 (abstract).
lujvo t1 is exhausted by effort/situation t2 (event).
lujvo c1 is heterosexual/bisexual in situation c2 by standard c4. For strict heterosexuality, see pavdutcinse. Cf. relcinse, mitcinse, nakcinse, fetcinse.
lujvo x1 is the trigonometric cosine of angle/arccosine x2. Cf. sinso, tanjo, selsinso, seltanjo, seldutsinso.
lujvo x1 is October/tenth month of year x2 in calendar x3. Note: Based on experimental rafsi for dau (duv). Use with caution. Alternative: pavnonma'i
lujvo s1=d2=l2 is a conservative in beliefs l3 against opposition s3 by means s4 From dzena, lijda, sarji. Cf. vricykricru, dzejdasratrusi'o.

lujvo si1 is a conservative political ideology as applied by t1=sa1=d2=l2 among/in people/territory/domain t2 based on the works of thinker si3 From dzena, lijda, sarji, turni, sidbo. Cf. dzejdasra, ka'irtrusi'o, vricykricrutrusi'o, fairpaltrusi'o, guntrusi'o, natpamtrusi'o, tsarainaitrusi'o.
lujvo k1 is classical. Cf. dzena, kulnu, nolzgi.
lujvo s1=d1 is Celtic in aspect s2.
gismu rafsi: dze x1 is an elder/ancestor of x2 by bond/tie/degree x3; x1's generation precedes x2's parents. See also patfu, rirni, tamne.
lujvo b1=d1 crouches/squats/hunkers down. Cf. diklo, binxo, krosa'i, demtse.
gismu rafsi: zip zi'o x1 reflects Antarctican culture/nationality/geography in aspect x2. See also ketco, friko, sralo, terdi.
lujvo x1 is a bass instrument (bass guitar, contrabass, bass horn, keyboard bass, washtub bass) of type x2 Possibly also bass drum.
lujvo t1=d1 is a shrub/bush of species t2. Cf. demspa, cmatricu.
fu'ivla x1 is tares of species/variety x2. see also cicyrismi
lujvo g1 is a walking stick of material g2. Cf. cadzu, grana, sarji
lujvo x1 is a walker-come with destination x2 with starting point x3 with route of going x4 with transportation means -walking limb x5 with walked on x6.
lujvo k1=c2 is a footpath at k2 accessing k3. Cf. dargu, pluta, klama.
lujvo p1 is a procession with participation ordered/sequenced by rules p2. Cf. cadzu, porsi.
lujvo s1=c1 is a foot/infantry soldier of army s2. Cf. cadzu, sonci, xirsoi.
cmavo A logical connective: sumti afterthought and.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: granting permission - prohibiting. See also curmi.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: competence - incompetence/inability. See also kakne, certu.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: feeling constraint - independence - challenge/resistance against constraint. See also selri'u, seljimte.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: feeling constraint - independence - challenge/resistance against constraint.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: feeling constraint - independence - challenge/resistance against constraint.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: request - negative request. See also cpedu, pikci.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: request - negative request.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: suggestion - abandon suggest - warning. See also stidi, kajde.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: suggestion - abandon suggest - warning.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: suggestion - abandon suggest - warning.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: obligation - freedom. See also bilga, zifre.
cmavo cluster A* logical connective: sumti afterthought x but not y.
fu'ivla g1 is g2 henry/henries of inductance (default is 1) by standard g3. Cf. klanrxenri, klanrvolta, xampo.
fu'ivla x1 in an enzyme that catalyzes chemical reactions x2. Cf. selfusra, sutri'a.
fu'ivla x1 is a stoat/ermine of subspecies x2. Cf. mustlei, mabrnfuru.
fu'ivla x1 is a hedgehog of species x2. see also jesymabru
fu'ivla x1 is a pike of species/breed x2
fu'ivla g1 is g2 hertz of frequency (default is 1) by standard g3. Cf. klanrxertsi.
fu'ivla x1 is an ester derived from acid x2 and alcohol x3 c.f. xumsle,slami, xalka.
fu'ivla x1 is x2 dunams in area by standard x3 1000 m², except for the Iraqi dunam and the former Turkish dönüm.
cmavo FA sumti place tag: tag 1st sumti place.
cmavo FAhA4 location tense relation/direction; arriving at/directly towards ...
cmavo BAI fatne modal, 1st place backwards; reverse of ...
lujvo g1 inverts/reverses/turns over f1 into f3. Cf. fatne, gasnu.
cmavo VUhU2 unary mathematical operator: reciprocal; multiplicative inverse; [1/a].
lujvo g1 reveals to f1 f2 (du'u) about subject/object f3 from facki gasnu c.f. jarco
cmavo FAhO unconditional end of text; outside regular grammar; used for computer input.

lujvo x1 is the terminator of structure originated by selma'o x2 in language x3. See also fanmo; cmavo; be'o; boi; do'u; fe'u; fu'o; ge'u; ke'e; kei; ku; ku'e; ku'o; le'u; li'u; lo'o; lu'u; me'u; nu'u; se'u; te'u; toi; tu'u; vau; ve'o
cmavo JOI non-logical connective: respectively; unmixed ordered distributed association.
gismu rafsi: fak fa'i x1 discovers/finds out x2 (du'u) about subject/object x3; x1 finds (fi) x3 (object). See also cirko, djuno, jijnu, smadi, sisku.

gismu rafsi: fad x1 [member] is ordinary/common/typical/usual in property x2 (ka) among members of x3 (set). Also: x2 is a normal/common/ordinary/typical property among set x3 (= selterfadni for reordered places); also regular, (mabla forms:) banal, trite, vulgar; (x3 is complete set). See also cafne, rirci, kampu, lakne, tcaci, cnano.
lujvo x1 is Tuesday of week x2 on calendar x3.
lujvo x1 is firethorn of species/variety x2.
lujvo j1 is a fender/firescreen for a fireplace using fuel f2 burning-in/reacting-with oxidizer f3. Cf. fagri, julne.
lujvo f1=c1 is a volcano projecting from land mass c2. Cf. je'erma'a.
gismu rafsi: fag x1 is a fire/flame in fuel x2 burning-in/reacting-with oxidizer x3 (default air/oxygen). See also jelca, sacki.
lujvo r1 kindles f2 in atmosphere f3 under conditions r3
lujvo x1 is a tool for starting fire x2. x1 is a lighter such as for cigarettes. Cf. sacki.
lujvo c1 is a flamingo of species c2. Cf. fagri, cipni.
lujvo x1=fe1 is the ashes of x3=fa2, combusted by fire x2=fa1. Cf. fagyfesyska.
lujvo s1 is/appears to be of ash color/hue as perceived/seen by x2=s3 under conditions x3=s4. Cf. fagyfesti.
lujvo k1 is a spark of fire x2=f1.
lujvo g1 extinguishes/puts out fire x2=s1=f1. Cf. fagysti.
lujvo x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of charcoal from source x2
lujvo x1=g3 is a torch illuminating g2 with fuel x3=f2 reacting with oxydizer x4=f3 (default air/oxygen). Cf. dictergu'i, laktergu'i.
lujvo z1 is a fireplace/hearth for fuel f2 burning in/reacting with oxidizer f3 (default air/oxygen). Cf. fagri, zdani, toknu.
cmavo FA sumti place tag: tag a sumti moved out of numbered place structure; used in modal conversions.
lujvo b1 distributes b2 to b3 from b4 over path b5. b1 is a distributor. Cf. benji, mrilu, xatra, tcana.

lujvo c1 is/are a/the function/activities involving persons c2 distributing f1 among/to f2; c1 is distribution C.f. fatri, cuntu, selvensro, terzbasro, vencu'u, zbacu'u, dintrocu'u, dinveicu'u. In a company, this may be referred to as logistics or channel management.
lujvo g1 [person/agent] distributes/allots/allocates/shares f1 among f2 with shares/portions f3. Cf. fatri, gasnu.

lujvo s1 is a socialist ideology as applied by t1 in/among people/territory/domain t2=f2 based on the works of thinker s3 From fatri, prali, turni, sidbo. Cf. sivypo'eci'e, ka'irtrusi'o, dzejdasratrusi'o, vricykricrutrusi'o, guntrusi'o, natpamtrusi'o, tsarainaitrusi'o.
lujvo p1=f1 is/are the profit/dividends shared/distributed from the earnings of company/corporation/firm p2 among f2 with shares/portions f3. Cf. fatri, prali, ra'erprali, posyselfai, dejyterze'a.
lujvo x1=l1=f1 explores fact x3=f2 about x2=l2=f3 using instrument x4=l3
lujvo b1 is a parachute of type/material b2. Cf. bukfa'u, bukyvoi, vofli, santa.
lujvo c1 (agent) drops f1 to f2 from f3.
lujvo g1 makes f1 fall. Cf. farlu, gasnu, cirko, renro
fu'ivla x1 is a falcon (genus 'falco'). see cipnrfalko
gismu rafsi: fan x1 is a sail for gathering propelling material x2 on vehicle/motor x3. Waterwheel (= jacfanxi'u). See also bloti.
lujvo x1 is the factorial of x2. See also ne'o
lujvo c1 (agent) concludes by expressing/saying c2=f1 for/to audience c3 via expressive medium c4 concluding f2. From fanmo, cusku. Cf. mulno, lojycpa, ni'i, ja'o.
gismu x1 is an aunt/uncle of x2 by bond/tie x3; x1 is an associated member of x2's parent's generation. See also bruna, mamta, mensi, patfu, rirni, tamne.
lujvo c1 is a terminator of class/part-of-speech c2 in language c3.
lujvo b1 is canvas of material b2. Cf. falnu, bukpu, marnybu'u
gismu x1 is a function/single-valued mapping from domain x2 to range x3 defined by expression/rule x4. See also mekso, bridi.
gismu x1 is alien/foreign/[exotic]/unfamiliar to x2 in property x3 (ka). See also cizra, jbena, ckini.

lujvo t1=d1=f1 is a windsurfingboard of material/property t2. From tanbo, djacu, falnu (f2, f3 subsumed). See also sufingboard (=bonjacta'o), kitesurfingboard (=volfanjacta'o), wakesurfingboard (=blobonjacta'o).
lujvo k1 sails to destination k2 from origin k3 via route k4 on sailing vehicle k5=f3. Cf. voikla.

gismu rafsi: fam fa'o x1 is an end/finish/termination of thing/process x2; [not necessarily implying completeness]. x1 is final/last/at the last; x1 is a terminal/terminus of x2; x1 is the final/terminated state of terminated process x2; x2 terminates/ceases/stops/halts at x1 (= selfa'o for reordered places). See also krasi, cfari, mulno, sisti, denpa, jipno, kojna, traji, krasi.
gismu x1 is a factory/foundry/industrial plant/mill producing x2 from materials x3. See also molki, gundi.
lujvo g1 is a/the manufacturing industry/sector, manufacturing/processing g2=f2 at factories/plants f1 from materials f3 using process g3 From fanri, gundi.
lujvo p1 is an industrial park managed by community/polity/company p2 for factories/plants producing f2. Cf. fanri, panka, zacpanka, zdipanka, gubypanka, kagnypanka.
gismu x1 prevents/keeps/stops/restrains/constrains event x2 from occurring. See also pinfu, bandu, zunti, rinju, jimte, bapli, rivbi.
gismu x1 translates text/utterance x2 to language x3 from language x4 with translation result x5. See also cusku, bangu.
gismu rafsi: faz x1 (event) annoys/irritates/bothers/distracts x2. Also: is disruptive to. See also fengu, raktu, dicra, tunta, zunti, jicla.

gismu rafsi: fap pro x1 opposes/balances/contends against opponent(s) x2 (person/force ind./mass) about x3 (abstract). Also resists. See also bandu, bradi, darlu, damba, jivna, lanxe, rivbi, sarji, xarnu.
lujvo c1 gets lost on the way to f2 (object/event) in/near f3=c3 from farna cirko
lujvo x1=d1 is the opposite direction from x3=f3 that x2=f2 is.
lujvo g1=f3 aims at f1 with f2 (object/event). x3 can be x1 itself or an extra object/event such as "weapon", "effort", etc. Cf. farna.
lujvo j1 shows the direction of f2 (object/event) to audience j3 from origin/in frame of reference f3 Cf. farsni, degja'o.

gismu rafsi: fal fa'u x1 falls/drops to x2 from x3 in gravity well/frame of reference x4. Note: things can fall in spin, thrust, or tide as well as gravity; (agentive "drop" = one of two lujvo: falcru and falri'a). See also lafti, cpare, klama, sfubu.

gismu rafsi: far fa'a x1 is the direction of x2 (object/event) from origin/in frame of reference x3. x2 is towards x1 from x3 (= selfa'a for reordered places). See also zunle, pritu, galtu, gapru, cnita, dizlo, berti, snanu, stuna, stici, purci, balvi, lidne.
lujvo s1=f3 non-agentively/inanimately points at/directionally indicates s2=f2 to observer s3 as being in the direction f1. Direction (i.e. x4) is relative to the x1 place. Cf. farja'o, degja'o.
gismu rafsi: fav x1 develops/evolves towards/into x2 from x3 through stages x4. See also pruce, banro, makcu, ciste, cupra, ferti.
lujvo s1=f1 reflects Breton culture/language in aspect s2=f2.

gismu rafsi: fau x1 (event) is an event that happens/occurs/takes place; x1 is an incident/happening/occurrence. (cf. cmavo list fau, krefu, lifri, fatci, rapli; gasnu, zukte, if specifically agentive, banli)
lujvo v1 is a verb meaning v2 in language v3. Cf. fasnu, valsi, gasnu
lujvo f1=b1 is the French language used by b2 to express/communicate b3 (si'o/du'u, not quote). Cf. fraso, bangu, banfuru'a.
lujvo g1=f1 is the country of France. Cf. fraso, gugde, gugdefuru.
gismu rafsi: fac x1 (du'u) is a fact/reality/truth/actuality, in the absolute. See also datni, jitfa, sucta, xanri, jetnu, fasnu, zasti, cfika, saske.
lujvo f1 = k1 [sequence] is able to be / capable of being reversed from / into sequence f2 by event k2 under conditions k3 (event / state). From fatne + kakne.
gismu rafsi: fat fa'e x1 [sequence] is in reverse order from x2 [sequence]; x1 (object) is inverted from x2 (object). Also opposite (one sense). See also cmavo list fa'e, dukti.

gismu rafsi: fai x1 is distributed/allotted/allocated/shared among x2 with shares/portions x3; (x2/x3 fa'u). Also spread, shared out, apportioned; agentive distribution (= fairgau, fairzu'e). See also cmavo list fa'u, fendi, preja, katna, tcana.
lujvo x1 (me'o) is the p-adic representation of number x2 in base x3. can be infinitely long to the left but not the right; for repeating p-adics (krefu fatysaclu) use ra'e before pi
cmavo BAI fasnu modal, 1st place (non-causal) in the event of ...
lujvo f1 is an event that has time/temporal duration t1 ranging from starting time/event t2 to ending time/event t3. Made from fasnu + temci.
lujvo g1 develops f1 into f2 from f3 through stages f4.

lujvo t1 is a developmental / evolutionary stage / state of t2 = f1 in its development towards / into f2 from f3 through stages f4. First place is intended for things like software version numbers. See also favytcinymupli (which is how you talk about actual things that have a version associated with them). Made from farvi + tcini.

lujvo m1 is an example/instance of developmental/evolutionary stage/state m2=t1 of developing thing t2=f1 in its development towards/into f2 from f3 through stages f4=m3. Someone causing the development is neither implied nor denied; hence this word can be used both for Darwinian evolution and software development. Made from favytcini + mupli.
lujvo t1 chatters/gossips to t2=f2 about subject t3 in language t4.
cmavo FA sumti place tag: tag 2nd sumti place.
cmavo VUhU3 binary mathematical operator: nth root of; inverse power [a to the 1/b power].
cmavo FEhE mark space interval distributive aspects; labels interval tense modifiers as location-oriented.
cmavo cluster ZAhO* location event contour tense: perfective in space; beyond the place of ...
cmavo cluster ZAhO* location event contour tense: continuative in space; throughout the place of ...
cmavo cluster ZAhO* location event contour tense: initiative in space; on this edge of ...
cmavo cluster ZAhO* location event contour tense: achievative in space; at the point of ...
cmavo cluster ZAhO* location event contour tense: completive in space; at the far end of ...
cmavo cluster ROI* location tense interval modifier: never in space; objectively quantified tense.
cmavo cluster ZAhO* location event contour tense: anticipative in space; up to the edge of ...
cmavo cluster ROI* location tense interval modifier: always in space; objectively quantified tense.
cmavo cluster ZAhO* location event contour tense: superfective in space; continuing too far beyond ...
cmavo VUhU1 n-ary mathematical operator: divided by; division operator; [(((a / b) / c) / ...)].
cmavo COI vocative: over and out (end discussion).
cmavo FEhU elidable terminator: end nonce conversion of selbri to modal; usually elidable.
lujvo c1=f1 growls/snarls/roars c2 [non-linguistic utterence] in anger at f2 for f3 (action/state/property). Cf. fengu, cmoni, fegba'u, capsidba'u.

lujvo g1 (person/agent) boils x2=f1 at temperature x3=f2 and pressure x4=f3. Note that this means simply to evaporate a liquid; to cook something by boiling is febjukpa. Also c.f. jukpa, djacu, ladru, cidja, patxu.
lujvo x1=j1 cooks/prepares food-for-eating x2=j2 by sitting it in boiling liquid x3=f1 at temperature x4=f2 and pressure x5=f3
gismu rafsi: feb x1 boils/evaporates at temperature x2 and pressure x3. Roil (= febjicla). See also dunja, lunsa, runme.
lujvo b1=f1 roars/snarls/growls angrily atterance b2 at f2 because of f3 (action/state/property). Cf. fengu, bacru, capsidba'u, fe'ucmo.
lujvo m1=f1 is irritated/[mildly angry] at f2 for f3 (action/state/property).
lujvo m1=f1=b1 grumbles with sound b2 at f2 because of f3 (action/state/property). jvajvo definition; Gismu deep structure is "milxe le ka fengu kei gi'e bacru"
lujvo r1 (event) angers f1. Cf. fengu, rinka
lujvo f1=c1 is without anger/mild/meek regarding f2 for f3 (action/state/property).
lujvo x1 is November/eleventh month of year x2 in calendar x3. Note: Based on experimental rafsi for fei (fel). Use with caution. Alternative: pavypavma'i

gismu rafsi: fem x1 is 10^{-15} of x2 in dimension/aspect x3 (default is units). See also grake, mitre, snidu, stero, delno, molro, kelvo, xampo, gradu, litce, merli, centi, decti, dekto, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, xexso, zepti, zetro
gismu rafsi: fed x1 (agent) divides/partitions/separates x2 into sections/parts/ind. x3 by method/partition x4. Also segments. See also sepli, bitmu, fatri, dilcu, katna, frinu.
lujvo m1 is a sewing pattern of forms m2 according to structure m3.
gismu rafsi: feg fe'u x1 is angry/mad at x2 for x3 (action/state/property). See also fanza, dunku.
gismu rafsi: fek x1 (action/event) is crazy/insane/mad/frantic/in a frenzy (one sense) by standard x2. See also bebna, racli, xajmi.
gismu rafsi: fer fe'a x1 is a crack/fissure/pass/cleft/ravine/chasm/[defect/flaw] [shape/form] in x2. See also kevna, cfila, jinto.

gismu rafsi: fen fe'o x1 sews/stitches/sutures materials x2 (ind./set) together with tool(s) x3, using filament x4. (x2 if a set must be a complete specification); See also cilta, jivbu, jorne, nivji, pijne, lasna.

gismu rafsi: fep fei x1 is measured in kopeck/cent money-subunits as x2 [quantity], in monetary system x3. Also pfennig, paisa, sen, fen, dinar, etc.; x1 is generally a price/cost/value. (additional secondary, tertiary, etc. subunit places may be added as x4, x5, x6, ...); See also sicni, jdini, jdima, vecnu, rupnu, dekpu, gutci, minli, merli, bunda, kramu.
gismu x1 is a/the lung [body-part] of x2; [metaphor: breathing/respiratory apparatus/bellows]. Also (adjective:) x1 is pulmonary. See also pambe, vasxu.
lujvo s1 is a cent coin issued by s2 in monetary system f3.

gismu rafsi: fre x1 is fertile/conducive for supporting the growth/development of x2; x1 is fruitful/prolific. Also fecund (note that the Lojban covers both potential and actual/realized fertility). See also vanbi, sidju, rorci, farvi, banro, cange.

cmene x1 is Virgo [constellation/astrological sign]. From ferti. The Greeks and Romans associated Virgo with their goddess of wheat, Demeter-Ceres who is the mother of Proserpina-Persephone. For this reason the constellation became associated with fertility (in both Babylonia, Greece and Rome). Alternatively, she was sometimes identified as the virgin goddess Iustitia or Astraea, holding the scales of justice in her hand as the constellation Libra. Since ferti in lojban covers both potential and actual/realized fertility, the original meaning of the constellation have been chosen, but you could probably still interpret the name in both senses (as a deity of fecundity or as a fertile virgin).
lujvo x1=f2=c1 abandons / forsakes / leaves behind x2=f1=c2 Cf. festi, cliva, tolcpa, radycru.
gismu rafsi: fes x1(s) is/are waste product(s) [left to waste] by x2 (event/activity). Also shit, crap; agentive wasting (= fesygau, fesyzu'e). See also xaksu, kalci, pinca.
lujvo x1=g1 [person/agent] leaves waste product/wastes x2=f1 by event/activity x3=f2=g2 Made from festi + gasnu
lujvo c1 is a goddess of people(s)/religion c2 with dominion over c3 [sphere]. Cf. fetsi, cevni, lijda, krici, censa, malsi

lujvo c1 is gynophilous/bisexual/straight male/lesbian in situation c2 by standard c4. This word is only about sexual interest in females; other sexual interests are irrelevant. Cf. nakcinse, fetfetcinse, mitcinse, dutcinse.
lujvo c1=f1 is female and gynophilous/gay/bisexual in situation c2 by standard c4 This word is about female homosexuality and bisexuality. See also fetcinse, naknakcinse, mitcinse, relcinse.
lujvo f1=n1 is an unmarried woman under law/custom/tradition s3. Cf. nalspe, naknalspe, specfari'i, bavyspe, pruspe.
lujvo p1 is the clitoris of p2. Cf. fetsi, pinji, nakpinji, vibna, vlagi, plibu
gismu rafsi: fet fe'i x1 is a female/doe of species x2 evidencing feminine trait(s) x3 (ka); x1 is feminine. See also nakni.
lujvo x1 is a wife of x2 (spouse) according to marriage tradition/custom/law x3. Cf. nakspe, pruspe, bavyspe, specfari'i.
lujvo t1 is a matriarch of people/territory/domain/subjects t2. Cf. nakydzetru, nolkantru.
lujvo x1 is an ovary of x2. Cf. sovda, gletu, gutra.

cmavo FA sumti place tag: place structure number/tag question.
cmavo BAI finti modal, 1st place (creator) created by ...
lujvo c1 is a fish-eater of fish species f2. Cf. finpe, citka, re'ucti, stagycti.
cmavo COI vocative: hospitality - inhospitality; you are welcome/ make yourself at home.

lujvo xr1 is a guineafowl of species/breed xr2
cmavo PA3 digit/number: fraction slash; default "/n" => 1/n, "n/" => n/1, or "/" alone => golden ratio.
cmavo cluster PA* half. synonym pimu; see also xadba
lujvo g1 [person/agent] confuses c1 (event/state) for c2 [observer] due to [confusing] property c3 (ka).
lujvo b1 becomes different/changes/transforms from f2 in property/dimension/quantity f3 under conditions b3. Cf. frica, binxo.
gismu rafsi: fig x1 is a fig [fruit/tree] of species/strain x2. See also grute.
lujvo cu1=cf1 is a fictional book about plot/theme/subject cf1 by author cu3=cf3 for audience cu4 preserved in medium cu5. Cf. lisycku, ctucku, tadycku, ckusro, cesysku.
fu'ivla x1 is a fern of family/genus/species x2.
lujvo g1 [person/agent] causes f1 to be easy for f2 under condition(s) f3. Cf. frili, gasnu, filri'a, sutygau, sutri'a.
lujvo z1=f1 (action) is easier than z2 (action) for x3=f2 (agent) by amount z4 under conditions x5=f3.
lujvo r1 [event/state] causes f1 to be easy for f2 under condition(s) f3. Cf. frili, rinka, filgau, sutri'a, sutygau.

lujvo g2=f1 is apparent to g1 via perceptual/cognitive faculty g3. x3 includes reason or critical thinking skills as well as discrete biological organs such as eyes or ears. Cf. frili, sapselga'e, sampu, klina.
lujvo f1=sj1 (du'u) is an easy to understand/clear fact/truth to f2=sj2 about subject sj3 under conditions f4.

lujvo s1 is easily understood/interpreted as the meaning of s2 by (agent) s3=f2 under conditions f3. From frili+smuni. The x1 of frili is subsumed into the overall sense of the word. See also: filseljmi, klina.
gismu rafsi: fis x1 reflects Palestinian culture/nationality in aspect x2. See also jordo, xebro.
lujvo t1=f2 speaks fluently to t2 about subject t3 in language t4 under conditions f3. Cf. frili, tavla.
lujvo fr1=fi1 dedicates invention/creation/composition/work fr2=fi2 to fr3 with conditions fr4.
gismu rafsi: fip fi'e x1 is a fish of species x2 [metaphorical extension to sharks, non-fish aquatic vertebrates]. See also danlu.
fu'ivla x1 is a trout of species/breed x2
fu'ivla x1 is a candirú of species/variety x2. syn. kandiru, pincyfi'e; see also latfi'e
fu'ivla x1 is a halibut of species x2. syn. polgosu; see also flundero, cucyzbefi'e, mlafi'e

gismu rafsi: fin fi'i x1 invents/creates/composes/authors x2 for function/purpose x3 from existing elements/ideas x4. x1 is creative/inventive. See also cmavo list fi'e, ciska, pemci, zbasu, larcu, specific works of authorship, prosa, skina.
fu'ivla x1 is an aspect of / a part of The Force connecting / within x2 No attempt at good fu'ivla making was harmed in the creation of this word.
lujvo c1 is a fish farm at c2, farmed by c3, raising/producing fish species x4=f2.
lujvo fi1 is a gill of fish fe2=fi1 of species x3=fi2. See also fipybirka, fipyrebla for other fish-body related words.
lujvo x1 fishes for fish species x2. see also finpe, genxu, xlura
lujvo x1 is March of year x2 in calendar x3. Cf. cibmasti, kanbyma'i, nanca.
lujvo x1 is stick-shaped fish meat [a fishstick] of fish type/species x2 Cf. finpe, rectu, grana
lujvo b1 is a fin of fish x2=f1 of species x3=f2. Cf. fipyrebla, fipfepri, limna'i.
lujvo g1 is a/the fisheries industry/sector producing fish products g2 from fish species f2 by process g3 Cf. finpe, gundi, nunjacycrepu. Omit f1.
lujvo r1 is the tail fin of fish r2=f1 of species x3=f2. Cf. limna.
lujvo g1 is a mask covering the face of g2=f2.
lujvo k1 is the beard/moustace/facial hair of f2=k2.
lujvo p1 is a silhouette of f1 made by p3 in medium p4.
lujvo x1 rejects x2 (offer, suggestion, proposal) from x3.
lujvo x1 accepts x2 (an offer/suggestion) from x3. Cf. friti, tugni, cpazau, radji'i, zarcpa.
lujvo c1=f3 [lacks law]/[is lawless with regard to] law(s) f1 specifying f2 (state/event) under conditions f4 by lawgiver(s) f5; c1=f3 is lawless. Cf. flalu, claxu.

lujvo g1=t1 is the Lower House/House of Representatives/House of Commons for territory t2 with members g3=f5. Cf. flalu, cfari, turni, girzu, flazautrugri, truci'e, zuktruci'e, flatruci'e, pairtruci'e, vajraifla.

gismu rafsi: fla x1 is a law specifying x2 (state/event) for community x3 under conditions x4 by lawgiver(s) x5. x1 is a legality; x2 is legal/licit/legalized/a legality (= selfla for reordered places). See also javni, ritli, zekri, pulji, tinbe.
lujvo t1 is an outlaw not following the law t2 made by t3.
gismu x1 is a flute/pipe/fife/recorder [flute-like/air-reed musical instrument]. See also zgike.
fu'ivla x1 is a dizi. Cf. flani, pinflani, zgica'a.
lujvo z1 is a judicial court administering lawsuit p2=f2 for community f3. Cf. zdani, pajni, flalu.
lujvo fa1 rebels against/opposes law fl1, which specifies fl2 (state/event) for community fl3 under conditions fl4 by lawgiver(s) fl5.
lujvo r1=f5 enacts r2=f1 (law/legislation/treaties/act) for community f3 under condition r3=f4. x1 is usually a national parliament.
lujvo g2 is a/are citizen(s) of country g1 according to law f1 specifying f2 (state/event) for community f3. From flalu, gugde. Cf. flaxa'u.
lujvo c1=t1=f5 is the legislative branch of the government of people/territory/domain/subjects t2. Cf. flalu, turni, ciste, truci'e, zuktruci'e, pairtruci'e, flacfatrugri, flazautrugri, vajraifla.
fu'ivla x1 is a plum of variety x2. see also persika, rutrprunu
lujvo x1 is a/are legal resident(s) of location/country x2 according to law f1 specifying f2 (state/event) for community f3. From flalu, xabju. Cf. flaselgu'e.
lujvo g1=t1 is the Upper House/Senate/House of Lords for territory t2 with members g3=f5=z3. Cf. flalu, zanru, turni, girzu, flacfatrugri, truci'e, zuktruci'e, flatruci'e, pairtruci'e, vajraifla.
lujvo c1 pours/intensely rains to c2 from c3.

gismu rafsi: fle x1 is a current/flow/river of/in x2 flowing in direction to/towards x3 from direction/source x4. [x1 is a stream of x2; x2 is a fluid Gas or liquid. (= selfle for reordered places); x1 flushes toward x3; flush (= caifle, sukfle)]; See also rirxe, senta where no directionality is implied, rinci, xampo, dikca, sakci, gapci, litki, ciblu.

gismu rafsi: fli x1 fails at doing x2 (state/event); x1 is a failure at its role in x2. Baffled (= pesfli, jmifli, dafspufli, menfli, among other senses); also x2 ceases/does not complete/fails to continue due to failure on the part of x1. See also cfila, snada, srera, troci, sisti, ranji, denpa, bebna, zunti.
gismu rafsi: fir x1 is a/the face [head/body-part] of x2; (adjective:) x1 is facial. See also sefta, stedu, crane, mebri.
lujvo x1 bounces x2 back to x3 from x4 because of failure x5.
lujvo x1=z1=f1 does x2=z2 to achieve goal x3=z3=f2 which x1 fails to achieve.
lujvo b1=f1 is an iceberg floating on f2 (water, sea etc.).
fu'ivla x1 is a flounder of species x2. Cf. mlafi'e.

gismu rafsi: flo foi x1 is a field [shape/form] of material x2; x1 is a broad uniform expanse of x2. Also woods (= ricfoi), lawn/meadow (= sasfoi), brush (= spafoi, cicyspafoi). See also purdi, cange.
fu'ivla x1 is a pangolin of species/breed x2. Cf. mabru, manti, mudyctijalra.
lujvo x1 is foamless/unleavened. see also nanbrmatsa, fomymledi
lujvo c1 is a quantity/contains Swiss cheese/cheese with holes from source c2. Cf. xelveto, xelvetik, ladru.
lujvo s1 is a bubble of material f2 filled with f3.
lujvo v1 is made of/contains/is a quantity of sparkling wine from fruit/grapes v2. Cf. fonmo, vanju, risyvanju, xalka, jikru, birje, uiski, campania, vo'otka, koinka.
lujvo x1 is yeast of species x2 growing on x3. see also nanba, birje, vanju
lujvo j1 is a telephone number of j2.
gismu rafsi: fom fo'o x1 is a quantity of foam/froth/suds of material x2, with bubbles/vacuoles of material x3. See also zbabu.
lujvo t1 talks on the phone to t2 about t3 in language t4.
gismu rafsi: fon x1 is a telephone transceiver/modem attached to system/network x2. See also tcana.
lujvo n1 is an answering machine/voice mail message about n2 from n3 to n4.
gismu rafsi: fro x1 is a fork/fork-type tool/utensil for purpose x2 with tines/prongs x3 on base/support x4. See also dakfu, smuci, komcu, tutci.
fu'ivla x1 is a strawberry of species/breed x2. Cf. frambesi, grute, jbari, rozgu.
fu'ivla x1 is an ash of species/variety x2.
fu'ivla x1 is a blackberry/raspberry/bramble of species x2. Cf. fragari, grute, jbari, rozgu.
fu'ivla x1 is a buckthorn of species/variety x2.
gismu rafsi: fas x1 reflects French/Gallic culture/nationality/language in aspect x2. See also ropno.

gismu rafsi: fra x1 reacts/responds/answers with action x2 to stimulus x3 under conditions x4; x1 is responsive. x3 stimulates x1 into reaction x2, x3 stimulates reaction x2 (= terfra for place reordering); attempt to stimulate, prod (= terfratoi, tunterfratoi). See also preti, danfu, spuda, cpedu, tarti.
gismu rafsi: fax x1 forgives x2 for event/state/activity x3. See also dunda, curmi, zungi.
fu'ivla x1 is February in year x2 on calendar x3
lujvo g1 (person/agent) fertilises g2=f1 for supporting the growth/development of x3=f2.
gismu rafsi: fic x1 differs/is distinct from/contrasts with/is unlike x2 in property/dimension/quantity x3. Also other-than (less common meaning). See also ranxi, drata, dunli, simsa, vrici.
lujvo x1 makes x2 undergo experience x3; x1 treats x2 in manner x3.
gismu rafsi: fi'o x1 reflects African culture/nationality/geography in aspect x2. See also ropno, xazdo.
lujvo f1=t1 is Africa from friko tumla c.f.zdotu'a rontu'a tcotu'a sralytu'a bemtu'a ziptu'a
gismu rafsi: fil x1 (action) is easy/simple/facile for x2 (agent) under conditions x3; x2 does x1 freely/easily. See also nandu, sampu, zifre.
gismu x1 is a fraction, with numerator x2, denominator x3 (x2/x3). See also parbi, dilcu, mekso, fendi.

gismu rafsi: fit x1 offers/proffers x2 [offering] to x3 with conditions x4. (x4 may be nu canja, nu pleji, etc.; an unconditional offering has the 'condition' of acceptance); x2 may be a specific object, a commodity (mass), an event, or a property; pedantically, for objects/commodities, this is sumti-raising from ownership of the object/commodity (= posfriti, posyselfriti for unambiguous semantics). See also canja, dunda, rinsa, vecnu, jdima, cnemu, pleji, vitke.
fu'ivla x1 is a bandersnatch of species x2
lujvo fru1=fra1 frowns/grimaces at/in reaction to fra3.
gismu rafsi: fru x1 frowns/grimaces (facial expression). x1 frowns/grimaces at/in reaction to x2 (= frufra). See also cmila, cisma.

gismu rafsi: gad x1 is an article/descriptor labelling description x2 (text) in language x3 with semantics x4. x2 is the noun phrase/sumti without the article/descriptor; description ((x1 with x2) = gadysu'i); note: 'determiner' has become the accepted general linguistics term, displacing 'article'; however, 'determiner' includes all words that can introduce a noun phrase/sumti, whether a description or not, such as pronoun possessives like lemi, quantifiers (especially in indefinites) like ci and su'o, and demonstratives like ti, ta, and tu; the term 'descriptor' in Lojban, is limited to words that introduce descriptions (excluding indefinites), such as those of selma'o LA and LE, their common compounds such as lemi, and possibly lenu. 'article' typically refers only to a single word; Lojban assumes the broader meaning] See also valsi, cmavo.
lujvo gas1 puts cover gac1 on gac2. Cf. gacri, gasnu.
lujvo d1=g1 is a flood covering g2. Cf. gacri, djacu, dukse.

lujvo c1=g1 is the lap of t2. Cf. galtu, tuple, crane, tsetupyzbe.
gismu x1 is a/the throat/gullet [body-part] of x2; [metaphor: narrow(ing) opening of a deep hole]. See also cnebo, kevna, tunlo.

lujvo f1=g1 is a/the pharynx [body-part] of g2. Similar to pharanx (gr. cleft, chasm). Nasopharynx (=zbigalxyfe'a), oropharynx (=molgalxyfe'a), laryngopharynx/hypopharynx (=galxyferni'a). See also moldruji'o, galxe and [fenra}.

See also pencu, sanji, viska, sumne, tirna, zgana, canci, simlu.
gismu x1 is a/the testes/ovary/testicle/scrotum/balls/gonad/stamen/pistil [body-part] of x2, gender x3. Egg/sperm/pollen/gamete producing/bearing organ. See also plibu, sovda, pinji, gutra, mabla.

See also jitro, ralju, sazri, te bende, jatna, fukpi, morna.

(cf. brito which refers to the United Kingdom as a whole or to the British empire, merko, sralo, kadno, skoto)

cmene Guangzhou Based on the Chinese Mandarin pronunciation. For the name based on the local Cantonese pronunciation see guonJAUS.
lujvo gun1=gub1 is a/the public sector owned by community gub2 (mass) providing/producing gun2 by process gun3 From gubni gundi.
lujvo j1 advertises jg3=g1 (du'u) to jg2=g2 (mass) about subject jg4. not necessarily advertising for sale; (cf. jungau)
gismu rafsi: gub x1 is public/un-hidden/open/jointly available to/owned by all among community x2 (mass). See also sivni.
lujvo g1=n1 is an advertisement about subject n2 from author n3 to audience g2=n4. Cf. gubni, notci, vecnu.
lujvo c1 votes (in a public election) for c2 among choices c3 in electorate g2.
lujvo s1=k3=g1 is a paliamentary republic with representatives s2=k1 representating community g2=k2 (mass)
lujvo p1=g1 is a public square managed by/belonging to polity/community p2. Cf. gubni, panka, zacpanka, zdipanka, fanrypanka, kagnypanka.
lujvo s1=g1 is a republic governed by people s2=g2
lujvo s1=g1 is the reputation of c1 for c2 (ka) known/imagined by s2=g2 (mass) From gubni si'o ckaji. In English, usually 'x1 is the reputation for x3 that x2 has with x4'.
lujvo n3 publishes about subject n2 with message n1=g1 to intended audience n4. Cf. ckupra, terkarni, kamgubgau.
lujvo b1 defends country b2=g1 from threat/peril/potential b3. Cf. jamna, damba, jenmi, bilni, sonci, tutra.
lujvo n2 is a treaty between countries n1=n3

gismu rafsi: gug gu'e x1 is the country of peoples x2 with land/territory x3; (people/territory relationship). Also sovereignty, domestic (as opposed to foreign), nation (when not referring to ethos). See also turni, natmi, jecta, tumla, tutra, lanci.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 AR (Argentina) for people x2. Cf. getygu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 EU (European Union) for people x2. EU is an exceptionally reserved ISO-3166 code. Cf. rongunma, ropno, rontu'a
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 EG (Egypt) for people x2. Cf. misrygu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 ES (Spain) for people x2. Cf. sangu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 ID (Indonesia) for people x2. Cf. bidgu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 IQ (Iraq) for people x2. Cf. raksygu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 IL (Israel) for people x2. Cf. brogu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 IN (India) for people x2. Cf. xingu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 IR (Iran, Islamic Republic Of) for people x2. Cf. gugdrxirana.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 IT (Italy) for people x2. Ch. italian, gugdrtalia.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 UA (Ukraine) for people x2. Cf. vurgu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 US (United States) for people x2. Cf. mergu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 ''BD'' (Bangladesh) for people x2. Cf. gugde, begygu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 BR (Brazil) for people x2. Cf. razgu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 CA (Canada) for people x2. Cf. kadnygu'e, KEnydys, kenyDAS.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 CN (China) for people x2. Cf. jugygu'e, djunguos, xa'anzu.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 ''CH'' (Switzerland) for people x2. Cf. gugdrxelvo, xelvet, xelvetik.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 DE (Germany) for people x2. Cf. dotygu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 FR (France) for people x2. Cf. fasygu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 GB (United Kingdom) for people x2. Cf. ritygu'e, gligu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 GR (Greece) for people x2. Cf. xesygu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 JP (Japan) for people x2. Cf. pongu'e.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 KP (Korea, Democratic People'S Republic Of) for people x2. Cf. gugdrtcosena, gugdrgogurio.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 KR (Korea, Republic Of) for people x2. Cf. gugdrxanguke, gugdrgogurio.
fu'ivla x1 is the country with the code ISO-3166 MX (Mexico) for people x2. Cf. mexygu'e.
