lujvo x1=s2=g2 is autistic/Aspergian, unable to understand social behavior x2=g3.
lujvo gas1=s1 raises/elevates it/his/her self by in frame of reference gal2 as compared with standard/baseline gal3. Cf. sevzi, galtu, gasnu.
lujvo g1=se2 pretends to have property(ies) si2 to observer si3 under conditions si4 c.f. sevzi simlu gasnu selxarkei.
lujvo r1=s2 throws/launches/casts/hurls oneself to/at/in direction r3. Cf. sevzi, renro.
cmavo cluster BAI* zukte modal, 2nd place purposefully; goalfully acting at ...
lujvo x1 commits suicide / kills him/herself by method x2.
lujvo f1=s2 exercises/show self-restraint from sevzi fanta c.f. nunsezyfanta
lujvo j1=s2 is conceited by standard d3 from sevzi jgira dukse
lujvo x1=sel1=sev2 is selfish/self-serving/egotistical in regard to activity x2=sel3. x1=sel1=sev2 is an egotist.
lujvo n1 is an autobiography/resumé/home page of n2=n3, intended for n4. Cf. skicu, notci, skami, samseltcana, ueb
lujvo j1=s2 is out of control/temper of/with regard to j3 (activity/event/performance). Cf. to'e, sevzi, jitro, se'itro, tolse'itro, fenki, fengu.
lujvo s1=z1 improves itself/is self-improving/augmenting/increasing in property/quantity z2 by amount z3. From sevzi + zenba. Dropped s2 place, as is common for sevzi lujvo.
gismu x1 is a fly [a small non-stinging flying insect] of species/breed x2. See also cinki, bifce.

gismu rafsi: sfa x1 (agent) punishes x2 for infraction x3 (event/state/action) with punishment x4 (event/state). Also chastise, castigate, chasten, discipline, correct (one sense); also x4 penalty. See also cnemu, pleji, venfu, zekri, canja, dunda, jdima, jerna, kargu, prali, dapma, cirko, jinga.
fu'ivla x1 reflects Swedish culture/nationality/language in aspect x2
gismu rafsi: sfo x1 is a sofa/couch (noun). See also nilce.
gismu rafsi: sub su'u x1 dives/swoops [manner of controlled falling] to x2 from x3. See also farlu
lujvo x1 is an ungulate of order/family/species x2. see bakni,xirma, lanme, kanba, xarju
cmavo SI erase the last Lojban word, treating non-Lojban text as a single word.
cmavo UI3b discursive: similarly. See also simsa, panra.
lujvo sl3 is an ceremony/celebration for recognizing/honoring si2 (object of esteem) with participants sl1=si1. Cf. sinma, salci, tersla, jmaji, jikca.
lujvo x1 (event) hurts/damages the respect/high regard/esteem for x2=s2 held by by s1 with result x4 (state). Cf. sinma, xrani.
lujvo st1 is a place of honor/[shrine/podium/wall area/trophy case] for person/thing/[event] st2=si2 venerated/honored by si1 c.f. sinma stuzi tsina.
cmavo MOI convert number to portion selbri; x1 is an (n)th portion of mass/totality x2; (cf. gunma).
lujvo d1 is an igloo for purpose d2. Cf. boldi'u, zdani.
lujvo t1=s1 is a snowboard of material/property t2. From tanbo, snime. See also xilta'o.
cmavo VUhU4 trinary mathematical operator: [sigma summation of a using variable b over range c].
lujvo p1 is seigniorage earned by p2=z1 in making coin z2=s1
cmavo rafsi: siz NU abstractor: idea/concept abstractor; x1 is x2's concept of [bridi].
cmavo BAI sidju modal, 1st place (aiding agent) aided by ...

lujvo v1 is an idea-carrying virus / meme / self-propagating idea capable of infecting / currently infecting v3=s3 with idea / concept / belief / opinion s1 about thing / topic / subject s2. vidru place 2 is dropped due to redundancy with sidbo. Made of sidbo + vidru.
lujvo s1 reflects Irish culture/nationality/language in aspect s2.
gismu rafsi: sil x1 [sound source] whistles/makes whistling sound/note/tone/melody x2. See also sance, tonga, sanga, zgike, savru.
gismu rafsi: si'i x1 is a coin/token/is specie issued by x2 having value x3 of composition including x4. See also fepni, jdini, rupnu.

gismu rafsi: sib si'o x1 (idea abstract) is an idea/concept/thought about x2 (object/abstract) by thinker x3. Also (adjective:) x1 is ideal/ideational. See also ciksi, jijnu, mucti, jinvi, nabmi, pensi, xanri, cmavo list si'o.
gismu rafsi: dju x1 helps/assists/aids object/person x2 do/achieve/maintain event/activity x3. See also cmavo list si'u, rirni, sarji, vipsi, ferti, selfu.
lujvo x1 is a figurative/metaphorical/non-literal meaning/interpretation of x2 recognized/seen/accepted by x3 . See also stidi, smuni, pe'a
fu'ivla x1 is a flea of species x2. Cf. cinki, blusfani, civla, gerku.
gismu rafsi: sig x1 is a cigar/cigarette/cigarillo made from tobacco/smokable substance x2 by x3. See also danmo, jelca, tanko, marna.
lujvo v1 is a cigarette/cigar smoker; v1 smokes cigarettes/cigars. Cf. sigja, vasxu. See also tankyva'u, damva'u, marnyva'u.
gismu rafsi: sik x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of silk produced by x2. See also curnu, bukpu, cilta.
gismu x1 is a portion/quantity of salt from source x2, of composition including x3. See also sakta.
lujvo x1 trades places with x2 in circumstance x3. See also simxu, basti, basysi'u
lujvo x1 interchanges x2 and x3 in circumstance x4. See also simbasti, gasnu
lujvo s1=b1 (mass/set) integrate / unite with each other, displaying quality s2. Cf. simxu, jmaji, jorne.
lujvo x1 fight [each other] over issue x2 (abstract). Cf. simxu, damba, da'arsi'u, da'asnu, dausnu.
fu'ivla x1 is symphony number x2 key x3 composed by x4 performed by/at x5 (event). Cf. zgike, nolzgi, simfoni zei pagbu, konceto, zgifi'i.
lujvo p1 is a movement of symphony number k3 in key k4 composed by k5. Cf. simfoni, pagbu, zgike, nolzgi.

gismu rafsi: mlu x1 seems/appears to have property(ies) x2 to observer x3 under conditions x4. Also: x1 seems like it has x2 to x3; suggest belief/observation (= mlugau, mluti'i); looks like/resembles (= smimlu, mitmlu). See also catlu, viska, simsa, zgana, ganse, jarco.
lujvo x1 make up/peace with each other under condition x2. Cf. simxu, panpi, binxo, papsimbi'o.
lujvo x1 are friends [of each other]. Cf. simxu, pendo.

gismu rafsi: smi x1 is similar/parallel to x2 in property/quantity x3 (ka/ni); x1 looks/appears like x2. Also: x1 is a likeness/image of x2; x1 and x2 are alike; similarity and parallel differ primarily in emphasis. See also dunli, frica, mintu, panra, simlu, vrici.
fu'ivla x1 is sesame of species/variety x2. syn. xonxoli, jerjelino
lujvo x1 is the sum of all of x2 added together. See also sujysi'u
lujvo x1 rubs x2 together. Cf. simxu, mosra, gasnu, termosygau.

gismu rafsi: sim si'u x1 (set) has members who mutually/reciprocally x2 (event [x1 should be reflexive in 1+ sumti]). Members of x1 do to each other/one another x2, and in return do x2; x1 (plural set) do the same thing x2 to each other. See also kampu, mintu.
gismu x1 is a snake/serpent of species/breed x2. See also curnu, danlu, respa, vindu.
lujvo x1 is an eel of species x2. syn. angila

gismu rafsi: si'a x1 esteems/respects/venerates/highly regards x2 [object of respect]. Also: x2 is respected/esteemed/celebrated (= selsi'a for reordered places). See also banli, censa, misno, nelci, prami, salci, jgira.
gismu x1 is the trigonometric sine of angle/arcsine x2. See also tanjo.

gismu rafsi: sni x1 is a sign/symbol/signal representing/referring/signifying/meaning x2 to observer x3. Also: x1 signifies x2; (adjective:) x1 is significant/meaningful/of import; signal an action (= sniti'i), connotation (= se sibyti'isni, sibyti'ismu). See also lerfu, tcita, barna, mifra, smuni.
gismu rafsi: sip x1 is asleep (adjective); x1 sleeps/is sleeping. See also senva, tatpi, cikna, sanji.
lujvo sa1 sings lullaby sa2 to sa3=si1. Cf. sipna, sanga, sipselsa'a.
lujvo g1=s1 snores. Cf. sipna, savru, gasnu, zbisnava'u.
lujvo sa2 is a lullaby sung by sa1 to sa3=si1. Cf. sipna, sanga, sipsa'a.
lujvo x1 is a dormouse of species x2.
lujvo t1=s1 is sleepy; t1=s1 needs/wants sleep. Cf. sipna, tatpi, sipydji.
lujvo d1=s1 is drowsy/sleepy. Cf. sipna, djica, tatpi, sipta'i.
gismu rafsi: sir x1 is straight/direct/line segment/interval between x2 and x3; (adjective:) x1 is linear. See also korcu, linji, kruvi, kuspe.
lujvo x1 is is a quantity of/made from/consists of fur of animal/species/source x2.
gismu rafsi: six x1 reflects Syrian culture/nationality in aspect x2. See also xrabo.

gismu rafsi: sis x1 seeks/searches/looks for property x2 among set x3 (complete specification of set). If searching for an object or an event, use tu'a in x2. See also cirko, kalte, kavbu, kucli, rivbi, manci, facki.
lujvo s1=p1 finds s2=p2 at/in location p3. Cf. sisku, penmi, facki.
gismu rafsi: sti x1 [agent] ceases/stops/halts/ends activity/process/state x2 [not necessarily completing it]. See also fanmo, mulno, cfari, denpa, fliba.
gismu rafsi: sit x1 cites/quotes/refers to/makes reference to source x2 for information/statement x3 (du'u). See also krasi.
lujvo c1=s1 cites/quotes c2=s3 (sedu'u/text/lu'e concept) to audience c3 via expressive medium c4 from source _s2. Cf. sitna, cusku.

gismu rafsi: siv x1 is private/personal/privy/[secret/confidential/confined] to x2; x1 is not-public/hidden. Also: x1 is secret (one sense); x2 is in the know/in touch with/privy to x1 (= selsivni for reordered places); exclusion can be expressed by na'e(bo) in x2: excluded/in the dark (= nalselsivni). See also gubni, mipri.
lujvo c1 is capitalism as practiced by p1=s2 From sivni, ponse, ciste. Cf. guntrusi'o, fairpaltrusi'o.

gismu x1 is a skirt/kilt/dress of material x2; x1 is skirted [garment open at the bottom; not legged]. A skirted garment may be full length (pastu), but must hang below the waist from support above or at the waist. See also taxfu, palku.
gismu rafsi: sam x1 is a computer for purpose x2. See also kanji, minji, pensi.
gismu rafsi: kap x1 is a pelt/skin/hide/leather from x2. See also pilka, calku, kerfa.

gismu rafsi: ska x1 is/appears to be of color/hue x2 as perceived/seen by x3 under conditions x4. Conditions may include lighting, background, etc.. See also blanu, bunre, cicna, cinta, crino, grusi, narju, nukni, pelxu, xunre, zirpu, carmi, kandi, xekri, blabi.
lujvo c1 is science/technology-oriented science fiction about plot/theme/subject c2 by author c3, based on science s1. Also known as ``hard science fiction''.
lujvo z1 is an engineer in the branch of s2 based on methodology s3 with purpose/goal z3 from saske zukte c.f. mi'ircikre
gismu rafsi: ski x1 tells about/describes x2 (object/event/state) to audience x3 with description x4 (property). See also lisri, tavla.
gismu rafsi: sij x1 is a ski/skid/skate/runner for surface (of material) x2 supporting skier/skater/sled/cargo x3. See also sakli, marce, cutci.

gismu rafsi: kin x1 is a cinema/movie/film about x2 [plot/theme/subject/activity], filmmaker x3, for audience x4. Also motion picture; x2 may be a convention rather than a subject; cartoon/animation (= selxraci'a skina); television/tv show (= tivyskina, regardless of length, factual content, etc.). See also tivni, vidni, pixra, finti.
lujvo m1 is an aerial tramway carrying m2 in/on lift m3, propelled by m4=s1. Cf. marce, benji.
fu'ivla s1 is a mackerel of species s2. cf. finpe, finprtuna
fu'ivla x1 has scurvy with symptoms x2. see also nimre
gismu rafsi: sko x1 is cord/cable/rope/line/twine/cordage/woven strands of material x2. See also cilta, jgena, marna, bikla, linsi.
lujvo x1 is a vine of genus/species/variety x2. see also vanjba

gismu rafsi: kot ko'o x1 reflects Gaelic/Scottish culture/nationality/language in aspect x2. Irish (= sicko'o), Scottish (= sunko'o), Celtic (= dzeko'o), Welsh (= nanko'o), Breton (= fasko'o); since Scottish/Gaelic is only the northern branch of the Celtic tribes, many would prefer a fu'ivla for Celtic; nationalism might also demand a separate fu'ivla for Irish. See also brito, glico.
lujvo x1 is metalinguistic with respect to the expression by x2 of text x3 for audience x4 via medium x5 . See also cusku, bancu, sei, sa'a
lujvo d1 means/intends to say c2 to c3 via medium c4.
lujvo m1=c1 expresses/states an order to m2=c3 for m3 (event/state) to happen. Cf. cusku, minde, mi'esku.
gismu rafsi: ku'o x1 is a groove/trench/furrow [shape/form] in object/surface x2. See also plixa.
lujvo t1 is a manner of expression of c1, saying c2 to c3 via medium c4 under conditions t3.

gismu rafsi: sau x1 is old/familiar/well-known to observer x2 in feature x3 (ka) by standard x4. This can cover both meanings of old. Old in years, i.e. age, can be conveyed through x2 = the world, life, existence (= loi nu zasti); in usage this has been a common default for ellipsis. However slabu is not the opposite of 'young' (= nalci'o, tolci'o), but the opposite of 'new' (= tolni'o); also ancient (= tcesau), age (= nilsau); x2 is used to x1 (= selsau for reordered places); historic/historical (= cirsau, cirselcedra; also vaipru). (cf. clani, citno, cnino, se djuno; not the opposite of citno, djuno)
gismu x1 is a syllable in language x2. See also sance, valsi, bangu.
gismu x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of acid of composition x2; (adjective:) x1 is acidic. x2: composition including x2, which need not be complete specification. See also slari, nimre.
lujvo g1 pickles st1 with acid sl1 See also: slami (vinegar)
gismu x1 is a cylinder [shape/form] of material x2. See also kamju, gunro.
lujvo x1 is a tower for purpose x2. Also means "rook" in chess.
gismu rafsi: sar x1 is sour/tart to observer x2. See also slami, titla, kurki, nimre.
gismu rafsi: las x1 is a quantity of/is made of/contains plastic/polymer of type/component unit(s) x2. See also rutni, boxfo, bukpu.
lujvo x1 is a nucleus of cell x2 [default biological]. See also selci, ratmidju.
lujvo s1=c1 is a cradle made of c2, holding c3, rocking at speed s2 through positions s3. See also vercka.
lujvo g1 swings s1. Cf. slilu, desku.
gismu rafsi: lig x1 is solid, of composition/material including x2, under conditions x3. Conditions include temperature and pressure. See also runta, litki, gapci, jdari, dunja, pulce, jduli.

gismu rafsi: sli x1 oscillates at rate/frequency x2 through set/sequence-of-states x3 (complete specification). Also (expressible either with desku or slilu): side to side, to and fro, back and forth, reciprocal (motion), rotates, revolves. See also dikni, rilti, morna, desku, janbe, boxna.
gismu x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of sulfur/brimstone (S); [metaphor: foul odor, volcanic]. See also xukmi, panci, pelxu.
lujvo x1 is golden/gold-colored when viewed by x2 under conditions x3. Cf. solji, skari, rijyska.
fu'ivla x1 is Slovenian/Slovene in aspect x2. see also nanslovo, slovo, slovako
gismu rafsi: lov lo'o x1 reflects Slavic language/culture/ethos in aspect x2. See also softo, rusko, vukro.
gismu rafsi: slu x1 is a/the muscle [body-part] controlling x2, of body x3; [metaphor: tools of physical power]. (adjective:) x1/x2/x3 is muscular (different senses). See also rectu, xadni, zajba.
gismu x1 is a quantity of/contains onions/scallions of type/cultivar x2. See also stagi.
lujvo c1 is calm about x2=c3. Cf. caucni, seicni, sivycni.
fu'ivla x1 is a guinea pig of species x2. From rodent species 'Cavia cobaya'.
gismu x1 is a mouse of species/breed x2. See also ratcu.

gismu x1 guesses/conjectures/surmises x2 (du'u) is true about subject x3; [epistemology]. Also: x1 has a hunch that x2 is true; x1 imagines x2 is true; words usable for epistemology typically have a du'u place. See also djuno, facki, jijnu, sruma.
gismu rafsi: sma x1 (source) is quiet/silent/[still] at observation point x2 by standard x3. See also kerlo, panpi, savru, tirna.
gismu x1 is a monkey/ape/simian/baboon/chimpanzee of species/breed x2. See also mabru, danlu.
lujvo v1=jt1=s1 is SIV [Simian immunodeficiency virus] of jt2. From smani, jinkytoldu'e, vidru. s2, v2 and v3 subsumed.
cmene v1=jt1=r1 is SIV [simian immunodeficiency virus] of jt2. From smani, jinkytoldu'e, vidru. v2, v3 and s2 subsumed. See also HIV (=re'ajinkytoldu'evir).
lujvo c1 whispers c2=s1 (sedu'u/text/lu'e concept) to audience c3 via expressive medium c4, quietly by standard s3 Cf. smaba'u, lausku, laurba'u, mliba'u, laurblesku.
lujvo siml1=sims1 resembles/looks like/appears to be similar/parallel to sims2 in property/quantity sims3 to observer siml3 under conditions siml4
gismu rafsi: smo x1 is a sock/stocking [flexible foot and lower leg garment] of material x2. See also cutci, taxfu.
gismu rafsi: muc x1 is a spoon/scoop (tool) for use x2, made of material x3. See also dakfu, forca, tutci.
lujvo d1 and d2=s2 antonyms of each other. Cf. smuni, dukti.
lujvo g1 refers to s1 with expression s2 recognized by s3. Cf. cusku.
gismu rafsi: mun smu x1 is a meaning/interpretation of x2 recognized/seen/accepted by x3. Referential meaning (=selsni, snismu). See also jimpe, sinxa, valsi, tanru, gismu, lujvo, cmavo, jufra.
lujvo sa1 is semantics with methodology sa3.
lujvo v1 is the context of meaning v2=s1 of event/action/object s2 recognized by s3. Cf. smuni, vanbi, jimpe, sinxa.

gismu rafsi: sad x1 [agent] succeeds in/achieves/completes/accomplishes x2 as a result of effort/attempt/try x3. Also: x1 reaches x2; (adjective:) x1 is successful; x2 (event/state/achievement). See also fliba, troci, jgira.
lujvo d1 knocks on/hits door/object d2 with instrument [or body-part] d3 making sound s1
gismu rafsi: nan x1 is to the south/southern side of x2 according to frame of reference x3. See also berti, stuna, stici, farna.
fu'ivla x1 is mustard of species/breed x2. Cf. armoraki, kobli, cpinytsapi, sansrmustardo, koblrsinapi.
lujvo x1 is a sound/acoustic signal, produced/emitted by x2 and meaning x3 to x4 (listener).
lujvo v1 is a sound recording of v2 (data/facts/du'u) about v3 on recording medium v4.
lujvo t1 is a microphone for recording sound s1 produced/emitted by s2. Cf. dicyselsna, cukmirvelvei, srimakyvelvei, cukyku'ovelvei.
lujvo x1 is a dreamcatcher, passing dreams x2, stopping dreams x3, with netting properties x4.
lujvo x1 is a variable taking value x2 under conditions x3. See also sinxa, cenba
fu'ivla x1 is a jellyfish/jelly/sea jelly/member of phylum Cnidaria of species/breed x2. See also jdufi'e.

gismu rafsi: nid x1 is x2 seconds in duration (default is 1 second) by standard x3. See also cacra, junla, mentu, tcika, centi, decti, dekto, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, xexso, zepti, zetro.
lujvo x1 assigns symbol/variable x2 to value/referent x3 for observer x4. See also sinxa, gasnu
lujvo x1 is an ideogram/symbol in writing system x2 meaning x3. see also jugle'u, misryle'u
gismu rafsi: si'e x1 is made of/contains/is a quantity/expanse of snow. See also bratu, carvi, bisli.
gismu rafsi: nip x1 adheres/sticks to x2; (adjective:) x1 is sticky/gummy/adhesive. Note that x1 is the adhering surface being claimed; x2 need not be sticky. See also tarla, viknu.
lujvo x1 is the sigma summation of expression x2 with variable x3 over domain x4. See also si'i
lujvo c1 fades from location c2 c.f. masno canci
lujvo m1 is a sloth of genus/species m2.
gismu rafsi: nuj x1 is a sandwich/layering [not restricted to food] of x2 sandwiched between x3. See also midju, nenri, sepli, senta, jbini, bitmu, sruri.
lujvo k1 is a [shared journal]/blog about topic/subject k2=c2 published/administered by k3 for participants/audience k4=c1. Cf. casnu, karni, snustu, kibykarni.
gismu rafsi: nur nu'a x1 is secure/safe from threat x2 (event). See also ckape, kajde, marbi, terpa, xalni, bandu.
lujvo s1 is a forum for c1 to discuss/talk about topic/subject c2. Cf. casnu, stuzi, snukarni, kibykarni.
gismu rafsi: nut x1 (event/state) is an accident/unintentional on the part of x2; x1 is an accident. See also zukte, cunso.
cmavo rafsi: soj PA4 digit/number: almost all (digit/number).
cmavo cluster ROI* tense interval modifier: usually; objectively quantified tense; defaults as time tense.
cmavo rafsi: sor so'i PA4 digit/number: many.
cmavo cluster MOI* quantified selbri: convert many to cardinal; x1 is a set with many members x2 of total set x3.
cmavo cluster ROI* tense interval modifier: many times; objective tense; defaults as time tense.
cmavo cluster ROI* tense interval modifier: a few times; objective tense; defaults as time tense.
gismu rafsi: sob so'e x1 is a quantity of soya [grain/bean] of species/strain x2. See also dembi, gurni.
lujvo sa1 is soy sauce for use with sa2, containing ingredients including sa3. Cf. kukfusra, tsapi, silna, furfipsanso.
gismu x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of alkali metal of type x2 [default sodium]. Also potassium, lithium, cesium. Soda. See also jilka, jinme.

gismu rafsi: sod x1 is made of/contains/is a quantity of a carbonated beverage/soda of flavor/brand x2. Also: soft drink (though this sometimes includes tea and coffee as distinct from alcoholic beverages which are "hard drinks"). See also jilka, jinme.
gismu rafsi: sof x1 reflects Russian empire/USSR/ex-USSR (Soviet]/CIS culture/nationality in aspect x2. See also rusko, vukro, slovo.

lujvo Nonce word; no clear meaning. Something like x1 is a Soviet cow of species / breed x2. Was created for the pangram (sentence that contains all letters of the alphabet) ".o'i mu xagji sofybakni cu zvati le purdi". Made from softo + bakni.
lujvo x1 is USSR (Soviet Union) Cf. gugdesu'u, softo, sesre, rukygu'e, gugderu'u, sesrygugde
cmavo SOI discursive: reciprocal sumti marker; indicates a reciprocal relationship between sumti.
lujvo sa1 is a field ration consisting of dishes including sa2, for so1 of army so2. Cf. sonci, sanmi, bilni, jenmi, fatri, pagbu
lujvo p1 expects p2 (event); p1 expects p2 to happen. p2 is likely. It has high probability. Cf. pacna, sorpa'a, sotpa'a.
cmavo cluster PA* number/quantity: 9,000 expressed with comma.
gismu rafsi: slo x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of gold (Au); [metaphor: valuable, heavy, non-reactive]. See also ricfu, rijno, narju, pelxu.
lujvo x1 is x2 (default 1) Astronomical Unit(s) (AU) from solri minli c.f. gusminli tanminli.
lujvo x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of helium (He). See also solri, navni

gismu rafsi: sol x1 is the sun of home planet x2 (default Earth) of race x3; (adjective:) x1 is solar. 'home planet' refers to a planet which is "home" to a race, but not necessarily the original "home" of a species if that species inhabits many worlds. See also gusni, lunra, mluni, plini, santa, terdi, tarci.
lujvo x1 is a sunflower of species/variety x2.
gismu rafsi: som so'o x1 sows/plants x2 [crop/plants] at/in x3. See also crepu, tsiju.
cmavo cluster MOI* quantified selbri: convert 9 to ordinal selbri; x1 is ninth among x2 ordered by rule x3.
gismu rafsi: son soi x1 is a soldier/warrior/fighter of army x2. See also bilni, damba, jenmi, xarci, pulji.
lujvo x1 is an army battalion, a subdivision of army unit x2 which serves country/nation/group x3. Cf. sonci, girzu, songripau, songripausle, jempausle.
lujvo x1 is an army company, a subdivision of army unit x2 which serves country/nation/group x3. Cf. sonci, girzu, pagbu, songri, songripausle, jempausle.
lujvo x1 is an army platoon, a subdivision of army unit x2 which serves country/nation/group x3. Cf. sonci, girzu, pagbu, selci, songri, songripau, jempausle.
lujvo k1 is an armoured personnel carrier propelled by k3. Cf. sonci, jamna, karce, jamkarce, gutyjamkarce, xiljamkarce, tsakarce, karcycelxa'i.
lujvo n1 is liked by most people. Cf. so'e, nelci, misno, selzaumi'o.
lujvo z1=n2 is pop music produced/performed at/by z2 (event). Cf. so'e, nelci, zgike, dja'aza, te'ekno, naizgi, nolzgi.
lujvo c1 is a polyglot, proficient in languages c2=b1. Cf. baucre.

lujvo x1=c1=p1 is sexually polyamorous/sexually loves many people/more than one person including, but not limited to, set x2=p2 in situation/activity/state x3=c2, exhibiting sexuality/gender/sexual orientation (ka) x4=c3 by standard x5=c4. Leaving in all the places of cinse doesn't do much, but it probably doesn't hurt. See also cinse, prami, so'i, sorpa'i.

gismu rafsi: soc sro x1 is a store/deposit/supply/reserve of materials/energy x2 in containment x3. x3 need not be a container, but could merely be a site/location restriction; e.g. a heap. The sumti indicates how the supply is identified and distinguished from other occurrences of the stored x2 that are not part of the store. (cf. panka; vreji for information storage; sabji for a store or reserve that is not necessarily tied to a site, banxa, panka)
gismu rafsi: sog x1 is a quantity of sorghum of species/strain x2. See also gurni.
lujvo j1 is an empire govening over g1 provinces with j2=g3 territories. Made out of so'i, gugde, jecta
lujvo k1 is a multiple rocket launcher propelled by k3. Cf. so'i, jakne, karce, janjaknyxa'i, xumjimcelxa'i, gutyjamkarce, karcycelxa'i.
lujvo t1 is a web-shape, manifested by t2.
lujvo n1 is an international group of peoples n2. from so'i natmi
lujvo p1 hopes for p2 (event); p1 hopes that p2 happens. p2 is possible and has medium probability. Cf. pacna, sotpa'a, sojypa'a.

lujvo x1=p1 is polyamorous/loves many people (romantic love implied), including, but not limited to, set x2=p2. Romantic love, is, I suppose, not absolutely necessary, but seems likely. See also prami, so'i, sorcinpa'i.
fu'ivla x1 is a bus/coach for carrying passengers x2, propelled by x3 This is a zi'evla of the word sorprekarce.
lujvo k1 is a bus/coach for carrying passengers p1=k2, propelled by k3. Cf. karce, marce, tcana, klama
lujvo t1 is a bus terminal/station/depot in transport system t2 for buses for carrying p1=k2 from sorprekarce tcana.
lujvo c2 believes in many gods/deities c1 with dominion over c3; c2 is a polytheist. Cf. cevni, ceikri, nalceikri, selcei, pavyselcei, nonselcei, ceirsenpi.

lujvo d1 is a dormitory (building/place) where people x2 (complete mass) sleep. x1 is from dinju and x2 is invented but related to sipna1. x2 should be used for all the people; e.g. "mi se sorsipydi'u" incorrect speaking for yourself.
lujvo t1 is a constellation of stars Cf. so'o, tarci, tarmi, tartai, tarso'imei, tarci'e, tarboi, cacryra'o.
lujvo x1 is a hamlet/settlement with inhabitants x2 from so'o zdani c.f. cmatca
lujvo p1 wishes for p2 (event); p1 wishes that p2 happened. p2 is unlikely. It has low probability. Cf. pacna, sorpa'a, sojypa'a.

gismu rafsi: sov so'a x1 is an egg/ovum/sperm/pollen/gamete of/from organism [mother/father] x2. (poorly metaphorical only due to gender- and species- being unspecified): ovoid, oblate (= pevyso'aseltai, but better: claboi); egg, specifically female (= fetso'a), of a bird (= cpifetso'a, cpiso'a), of a chicken (= jipcyfetso'a, jipcyso'a. (but note that Lojban does not require specificity, just as English doesn't for either milk or eggs; "sovda" is fine for most contexts); If fertilized, then tsiju or tarbi. (cf. ganti, gutra, mamta, patfu, rorci, tsiju, lanbi, tarbi; also djine, konju for shape, tarbi)
cmene x1 is Soviet. Cf. sesre, softo, gugdesu'u
lujvo k1 is made of/contains a quantity of custard. Cf. sovda, kruji.

lujvo j1 has the rank of General/Admiral/Air Chief Marshal (equivalent of NATO OF-9) in military unit /organization j2. Cf. so, moi, jatna, jemja'a, vairsoi, pavnonmoija'a, bivmoija'a. Based on STANAG 2116: NATO Codes for Grades of Military Personnel.
lujvo x1 is September/the ninth month of year x2 in calendar x3. Cf. pavmasti, nanca.
lujvo b1 is a hedge separating b2 and b3 in b4 made of plants of species s2. Cf. spati, bitmu.
lujvo x1 is an aphid of genus/species x2.
gismu rafsi: paj x1 (event/action abstract) surprises/startles/is unexpected [and generally sudden] to x2. Also expectation (= nalspaji), alarm (= tepspaji). See also manci, jenca, bredi, suksa.
gismu x1 (agent) polishes object/surface x2 with polish x3, applied using tool x4. See also mosra, sraku, xutla.

gismu rafsi: san x1 reflects Spanish-speaking culture/nationality/language in aspect x2. Metaphorical restriction to Spain by contrast with xispo (comparable to the distinction between glico and merko/sralo/brito/kadno); Spain (= sangu'e); Spanish dialects spoken in Spain, especially Castillian (= sansanbau). See also xispo, ketco, mexno, gento.
fu'ivla x1 is a quantity of asparagus of species/strain x2
lujvo sa1 is botany concerned with plants of type sp2 based on methodology sa3. Cf. mivyske, dalske.

gismu rafsi: spa x1 is a plant/herb/greenery of species/strain/cultivar x2. Also (adjective:) x1 is vegetable/vegetal/vegetative. See also genja, grute, gurni, latna, rozgu, stagi, tricu, tsiju, tujli, xruba, xrula, pezli, srasu.
fu'ivla x1 is a radish (plant) of variety x2 from spati and 'Rapharus sativus' c.f. stagnrafanu
fu'ivla x1 is basil of variety x2. syn. alba'aka
fu'ivla x1 is Queen Anne's lace of species x2. See also gejrdauko, rulsantyspa.
fu'ivla x1 is a camomile plant of species/strain/cultivar x2. Cf. spati.
fu'ivla x1 is a water chestnut (plant) of species/variety x2. see also stagrleoxari
fu'ivla x1 is a cashew/mango/poison ivy/sumac of genus/species x2; x1 belongs to the Anacardiaceae.
fu'ivla x1 is pepper (''Piper'') of species/variety x2. see also kapsiku, tsaprpiperi
fu'ivla x1 is a quantity of witch-hazel/hamamelis/winterbloom of species/strain x2
fu'ivla x1 is a celery plant of species/variety x2. Cf. ampigravle, gejrdauko, najgenja, rulsantyspa, stagi.
fu'ivla x1 reflects Esperanto culture/nationality/language in aspect x2. Cf. pa'arbau. No corresponding nation exists at the moment.
lujvo x1 marries x2 according to marriage traditions/custom/law x3.
lujvo r1 is a wedding ceremony marrying x2=s1 to x3=s2. Cf. detke'u, jbedetnunsla.
lujvo m1=s1 is a concubine/lesser spouse of s2 under law/custom/convention s3. Cf. speni, mleca.
gismu rafsi: spe x1 is married to x2; x1 is a spouse of x2 under law/custom/tradition/system/convention x3. See also prami, gletu.
lujvo x1=s1=n1 is engaged to x2=s2=n3 by law/convention x3=s3 See also: speni, nu'ospe, spesti, mrospe
fu'ivla x1 is a smelt of species x2. see finpe, salmone, merlanu
lujvo x1=sp1=st1 is divorced from x2=sp2 by law/convention x3=sp3 See also: speni, nu'ospe, mrospe
gismu rafsi: spi x1 [object/substance] is a piece/portion/lump/chunk/particle of x2 [substance]. See also pagbu.
gismu x1 is a hospital treating patient(s) x2 for condition/injuries/disease/illness x3. Hospice (a place where x2 of spita is lenu mrobi'o = mrospita). See also bilma, mikce.
fu'ivla x1 is a parrot of species/breed x2. Cf. cipni, cipnrlori.

gismu rafsi: pof po'u x1 is broken/inoperable/broken down/non-utile/not usable for function x2. Agentive break, cause to become inoperable (= pofygau, pofyzu'e); accidentally break, as a result of an event, non-agentive (= pofyja'e, nutpo'uja'e). See also daspo, katna, porpi, se xrani, cikre.
lujvo g1 destroys, using/through event d1, object/person d2. Made from daspo + gasnu.
gismu rafsi: poj po'a x1 bursts/explodes/violently breaks up/decomposes/combusts into pieces/energy/fragments x2. See also cecla, jakne, jbama.
lujvo sp1=st1 crushes/destroys by stomping sp2=st2 using limbs st3.
fu'ivla x1 reflects Esperanto language/culture/community in aspect x2. Cf. esperanton, bangepu'o.

gismu rafsi: spu x1 answers/replies to/responds to person/object/event/situation/stimulus x2 with response x3. x3 also answer/reply. If x2 is a person/object, it will usually require "tu'a" indicating that the reply/response is to that person/object doing something. "tu'a" may not be needed if the person/object itself is the stimulus, rather than something it is doing. See also cusku, preti, nabmi, danfu, frati, cpedu.
gismu rafsi: put pu'u x1 spits/expectorates x2 [predominantly liquid] from x3 to/onto x4. Saliva/spit/sputum/spittle (= molselpu'u). See also jetce, kafke, vamtu.
gismu rafsi: raj x1 is vertical/upright/erect/plumb/oriented straight up and down in reference frame/gravity x2. See also sanli, pinta.

gismu rafsi: rak x1 [abrasive/cutting/scratching object/implement] scratches/[carves]/erodes/cuts [into] x2. (cf. guska, katna, mosra, plixa, kakpa (unlike kakpa, sraku does not imply material is removed), spali)
gismu x1 reflects Australian culture/nationality/geography/dialect in aspect x2. See also glico.
lujvo s1=b1 is the Australian English language used by b2 to express/communicate b3 (si'o/du'u, not quote). Cf. sralo, bangu, glibau, bangenugu.
lujvo s1=g1 is Australia from sralo gugde c.f. sralytu'a
lujvo s1=t1 is Australia/Oceania/Australasia from sralo tumla c.f.zdotu'a rontu'a tcotu'a bemtu'a frikytu'a ziptu'a

gismu rafsi: ra'a x1 pertains to/is germane/relevant to/concerns/is related/associated with/is about x2. Also: x1 is a question of/treats of x2; can be symmetric, although x1 is conventionally more specific or constrained in scope than x2. See also cmavo list ra'a, ckini, ponse, steci.
gismu rafsi: sas x1 is a blade/expanse of grass of species x2. Lawn/meadow (= sasfoi). See also spati.
lujvo bi1=ba2 is allergic to ba3 with symptoms bi2. Cf. bi'agla, bifce, plise, mlatu, derdembi, nimre.
lujvo x1 erroneously defends x2 against x3; x2 is allergic to x3. Cf. srebadbi'a, urci.
gismu rafsi: sre x1 errs in doing/being/making mistake x2 (event), an error under conditions x3 by standard x4. (cf. drani, which is non-agentive, cfila, fliba)
lujvo d1=b1 is a stripe on surface b2 of material d2=b3 This could also be a striped pattern although srimo'a might be more suited to that.

lujvo v4=m1 is a magnetic tape/cassette storing v2 (data/facts/du'u) about v3 (object/event) in file(s) v1. Cf. vreji, datni, datnysri, veisri, skami, sance, zgike, vidni, skina, makyvelvei, cukmakyvelvei, cukmirvelvei, cukyku'ovelvei, snaveitci, dicyselsna.
gismu x1 reflects Sanskrit language/Sanskritic/Vedic culture/nationality in aspect x2. See also xindo, xurdo.

lujvo s1=b1 is a rib of s2=b2. During the development of mammalian embryos, fused-on remnants of ribs can be traced in neck vertebrae (cervical ribs) and sacral vertebrae. In reptiles, ribs sometimes occur in all vertebrae from the neck to the sacrum. Cf. bongu, cutne.
lujvo k1=s1 comes/goes to k2 from k2 around s2. Cf. sruri, klama.
gismu rafsi: ru'a x1 assumes/supposes that x2 (du'u) is true about subject x3; [epistemology]. Words usable for epistemology typically have a du'u place. See also smadi, birti.
lujvo m1 is an iris/diaphragm covering m2, made of m3.
lujvo m1=s1 orbits s2 in direction s3 using orbit m4. Cf. cmaplini, plinycma, mluni, ru'u, solri.
lujvo p1 puts/places p2 around s2. Cf. sruri, punji.

gismu rafsi: rur sru x1 encircles/encloses/is surrounding x2 in direction(s)/dimension(s)/plane x3. (jinsru =) x1 is a ring/belt/band/girdle around/circling/ringing x2 near total containment in some dimension(s). See also karli, senta, snuji, vanbi, se nenri, se jbini, bartu, djine.

lujvo t1=s1 is a scarf worn on body part t2=s2. Includes "neckscarf" (nebysruta'u), "headscarf" (sedysruta'u), and "waistscarf" (befsruta'u). Worn for warmth, cleanliness, fashion, or religious reasons. Cf. dasri.
gismu rafsi: sac x1 is honest/open/truthfully revealing to/candid/frank with x2 about matter/fact x3. Also straight, straight-forward. See also tcica, jetnu, jitfa, mipri.
lujvo g1 parks/moors/berths/anchors vehicle s1 at s2.

gismu x1 is the edible x2 portion of plant x3; x1 is a vegetable. Note that fruits and nuts are also vegetables; generally this word will be used for either the general category of edible plants, or for non-fruit vegetables (= nalrutstagi). See also grute, kobli, narge, sluni, spati, sunga, tamca.
fu'ivla x1 is a radish (root/bulb) of variety x2 from stagi and 'Rapharus sativus' c.f. spatnrafanu
fu'ivla x1 is a water chestnut (corm) of variety x2. see also spatrleoxari
lujvo c1 is a vegetarian that eats vegetables s3. Cf. stagi, citka, re'ucti, fi'ecti.

gismu rafsi: tak x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of ceramic made by x2, of composition x3, in form/shape x4. Made of baked clay or other non-metallic solid; x3: composition including x3, which need not be complete specification. See also kliti.
gismu rafsi: sta x1 remains/stays at/abides/lasts with x2. See also vitno, zasni, ralte, stodi, xabju, stuzi, renvi.
gismu x1 is a/the stalk/stem/trunk [body-part] of plant/species x2; [metaphor: main support]. See also tuple, mudri.
lujvo c1=s1 is a/the sprout/shoot of plant/species s2 by standard/norm c3. Cf. stani, cmalu, cmastani.
lujvo x1 is a quantity of rhubarb of species/strain x2. Cf. stani, xruba.
gismu rafsi: tap x1 steps/treads on/in surface x2 using limbs x3. See also bajra, plipe, cadzu, serti.
gismu x1 is a quantity of soup/stew/olla/olio [food] of ingredients including x2. x2 is in x1, an ingredient/part/component of x1. See also sanmi, mixre, salta, sanso.
gismu x1 has a talent/aptitude/innate skill for doing/being x2. See also jinzi, certu, rarna, larcu, kakne.
gismu rafsi: seb x1 feels frustration about x2 (abstraction). See also cinmo.

gismu rafsi: tec te'i x1 (ka) is specific/particular/specialized/[special]/a defining property of x2 among x3 (set). [x2 are members/individuals of a subset of x3; object whose association is specific/defining of a subset or individuals (= tecra'a, also cf. cmavo list po'e, [x2 is also special to x1]); also: especially/strongly/specifically associated]; (x3 is completely specified set)]; See also srana, se ponse, ckini, tcila, tutra.
gismu rafsi: sed x1 is a/the head [body-part] of x2; [metaphor: uppermost portion]. Skull (= sedbo'u). See also drudi, mebri, xedja, besna, flira, mapku.
gismu rafsi: tel x1 is a lock/seal of/on/for sealing x2 with/by locking mechanism x3. See also ckiku.
fu'ivla x1 is Stepmania Stepmania, the "Dance Dance Revolution"-style game for Windows/Mac/Linux.

gismu rafsi: te'o x1 is x2 steradian(s) [metric unit] in solid angle (default is 1) by standard x3. See also centi, decti, dekto, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, xexso, zepti, zetro.
gismu rafsi: sic x1 is to the west/western side of x2 according to frame of reference x3. See also stuna, berti, snanu, farna.

gismu rafsi: sid ti'i x1 (agent) suggests/proposes idea/action x2 to audience x3; x1 (event) inspires x2 in/among x3. Event which inspires/suggests/is suggestive (= faurti'i, sidyfau). See also cmavo list ti'i, tcica, xlura.

gismu rafsi: tik x1 (event) adjusts/regulates/changes x2 (ka/ni) in amount/degree x3. Non-resultative, causal change; agentive adjust (= tikygau, tikyzu'e). See also cenba which need not be causal, galfi which is causal and resultative, binxo which need not be causal but is resultative, zasni, stodi.
lujvo x1 is a cause with cease x2 with causation conditions x3.
gismu rafsi: tiz x1 is a chair/stool/seat/bench, a piece or portion of a piece of furniture intended for sitting. See also nilce, zutse, jubme, ckana.

gismu rafsi: sto x1 is constant/invariant/unchanging in property x2 (ka) in response to stimulus/conditions x3. Also stable/consistent/steadfast/firm/steady. See also cenba, stika, stali, vitno, manfo, zasni, tinsa, jdari.
lujvo g1 maintains/preserves/keeps up/conserves s1 in condition s2 (ka) under (external) conditions s3
lujvo n1=s1 is insatiable in property n2=s2 despite input n3=s3. Cf. nitcu, stodi, mansa, banzu.
fu'ivla x1 is an ostrich of subspecies x2.

lujvo c1 (quoted word(s)) is a/the place name [inherent/inalienable site/place/position/situation/spot/location] of c2=s1 to/used-by namer/name-user c3 (person). s2 is omitted. See also stuzi, cmene, stucmevla and stucmeske.
lujvo v1 is a word derived from place name/toponym c1 (quoted word(s)) meaning/causing v2 in language v3. See also stucme, cmevla, valsi.
lujvo d1 and d2=s2 are antipodes on s1. Cf. stuzi, dukti.
gismu rafsi: sun x1 is to the east/eastern side of x2 according to frame of reference x3. See also stici, berti, snanu, farna.
gismu rafsi: tur su'a x1 is a structure/arrangement/organization of x2 [set/system/complexity]. (x2, if a set, is completely specified); See also ganzu, morna, ciste, lujvo, greku, gerna.
lujvo p2=s1 is a piece of real estate possessed by p1 in condition p3. Cf. ponse, stuzi, tumla, zdani.

gismu rafsi: tuz stu x1 is an inherent/inalienable site/place/position/situation/spot/location of x2 (object/event). Generally used for normally stationary objects/events, to give their 'permanent' location. See also cmavo list tu'i, jmive, diklo, zvati, tcini, xabju, jibni, judri, lamji, mokca, stali.
cmavo SU erase to start of discourse or text; drop subject or start over.
cmavo UI2 evidential: I generalize - I particularize; discursive: abstractly - concretely. See also sucta, sucni'i.
cmavo cluster UI*2 evidential: I generalize - I particularize; discursive: abstractly - concretely.
cmavo rafsi: sup su'e PA4 digit/number: at most (all); no more than.
cmavo VUhU1 n-ary mathematical operator: plus; addition operator; [(((a + b) + c) + ...)].
cmavo rafsi: suz su'o PA4 digit/number: at least (some); no less than.
cmavo cluster MOI* quantified selbri: convert at least 2 to cardinal selbri; x1 is a set with plural membership x2.
cmavo cluster MOI* quantified selbri: convert at least 2 to ordinal selbri; x1 is at-least-2nd among x2 by rule x3.
cmavo rafsi: suv NU abstractor: generalized abstractor (how); x1 is [bridi] as a non-specific abstraction of type x2.
lujvo x1=k1 estimates numerical value x2=k3=s1 about x3=s2
gismu rafsi: suc x1 (si'o) is abstracted/generalized/idealized from x2 [something concrete] by rules x3. See also fatci, xanri.
gismu rafsi: sud x1 is dry of liquid x2; (adjective:) x1 is arid. See also cilmo, litki, runta.
lujvo g1 dries/dehydrates s1, removing liquid s2
lujvo z1=s1 is drier than z2 by amount z4 of liquid s2. Cf. sudga, zmadu, sudrai.
lujvo s1=n1 is a crouton of bread b1, made from grains b2.
lujvo t1=s1 is the driest among set/range t4 of liquid s2. Cf. sudga, traji, sudmau.
lujvo j1=v2=s1 is a raisin/sultana/currant processed from a grape of species j2. Cf. sudga, vanju, jbari.
lujvo t1=s1 is a desert with land location t2.
gismu rafsi: sfu x1 is a/the hoof [body-part] of x2. See also xirma.
lujvo x1 add up to x2. See also simsumji
gismu rafsi: suk x1 (event/state) is sudden/sharply changes at stage/point x2 in process/property/function x3. Also abrupt, discontinuous. See also spaji, vitci, vlile.
lujvo x1 is a sumti qualifier labelling sumti x2 with semantics x3. See also la'e, lu'e, tu'a, lu'a, lu'i, lu'o, vu'i; lu'u
gismu rafsi: suj x1 is a mathematical sum/result/total of x2 plus/increased by x3. See also jmina, jalge, mulno, pilji.
lujvo x1 is a pro-sumti/pronoun representing x2 as argument of predicate/function x3 filling place x4. See also sumti, krati
gismu x1 (experiencer) smells/scents (transitive verb) x2; x2 smells/has odor/scent to observer x1. See also nazbi, panci, cpina, ganse, zgana.
lujvo x1 is a termset/set of arguments of predicate/function x2 filling places x3. See also ce'e, nu'i
gismu rafsi: sum su'i x1 is a/the argument of predicate/function x2 filling place x3 (kind/number). (x1 and x2 are text); See also bridi, darlu, gismu.
gismu rafsi: sug x1 is a quantity of garlic [bulb] of species/strain x2. See also stagi.
lujvo s1 reflects Scottish culture/nationality/language in aspect s2.
gismu rafsi: sul x1 is a quantity of/made from/consists of wool [tight curly hair] from animal/species/source x2. See also kosta, kumte, lanme, kanba, bukpu, kerfa.
lujvo j1 is the longitude/right ascension of j2 in system j3 From stuna, stici, judri, Cf. bernanjudri, plinyxabykoi, jedjipli'i, julra'o, cacryra'o.
lujvo x1 is Orthodox Christian in aspect x2. Cf. xriso, stuna, glixi'o, patxi'o, la'orxi'o, lijda.
fu'ivla x1 is Finnish in aspect x2
lujvo x1 is the Sabbath, the day on which x2 rests. see also redgaudei, tedydei, trudei
lujvo x1=g1 relaxes x2=s1 by doing x3=g2=s2 cf. surla, gasnu
gismu rafsi: sur x1 relaxes/rests/is at ease in/by doing/being x2 (activity). See also dunku, tatpi, cando, vreta.
lujvo c1=s1 is fast/swift/quick/hastes/rapid at learning c2 (du'u) about subject c3 from source c4 (obj./event) by method c5 (event/process).
lujvo s1=k1 quickly comes/goes to destination k2 from origin k3 via route k4 using means/vehicle k5. See klama.
lujvo l1=s1 dashes/speeds/swiftly travels via route l2 using means/vehicle l3. see also: sutkla
gismu rafsi: sut x1 is fast/swift/quick/hastes/rapid at doing/being/bringing about x2 (event/state). See also masno.
lujvo x1 is a roadrunner of species x2. see also cipnrkuku
lujvo d1 is eager/impatient for d2=s2 to happen. Cf. sutra, djica, djicni.
lujvo g1 hurries/rushes/speeds s1 to do/be/bring about s2. Cf. sutra, gasnu, sutri'a, filgau, filri'a.
lujvo x1=sr1=t1=su1 makes mistake x2=sr2 under the conditions of speaking quickly to x3=t2 about subject x4=t3 in language x5=t4 by standard x6=sr4
lujvo z1=s1 accelerates/[speeds up] at doing/being/bringing about s2 (event/state) by amount z3. Cf. sutra, zenba.
lujvo j1 is a union or loose federation of sovereign states. Cf. su'o, gugde, jecta, balgu'e. Examples: United Nations (UN), European Union (EU), Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN).
lujvo x1=k3 is the relationship between x2=k1, x3=k2, x3...; x1 is a property of x2.
cmavo rafsi: taz KOhA6 pro-sumti: that there; nearby demonstrative it; indicated thing/place near listener.
lujvo s1 (set) discuss subject t2 in language t4. Cf. tavla, simxu, casnu.
cmavo TAhE tense interval modifier: habitually; subjective tense/modal; defaults as time tense.
cmavo cluster TAhE* tense interval modifier: non-habitually; subjective tense/modal; defaults as time tense.
cmavo BAI tadji modal, 1st place (in manner 3) methodically; by method ...
cmavo cluster BAI* sumti question asking for a method; how?.
lujvo v1=t1 yawns, expressing fatigue due to effort/situation t2 (event)
cmavo UI3 discursive: by the way - returning to main point. See also denpa, cneterta'a.
cmavo cluster UI*3 discursive: by the way - returning to main point.
lujvo x1 is a tablet computer for purpose x2 Cf. tanbo, skami, kibro, samvidni
cmavo UI3a discursive: making a tanru - expanding the tanru. See also tanru.
cmavo cluster UI*3a discursive: making a tanru - expanding the tanru.
lujvo x1 is a diamond (gem) from source x2. Cf. kunra, tabykrili.
gismu rafsi: tab x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of carbon/graphite/[diamond]/charcoal; x1 is organic. See also kolme.
gismu x1 is a horn/trumpet/trombone/bugle [brass-wind/lip-reed musical instrument]. See also zgike.
fu'ivla x1 is a trumpet. Cf. tabra, zgica'a.

lujvo j1=t1 is a/the horn [primitive type/predecessor of brass-wind/lip-reed musical instrument] cut from j2. tabryjirna is foremost a horn jirna rather than a brass instrument tabra, although it is used as a simple musical instrument. Don't to be mistaken for horn (brass instrument;=jirnytabra). x2 may be species or a specific animal. Swedish horn were usually made from cow or goat. The israelic shoar were usually made from sheep.
lujvo b1=t1 is charred/carbonized under conditions b3.
lujvo k1 is crystalline carbon (default diamond) in form/arrangement k3 from tabno krili c.f. jemna tabjme kunra

lujvo x1 is organic/carbon-based. organic applies to chemicals; carbon-based to life forms. The distinction between tabyselcmu and mivyselkra is that e.g. calcium phosphate in bones is mivyselkra but not tabyselcmu, while polyethylene is tabyselcmu but not mivyselkra.
lujvo x1=p1 (agent) touches eir tongue to/licks x2=p2=t2 at x3=p4 [a locus on x2]. t1 and p3 are implicitly the tongue of agent x1. See also pencu, tance.
lujvo g1 is a study group studying t2.

gismu x1 [process] is a method/technique/approach/means for doing x2 (event) under conditions x3. Also practice/way/mode; style/manner/conduct (= tratadji); pattern (= montadji, tadjymo'a, or platadji, tadjypla). See also ciste, pruce, zukte, pluta, cmavo list ta'i.
lujvo c1 adopts c2=t1 (method) for purpose t2.
gismu rafsi: tad x1 studies/is a student of x2; x1 is a scholar; (adjective:) x1 is scholarly. See also ckule, cilre, ctuca.
lujvo c1 is a washing machine. Cf. zbabu, paltylumca'a.
fu'ivla x1 is a chemise/shift/smock of material x2. Usually women's undergarments and dresses. cmeize for type 4. Cf. taxfu.

fu'ivla x1 is a jersey of material x2. Knitted clothing, traditionally in wool or cotton, with sleeves, worn as a pullover, as it does not open at the front, unlike a cardigan (tafrkardiga). Cf. taxfu.

fu'ivla x1 is a cardigan of material x2. A type of sweater (nivycreka) or jumper (luzbarcreka) that fastens up the front with buttons or a zipper, usually machine- or hand-knitted from wool. kardiga for type 4. Cf. creka.
lujvo tc1 is a clothing custom/fashion of tc2=ta1 under conditions tc3 (era/region/occasion).
lujvo f1 is a hole in garment x2=t1 for wearing by x3=t2 (gender/species/body part). Cf. bukfe'a.
gismu rafsi: tag x1 is snug/tight on x2 in dimension/direction x3 at locus x4. See also trati, jarki, kluza, rinju.
lujvo g1 tucks t1 onto/into t2. Cf. tagji, gasnu, polje, setca.
cmavo BAI tamsmi modal, 1st place (like)/(in manner 2) resembling ...; sharing ideal form ... tamsmi is x1 resembles x2 sharing ideal form/shape x3 in property x4
fu'ivla b1=c1 is a typhoon/hurricane/cyclone moving from direction b2 at speed b3 rotating around centre /eye c2 with rotational direction c3. Cf. carbi'e, vilti'a.
lujvo m1=t2 is a t1 form of m3
lujvo v1=t1 pants because of tiring effort/situation t2 (event). Cf. tatpi, vasxu.
lujvo x1 is the morphology of x2 according to methodology x3. see also rafske
lujvo g1 is a thimble. Cf. tamji, gacri, degygai.
fu'ivla x1 is a badger of species x2
gismu rafsi: tal x1 (person) challenges x2 at/in property x3. (cf. jinga, damba, darlu, jivna, nandu for a challenging event/situation)
gismu x1 is a tomato [fruit/vegetable/plant] of species/strain x2. See also grute, stagi.
lujvo g1 defines t2 into form t1. Cf. tarmi.

gismu rafsi: taj x1 is a/the thumb/big toe [body-part] on limb x2 of x3; [metaphor based on relative shape]. Thumb (specifically the hand = xantamji), big toe (= jmatamji). See also degji, tance, xance, jamfu.
lujvo x1 is a colobus of species x2. see also smani
gismu x1 is cousin to x2 by bond/tie x3; [non-immediate family member, default same generation]. Probably preferred for metaphorical siblings (over bruna). See also dzena, famti, mensi, bruna, tunba.
lujvo x1 has form x2, similar in form to x3 in property/quality x4.
lujvo p1=ti1 is a model/mannequin serving fashion/artistic/commercial concept ti2=ta1. Cf. tigni, tarmi, larcu, taxfu.
lujvo m1=t2 is a quantity of macaroni/penne/fusilli/shaped pasta in shape t1 made from grains m2. Cf. grusko, grupu'o.
lujvo b1 is a rainbow at location b2=t2.
gismu rafsi: ta'o x1 is a board/plank [3-dimensional long flat rectangle] of material x2. See also bliku, kubli.
gismu rafsi: tac x1 is a/the tongue [body-part] of x2; (metaphor: similar to nazbi, tamji, degji). (adjective:) x1 is lingual. See also moklu, bangu, nazbi, tamji, degji.
gismu x1 is the trigonometric tangent of angle/arctangent x2. See also sinso.
gismu x1 is a quantity of tobacco [leaf] of species/strain x2. See also sigja, marna.
lujvo xu1 is nicotine with chemical purity xu2.
lujvo x1 is x2 (default 1) parsec(s) from tsani minli c.f. gusminli solminli.
gismu rafsi: tau x1 is a binary metaphor formed with x2 modifying x3, giving meaning x4 in usage/instance x5. (x2 and x3 are both text or both si'o concept) See also gismu, smuni.

gismu rafsi: tas x1 is a pan/basin/tub/sink, a shallow container for contents x2, of material/properties x3. Also bowl. See also baktu, palne, palta, patxu, kabri for a bowl that is normally lifted for use, botpi.
lujvo t1=t1 is a skysurfingboard of material/property t2. From tanbo, tsani. See also si'erta'o, jacta'o, xilta'o
gismu rafsi: tax ta'e x1 is a box/carton/trunk/crate for contents x2, and made of material x3. See also bakfu, botpi, cutne, dacru.

gismu x1 is a tile/cake [shape/form] of material x2, shape x3, thickness x4. A tile is a 3-dimensional object, relatively uniform and significant in the 3rd dimension, but thin enough that its shape in the the other two dimensions is a significant feature; 'city block' is conceptually a tile; polygon (= taplytai or kardytai - shaped like an approximately-2-dimensional block, lijyclupa - a loop composed of lines). (cf. bliku, kubli, matci; karda, for which the 3rd dimension is insignificant, bliku, kurfa, matci, plita, tarmi)
lujvo si1 is a track of st1 treading on surface st2 using limb st3 from stapa sinxa
lujvo g1 is g2 pace/paces (length unit). Cf. stapa, gutci, degygutci, jmagutci, cibjmagutci, birgutci.
gismu x1 is an embryo/zygote/fetus/fertilized egg with mother x2, and father x3. See also gutra, mamta, patfu, sovda, rorci, tsiju, grute.
lujvo b1 is a globular cluster consisting of stars with properties t2. Cf. tarci, bolci, tarso'imei, tarci'e.

cmene x1 is Gemini [astronomical constellation/astrological sign]. From twin/triplet/quadruplet (=tarbykansa). In Babylonian astronomy these stars are known as the Great Twins and are in greece associated with the myth of Castor and Pollux.
lujvo s1 is the/a umbilical cord connecting t1=x2 to mother t2=x3. Cf. tarbi, skori
lujvo v1 performs abortion/induces delivery of embryo/zygote/fetus/fertilized egg t1=v2 on t2=v3. (The survival/death of t1=v2 is not implied.) Cf. tarbi, vimcu. Abortion/Inducement = nuntarbyvi'u.
gismu rafsi: tar x1 is a star/sun with stellar properties x2. See also solri, tsani.
lujvo c1 is a solar system based on star(s) t1 (default is the Solar System) with stellar properties t2 with components c3 displaying c4 (ka) Cf. tarci, ciste, tarso'imei, sostartai, tarboi.
lujvo x1 is stellar astronomy based on methodology x2. Cf. kesyske, tarske
fu'ivla x1 is dandelion of species x2.
gismu x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of tar/asphalt from source x2. See also kolme, pesxu, snipa.

gismu rafsi: tam tai x1 [ideal] is the conceptual shape/form of object/abstraction/manifestation x2 (object/abstract). Also pattern; x1 is the mathematical or theoretical ideal form, while x2 is an object/event manifesting that form; e.g. circular/circle-shaped (= cukseltai) vs. circle (=cuktai, while cukla alone is ambiguous); model (= ci'ersaptai, saptai, ci'ersmitai, smitai). See alse nejni, te marji for physical shape, tapla, bliku, kubli, kurfa, cukla, mapti, morna, sarlu.
fu'ivla x1 is a tarsier of species x2. see also smani
lujvo s1 is astronomy based on methodology s3. Cf. tarci, saske, mu'eske, termu'eske.
lujvo s1 is a/the galaxy (default is the Milky Way) Cf. tarci, so'imei, sostartai, tarboi, tarci'e.
lujvo tarm1 tartai tarc2. Cf. tarci, tarmi, sostartai, tarso'imei, tarci'e, tarboi, cacryra'o.
gismu rafsi: tra x1 behaves/conducts oneself as/in-manner x2 (event/property) under conditions x3. Also (adjective:) x1 is behavioral. See also cnano, frati, tcaci, cilce, jikca, marde.
gismu x1 thirsts for x2; x1 needs/wants drink/fluid/lubrication x2. See also nitcu, djica, xagji, pinxe.
gismu rafsi: ta'i x1 is tired/fatigued by effort/situation x2 (event); x1 needs/wants rest. See also cikna, sipna, surla.
gismu rafsi: tat x1 is a/the breast/mammary/teat [body-part] of x2; [metaphor: projection providing liquid]. Nipple (= tatyji'o). See also ladru, mabru.
lujvo b1=t1 gets tired from t2 (event). Cf. tatpi.

lujvo x1=d2 is a mastodon of species x2 The mastodon's English name (and former genus name) comes from "breast-tooth" due to the unusual shape of its molars. They are not in the same family as elephants or mammoths xantrmamutu.
lujvo t1=j1 a nipple/teat (mammary papilla) of t2. Cf. tatru.
lujvo tax1 is a bra with purpose tax2.
cmavo LAU 2-word letteral/shift: change case for next letteral only.

gismu rafsi: tav ta'a x1 talks/speaks to x2 about subject x3 in language x4. Not limited to vocal speech, but this is implied by the x4 without context of some other medium of conversation (use cusku, casnu, skicu, ciksi for weaker implication of vocal communication); converse/discuss/chat (= simta'a, simsku, vricysimta'a for a conversation not clearly delimited by subject). See also bacru, cusku for actual expression, casnu, darlu, skicu, ciksi, bangu.

fu'ivla x1 is a bikin/two piece skimpy woman's garment of material x2 consisting of top x3 and bottom x4 Can be used in the sense of swimwear, or coordinated underwear, or even skimpy outerwear. The key aspects are two piece, for women, and covering little more than the breasts and crotch.

gismu rafsi: taf ta'u x1 is dress/a garment/clothing for wearing by x2 (gender/species/body part) serving purpose x3. Also: x2 can wear/is wearing x1; refers to something intended for use as a garment, not merely something that happens to be worn at some time (which need not be true for dasni). See also creka, cutci, daski, dasni, gluta, kosta, mapku, palku, pastu, skaci, smoka, lunbe.
fu'ivla x1 is a jackfruit (Artocarpus heterophyllus) of breed x2 See tcempedake
lujvo b1 is the city/town hall of city/town t1 c.f. tcadu briju
gismu rafsi: cac x1 is a custom/habit/[ritual/rut] of x2 under conditions x3. Also: x1 is customary/usual/the practice. See also fadni, kampu, lakne, jinzi, ckaji, cnano, tarti, ritli, javni, zekri.
lujvo c1 is a pigeon of subspecies c2. Cf. tcadu, cipni, kolmba.
gismu rafsi: tca x1 is a town/city of metropolitan area x2, in political unit x3, serving hinterland/region x4. Also (adjective:) x1 is urban. See also jarbu, nurma, cecmu.
fu'ivla x1 is a jackal of species/breed x2. Cf. gerku, labno, lorxu, ko'otli.

gismu x1 is a station/node of/in/on transport/communication/distribution system/network x2. x2 may be represented by massed vehicles of system. See also dargu, litru, pluta, trene, ciste, ve mrilu, tivni, cradi, ve benji, fonxa, dikca, fatri.
fu'ivla x1 is sandalwood of species/variety x2.

lujvo x1=p1 is a network route/path to node x2=p2=t1 from node x3=p3=t1 via points/nodes x4=p4 within transport/communication/distribution system/network x5=t2. Unusual in that t1 appears more than once. x4 is also really a set of t1s. See also tcana, pluta
gismu x1 is made of/contains/is a quantity of tea brewed from leaves x2. See also ckafi.
lujvo tu1 is the mayor of tu2=tc1.
lujvo p1 is a tea tray made of p3. Cf. tcati, palne.
fu'ivla x1 is Czech in aspect x2. Cf. slovo, ropno, tcesk.
lujvo b1=m1 is huge/enormous/very big in property b2 with criterion b3.
lujvo g1 (person/agent) tortures/inflicts severe pain on x2=c1 at locus x3=c2. Cf. tikpa, tunta, katna, mi'arpe'u.
lujvo x1 (property - ka) is global among x2.
fu'ivla x1 is a cempedak (Artocarpus champeden) of breed x2 See tca'anka, zduriane
gismu rafsi: ten x1 stretches/extends to range x2 [interval/extent] in dimension x3 from relaxed range x4. See also kuspe, pruni, preja, ranji, trati.

lujvo x1 is an archaeon of species/defining property x2. The Archaea are a group of single-celled microorganisms. In the past they had been classed with bacteria as prokaryotes (=pruslemijyji'e) and named archaebacteria, but this classification is regarded as outdated. See also tcepru, jurme.
lujvo x1 is archeology of/about subject matter x2 based on methodology x3. From tcepru, saske. See also citri.
cmene Czech Republic. Cf. tce'exo, slovo, gugde.
lujvo x1 is an oscillate with oscillation state x2.
lujvo m1 is very much/very extreme in property m2 (ka), towards m3 extreme/direction. Differs from mutce only in intensity; add more "tce" to taste. Made from mutce + mutce.

gismu rafsi: tic x1 (event/experience) misleads/deceives/dupes/fools/cheats/tricks x2 into x3 (event/state). Agentive deception (= ticygau, ticyzu'e); x3 could be an action or a belief on the part of x2; harmful intent or result is not implied (= malticyzu'e for such harmful intent); self deception (= sezytcica); deceive/trick into misguided action (= ticyxlu); misguided belief (= tickri); fib/lie/tell an untruth/lie/fib (= ticysku, jifsku), white lie (= zanticysku). See also stace, xlura, stidi, kajde.
gismu rafsi: tid x1 [agent] reads x2 [text] from surface/document/reading material x3; x1 is a reader. See also ciska, cukta, karni.

gismu x1 [hours, minutes, seconds] is the time/hour of state/event x2 on day x3 at location x4. Also o'clock, time-of-day. (time units in x1 are specified as numbers separated by pi'e or are unit values massified with joi); See also cmavo list ti'u, cacra, cerni, detri, donri, djedi, junla, nicte, mentu, snidu, temci, vanci, dirba, mokca.
lujvo c1=t1 is practical, likely to be applicable to event c2=t2.
fu'ivla x1 is a stork of species/type x2 Genus Ciconia
lujvo x1 reschedules from time x2[hours, {minutes}, {seconds}] state/event x3 to time x4[hours, {minutes}, {seconds}]. Cf. tcika, galfi, tcikygau, detytcikygau, bavypunji, prupu'i.
lujvo g1 schedules time t1 [hours, {minutes}, {seconds}] for state/event t2 on day t3 at location t4. Cf. tcika, gasnu, detytcikygau, tcikyga'i, bavypunji, prupu'i.
gismu rafsi: til x1 is a detail/feature/particular of x2. See also diklo, steci.
gismu rafsi: tim ti'a x1 is weather at place/region x2; (adjective:) x1 is meteorological. Climate (= citsyti'a, timymo'a). See also brife, bumru, carvi, dilnu, bratu.
fu'ivla x1 is a chimpanzee of species/subspecies x2. Cf. jbonobo, smani.

gismu x1 [state/property] is a situation/condition/state/position/are conditions/circumstances of x2. Characteristics or environment of an object/event/process stage or state that are typically/potentially only temporary. See also stuzi, zvati, vanbi, ve pruce, ckaji, zasni.
gismu x1 is a label/tag of x2 showing information x3. See also sinxa, cmene, judri.
lujvo g1 puts a label t1 on t2 showing information t3. Cf. tcita, gasnu, ba'argau.
lujvo j4=t1 is a handle on object j2 with purpose t2. Cf. batke.
lujvo x1 is a llama/vicuña/alpaca/guanaco of species x2. Cf. kumte, zdokumte, rabykumte, kumtrvikunia, kumtrvalpaka, kumtrlama, kumtrguanako
lujvo k1=t1 is South America from ketco tumla c.f.zdotu'a rontu'a bemtu'a sralytu'a frikytu'a ziptu'a
lujvo x1 is a peccary of species x2. see also xarju
lujvo n1=j1 is a parasite on n2.
cmavo rafsi: ter SE 3rd conversion; switch 1st/3rd places.
cmavo VUhU2 binary mathematical operator: to the power; exponential; [a to the b power].
cmavo FAhA3 location tense relation/direction; edged by/edging up to ...
fu'ivla x1 is a form of techno music performed/created by x2 with characteristics x3. Cf. zgike, dja'aza, sopselneizgi, naizgi, nolzgi.
lujvo sk1 specifies sk2=st2 among st3 to audience sk3 as having property sk4=st1
cmavo TEhU elidable terminator: end conversion between non-mex and mex; usually elidable.
cmavo cluster BAI* bangu modal, 3rd place (expression) language expressing ...
cmavo cluster BAI* benji modal, 3rd place (source) sent to receiver ...
lujvo x1 is a plant of the mint family, of genus/species/variety x2. see also kurtsapi, spatrmenta
lujvo k1 is the moustache of k2=c2.
cmavo cluster BAI* catni modal, 3rd place authoritatively; with basis of authority ...
cmavo cluster BAI* ciste modal, 3rd place of system components ...
cmavo cluster BAI* cinmo modal, 3rd place (attitude about) emotionally; emoting about ...
cmavo cluster BAI* cusku modal, 3rd place (3rd party hearsay) as told to ...
lujvo j1 is particular/fastidious about j2=s1. Cf. jundi.
lujvo s1 is committed to s2 with service s3
lujvo v1 is a term/jargon (from a specialised area of knowledge) meaning v2=s2 in language v3. Cf. valsi, steci, bangu.
cmavo cluster BAI* detri modal, 3rd place on a date measured at location ...
cmavo cluster BAI* diklo modal, 3rd place locally; at specific locus within range ...
lujvo m1 surveys t1=m2 as m3 (map or measurements) in unit m4 with accuracy m5 see also tumymre
cmavo cluster BAI* dunli modal, 3rd place equally; equal in property ...
cmavo cluster BAI* djuno modal, 3rd place knowingly; knowing about ...
lujvo x1 is Saturday of week x2 on calendar x3.

lujvo s1=t1 is earth science [science about earth/soil] based on methodology s3. terdi2, terdi3 and saske2 subsumed. x1 is an all-embracing term for the sciences related to the planet Earth. It is arguably a special case in planetary science. Not limited to reductionistic science, but also embrace holistic views. See also derske.
cmavo cluster BAI* finti modal, 3rd place creatively; created for purpose ...
lujvo x1 is x2 times the x4th power of x3.
lujvo m1 is a polynomial in t2 of degree t3 interpreted by rules m2
cmavo cluster BAI* zgana modal, 3rd place observed by means ...
cmavo TEI composite letteral follows; used for multi-character letterals.
cmavo cluster BAI* javni modal, 3rd place orderly; by rule within system ...
cmavo cluster BAI* jimte modal, 3rd place limitedly; limited in property/domain ...
cmavo cluster BAI* jitro modal, 3rd place controlledly; controlling event ...
cmavo cluster BAI* klama modal, 3rd place with origin ...
cmavo cluster BAI* krati modal, 2nd place representingly; representing in matter...
cmavo cluster BAI* ckini modal, 3rd place with relation ...
cmavo cluster BAI* korbi modal, 3rd place (bounding) bordering ...
cmavo cluster BAI* klani modal, 3rd place quantity measured on scale ...
lujvo g1 unlocks/unseals c1=s2 using lock/seal s1 with mechnism s3. Cf. stela, claxu, gasnu, toltelgau, telga'o, ga'orgau.
cmavo cluster BAI* klesi modal, 3rd place (category) defined by quality ...
lujvo g1=s2 is locked, preventing access to g2 by g3, the lock being s1 using mechanism s3. Cf. stela, ganlo, telgau, ga'orgau.
lujvo g1 locks lock s1 on s2 by mechanism s3. Cf. stela, gasnu, telga'o, ga'orgau.
cmavo cluster BAI* lidne modal, 3rd place ordered within sequence ...; non-time sequence.
cmavo cluster BAI* marji modal, 3rd place in material form ...
cmavo cluster BAI* manri modal, 3rd place (of reference) observed/measured with/by rules ...
cmavo cluster BAI* zmadu modal, 3rd place (relative!) more than/exceeding in property ...

gismu rafsi: tem tei x1 is the time-duration/interval/period/[elapsed time] from time/event x2 to time/event x3. Also age/elapsed time (= niltei). See also cacra, cedra, citsi, ranji, tcika, junla, renvi.
cmavo cluster BAI* mleca modal, 3rd place (relative!) less than in property ...
cmavo cluster BAI* cmene modal, 3rd place as a name used by ...
lujvo f1 is a ruin that has decayed from time/event t2 to time/event t3 from temci festi
lujvo x1=l1 is a time traveller travelling over time interval x2=l2=t1 from x3=t2 to x4=t3 with time machine/time travel device x5=l3 cf. temci, litru
lujvo c1=s1 is immediately next to s2 in time. Cf. temci, sepli, claxu, sepcau, zi.

gismu rafsi: tod x1 is a butterfly/moth of species/breed x2. See also cinki.

lujvo x1 is reluctant/unwilling/disinclined to x2 for purpose x3. See also aunai

lujvo x1 is a shortage/deficiency/insufficiency/derth/too little of x2 by standard x3. See also mo'a
lujvo f1 rises to f2 from f3 in gravity well/frame of reference f4. Cf. to'e, farlu, galmu'u.
lujvo f1=b1 (action/event) becomes calm/calms down/is pacified under conditions f2 by standard b3. For person, use tu'a f1=b1.
lujvo g1 is gloomy/downcast/unhappy about g2 (event/state). Cf. to'e, gleki, badri.

lujvo x1=ga1 unrolls/unravels object x2=gu1 on/against surface x3=gu2, with axis/ axle of rotation x4=gu3. Cf. to'e, gunro, gasnu.

lujvo x1 avoids/ignores/directs attention away from object/affair x2. See also a'anai
lujvo k1 (object/commodity/property/event) is inexpensive to k2 by standard k3. Cf. to'e, kargu.
lujvo x1 is callous/implacable/heartless/merciless/ruthless towards x2 (person) about x3 (abstraction). See also kusru, uunai
lujvo x1 disbelieves/rejects x2 as false about x3. See also ianai
lujvo k1 is a ridge in/on object/surface k2. Cf. to'e, skuro.
lujvo k1 feels discomfort/is uncomfortable with conditions/environmental property(ies) k2. Cf. to'e, kufra, cinmo.
lujvo b1=m3 grandly exhibits the corruptness b2=m1 of unethical mass b3=m2.
lujvo m1 is incompatible with m2 in aspect m3. Cf. frica, dukti.
lujvo c1=m2 (person) is unintelligent/dumb/stupid by standard c3. Cf. menli, certu, bebna, pensi, mencre
lujvo g1 deciphers m1 into m2 out of coding system m3. kligau, ciksi, jimpe, tcidu.
lujvo x1 is ugly to x2 in aspect x3 (ka) by aesthetic standard x4.

lujvo m1=t1 is the ugliest/[most unsightly] among set/range t3 to m2 in aspect m3 (ka) by aesthetic standard m4.

lujvo m1 forgets fact/memory m2 about subject m3. Cf. to'e, morji, nalmo'i. Assumes that morji refers to a change of state i.e. 'remember'= 'bring to mind'.
lujvo x1 invents strategy (long-term plan) x2 for achieving x3 (event/state).
lujvo x1 (du'u) confirms/corroborates/verifies x2 (du'u) under rules/logic x3 .
lujvo s1 is threatened by s2 (event) from to'e snura c.f. ckape
lujvo x1 despairs/is despondent/pessimistic about x2, expected likelihood x3. Cf. to'e, pacna, norpa'a. See also a'onai
lujvo x1 is functional/operational/usable for function x2; x1 works properly See also spofu, cikre, daspo.
lujvo x1 is a damage/harm/loss to x2 resulting from activity/process x3. See also prali
lujvo x1 releases x2 from restraint/binding x3 to do/be x4 . See also rinju, gasnu, zifcru
lujvo r1 opposite of greets / offers goodbyes to r2 in manner r3 (action). Made from to'e + rinsa.
lujvo s1 blows/exhales fluid/gas from high pressure of s2 to low pressure of s3. Cf. to'e, sakci, bifca'e.
lujvo s1 (agent) withdraws/pulls out/extracts/removes s2 from interior/members of s3 from to'e setca
lujvo x1=c2 is bored with x2=c1. Cf. cinri, selci'i, nalselci'i, norselci'i, a'unai.
lujvo m2 is dissatisfied by m1 with regard to property (ka)/state m3. Cf. mansa, selmansa, tolgei.
lujvo t2 (load/force/torque) untwists t1. Cf. to'e, torni.
lujvo x1 disrespects/disregards/snubs/derides x2. Cf. to'e, sinma, tolsi'arai, ionai.
lujvo t1=s1 holds s2 in utmost contempt among set/range t4. Cf. to'e, sinma, traji, tolsi'a, ionai.
lujvo x1 [agent] begins activity/process/state x2. Cf. to'e, sisti, cfagau, co'arbi'o.
lujvo x1 (event/state) is deliberate/intentional on the part of x2; x1 is deliberate. to'e + gi'uste definition for snuti
lujvo x1 is a bachelor / single / unmarried.
lujvo x1 [agent] begins activity/process/state x2. Cf. to'e, sisti, cfagau, co'arbi'o.
lujvo s1 expends effort/is actively/effortfully involved in doing/being s2 (activity) Made from to'e + surla. See also a'i, lazni, renvi, snada, surla, tatpi, troci.
lujvo x1 is little/limited in property x2 towards x3. See also so'u
lujvo g1 unlocks lock s1 on s2 by mechanism s3. Cf. to'e, stela, gasnu, telgau, telga'o, telcaugau, kargau.
lujvo x1 disagrees with person(s)/position/side x2 that x3 (du'u) is true about matter x4. See also ienai
lujvo x1 is a coward in activity x2 (event) by standard x3. Cf. to'e, virnu, pronalka'e, u'onai.
lujvo v1 is immoral by standard v2.
fu'ivla x1 is rabid with symptoms x2. See also tolvut.
lujvo x1 is calm/tranquil/serene about x2 (abstraction) under conditions x3. Cf. to'e, xanka.
lujvo x1 (agent) denies that x2 (du'u) is true. Cf. to'e, xusra, natfe, nafmupli, nafxu'a.
lujvo g1 unbalances l1 with force l2. Cf. to'e, lanxe, gasnu.
lujvo c1 arrives at c2 via route c3. Cf. cliva, tolcanci.
lujvo x1 disapproves of/objects to plan/action x2. See also i'anai
lujvo x1 is boring/dreary/wearisome/tedious to x2 in property/aspect x3. See also u'inai
lujvo x1 is Arctic in aspect x2. see also berti
gismu rafsi: tog to'a x1 is a tone/note of frequency/pitch x2 from source x3. See also rilti, zgike, janbe, siclu.
fu'ivla x1 is x2 torrs by standard x3. synonym magmiltre
lujvo c1 is a dwarf of mythos/religion c2, short by measurement standard t3. Cf. torpre, brabracrida, firkre, ranmi.
gismu rafsi: tor to'u x1 is short in dimension/direction x2 (default longest dimension) by measurement standard x3. See also cmalu, jarki, caxno, cinla, clani.
gismu rafsi: ton to'i x1 twists under load/force/torsion x2. See also tinsa, trati.
lujvo t1 is a short time/duration/interval/period/elapsed time from time/event t2 to time/event t3. Cf. clatei, snidu.
lujvo x1=t1 is hypocritical in action t2=d1, which is contrary to assertion x2, under conditions t3. Cf. dukti, tarti, xusra, jitfa, tcica.

gismu rafsi: rai x1 is superlative in property x2 (ka), the x3 extreme (ka; default ka zmadu) among set/range x4. Also: x1 is x3-est/utmost in x2 among x4; x1 is the x3 end of x4; x1 is extreme; x1 is simply x3. (cf. cmavo list rai, jimte, milxe, mutce, note contrast with milxe and mutce rather than with mleca and zmadu, which are values for x3, banli, curve, fanmo, krasi, manfo, prane)
gismu x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of nitrogen/ammonia/nitrates. (adjective:) x1 is nitric/nitrous. See also vacri.
gismu x1 is taut/tense/strained tight in direction x2. See also tinsa, torni, tagji, tcena, kluza.
lujvo x1 is the metric system with relations x2 among units x3 and properties x4.

gismu rafsi: ren re'e x1 is a train [vehicle] of cars/units x2 (mass) for rails/system/railroad x3, propelled by x4. A railed vehicle or train of vehicles; also subway (tu'unre'e), metro, trolley, tramway (= lajre'e), roller coaster; monorail (= dadre'e); cable car, sky car, ski lift (= cildadre'e). See also tcana.
fu'ivla x1 is a palm tree, species/strain x2. Cf. tricu.
gismu rafsi: ric x1 is a tree of species/cultivar x2. See also cindu, ckunu, pezli, mudri, spati.
fu'ivla x1 is fenugreek of species/variety x2.
gismu rafsi: tri x1 attracts/appeals to/lures x2 (person/event) with property/quality x3 (ka). Also: x1 is alluring to x2. See also djica, nelci, rigni, xlura, maksi.
lujvo c1=t1 appeals to/lures, expressing c2 (sedu'u/text/lu'e concept), audience c3=t2 via expressive medium c4 with property/quality t3 (ka). Cf. trina, cusku.

gismu rafsi: rix ti'e x1 is posterior/behind/back/in the rear of x2 which faces/in-frame-of-reference x3. Also: x3 is the standard of orientation for x2; spine (= rixybo'u, rixybo'ukamju). See also crane, rebla, mlana, pritu, zunle.
fu'ivla x1 is a manatee of species x2. variant trixexu
fu'ivla x1 is a manatee of species x2. variant trixexo
gismu rafsi: toc toi x1 tries/attempts/makes an effort to do/attain x2 (event/state/property) by actions/method x3. Also experiments at. See also fliba, snada, cipra.
lujvo f1=j1 fails to control j2 in j3 (activity/event/performance). Cf. jitro, fliba.
lujvo k1=t1 is the supervisory board/board of directors/governing council of t2=k3. Cf. turni, kamni, trukamni, ctakamni, gazykamni, kagnyja'a.
fu'ivla x1 is a lamprey of genus/species x2.
fu'ivla x1 is a nasturtium of species x2.
lujvo c1 is a totalitarian system in j2 with power exercised by t1=t1 From jitro, ro, turni. Cf. ka'irtrusi'o.
lujvo b1 takes power from t1 over people/territory/domain/subjects t2 in circumstance b3. Cf. turni, basti, jamji'a, kamvli.

lujvo c1=t1 is the government of organizational type c2 of people/territory/domain/subjects t2 displaying properties c4. Cf. turni, ciste, vajraifla, zuktruci'e, flatruci'e, pairtruci'e, flacfatrugri, flazautrugri, trupau, trupausle.
lujvo j1 is intergovernmental / takes place where the decision-making power is shared among j2=t1=c1 (governments). Cf. truci'e, jbini.
lujvo c1 is a political affair involving c2

lujvo g1=d1=t1 is a political party operating in territory t2 with members g3 CF. turni, djica, girzu, trusi'o, truci'e, ka'irtrusi'o, dzejdasratrusi'o, vricykricrutrusi'o, fairpaltrusi'o, guntrusi'o, natpamtrusi'o, tsarainaitrusi'o.
fu'ivla t1 is a privet of species t2.
lujvo k1=j1 is the management board/executive committee/executive board of k3=j2. Cf. jitro, kamni, fuzraikamni, trokamni, ctakamni, gazykamni, kagnytruralju.
lujvo c1 is a member of governing council k1=t1.
lujvo m1 is a crown made of m2 used by ruler t1 of people/territory/domain/subjects t2. Cf. turni, mapku, nolmapku, nolboi, nolga'a.
lujvo p1 is a government ministry/department responsible for t2. CF. turni, pagbu, truci'e, trupausle, zuktruci'e, trupauja'a.
lujvo r1 is the minister/secretary of ministry/department t2 From turni pagbu jatna. Cf. trupau, truralju.
lujvo s1 is a sub-division of the Ministry/Department of t2. Cf. turni, pagbu, selci, trupau, truci'e.
lujvo r1 is the head-of-government of polity t2. Cf. turni, ralju, nolraitru, vliraitru, viptru, gugja'a, trupauja'a, balnoltru, vajraifla.

lujvo s1 is a political ideology about t1 ruling t2 based on the work of thinker s3 Cf. turni, sidbo, truci'e, trudjigri, ka'irtrusi'o, dzejdasratrusi'o, vricykricrutrusi'o, fairpaltrusi'o, guntrusi'o, natpamtrusi'o, tsarainaitrusi'o.
lujvo x1 is married to the governor/ruler of x2 according to custom x3; x1 is first lady/prince consort/queen consort of x2.
lujvo tc1=tu1 is the administrative capital (seat of government) of tu2=tc3 located in tc3 Cf. turni, tcadu, raltca.
lujvo k1=t1 is a jeep/land rover propelled by k3. Cf. tsali, karce, bevma'e, sonjamkarce.
fu'ivla x1 reflects Cherokee culture/nationality/language in aspect x2.
gismu rafsi: tsa x1 is strong/powerful/[tough] in property/quality x2 (ka) by standard x3. See also ralci, ruble, carmi, vlipa.
gismu rafsi: tan x1 is an expanse of sky/the heavens at place x2; [celestial]. See also gapru, kensa, tarci, terdi.
gismu x1 is a seasoning/condiment/spice causing flavor/effect x2 (event/property). Also: x1 flavors x2 (tu'a). See also vrusi.
fu'ivla x1 is pepper (genus ''Piper'') with flavor x2. Cf. cpinytsapi, spatrpiperi, kapsiku.

lujvo s1 is a fascist ideology as applied by t1 among/in people/territory/domain t2 based on the works of thinker s3 From tsali, traji, natmi, turni, sidbo. Cf. trudjigri, ka'irtrusi'o, dzejdasratrusi'o, vricykricrutrusi'o, fairpaltrusi'o, guntrusi'o, natpamtrusi'o.
lujvo s1 is a gorilla of species/subspecies s2.
lujvo b1=z1 sits down on surface z2. Cf. zutse, binxo, cfatse, nitytse. Simple zutse refers to the act of sitting, whereas tsebi'o means the act of becoming seated.
fu'ivla x1 is a sassaby/topi/korrigum/damalisk of species/breed x2. see also bajbakni
lujvo s1=z2 is a seat for s2=z2. Differs from stizu in that it focuses on the space rather than the object. Cf. stuzi, zutse.
lujvo t1=zb1 is a lap [body part] of t2=zu1 supporting zb2. Cf. tuple, zutse, zbepi, galtupcra. A lap only exists in a seated form, and not when a being is standing erect or when it is lying down.

gismu rafsi: tsi x1(s) is/are (a) seed(s)/spore(s) [body-part] of organism x2 for producing offspring x3. Also germ cell; implies actual potential for self-development; seeds generally contain embryo and food, and hence would include a fertilized egg. See also tarbi, dembi, grute, jbari, sombo, spati, sovda.
gismu rafsi: sin x1 is a stage/platform/dais/[scaffold] at/in x2 supporting x3, made of material x4. (x3 object/event); See also greku, jubme.
lujvo c2=t1 is semen secreted by organism c3 for producing offspring t3.
fu'ivla x1 is a zucchini squash (L. cucurbita pepo). A long, dark-green type of guzme eaten raw or cooked.
fu'ivla x1 is a tsunami caused by x2.
cmavo rafsi: tuf KOhA6 pro-sumti: that yonder; distant demonstrative it; indicated thing far from speaker&listener.
cmavo LAhE extracts a concrete sumti from an unspecified abstraction; equivalent to le nu/su'u [sumti] co'e.
cmavo TUhE start of multiple utterance scope; used for logical/non-logical/ordinal joining of sentences.
cmavo BAI stuzi modal, 1st place (used to situate letters) associated with site ... ; label with location.
lujvo f1=t1 makes facial gesture to show agreement with person(s)/position/side t2 that t3 (du'u) is true about matter t4. Cf. tugni, frumu, sedmu'utu'i.
cmavo PA5 null operand (used in unary mekso operations). See also xo'e.
cmavo TUhU elidable terminator: end multiple utterance scope; seldom elidable.

lujvo b1 = t1 is a tentacle / tube-shaped arm [body part] of b2. The other places of tubnu (outer and inner material of the tube) are dependant on the body with the tentacle; generally they'll just be "skin" and "blood" or "flesh" anyways. Made from tubnu and birka.
lujvo t1 is a tubeworm of species t2.
fu'ivla x1 reflects Turkish culture/nationality/language in aspect x2. Cf. bangrturkie, kulnrturkie, xelso, ropno, xazdo.
gismu rafsi: tu'u x1 is a length of tubing/pipe/hollow cylinder [shape/form] of material x2, hollow of material x3. Also tube, sleeve, leg, hose, (adjective:) tubular. See also kevna, canlu.
