lujvo s1 is a brother/sister-in-law (brother's/sister's spouse) of m2 under law/custom/tradition/system/convention sp3. Omit x4=s2=m1. Cf. speni, bunspe, me'ispe.
lujvo x1=b1=t1 settles issue x2=t4 with person x3=t2, agreeing that x4=t3 (du'u) is true. Cf. tugni, sarxe, fapro, darlu, xarnu.
gismu rafsi: tug tu'i x1 [person] agrees with person(s)/position/side x2 that x3 (du'u) is true about matter x4. See also sarxe, mapti, darlu, natfe, panpi, sarji.
lujvo t1=t2=s1 are unanimous / sharing the same view on t3=s2 (du'u). Cf. simxu, tugni.
gismu rafsi: tuj x1 is a tulip (defined by flower shape) of species/strain x2. See also spati.
lujvo c1=t1 swallows c2. From tunlo citka.
lujvo l1 explores lands in l2=t2 discovering facts f2 using means l3 from tumla facki litru
gismu rafsi: tum tu'a x1 is a parcel/expanse of land at location x2; x1 is terrain. (cf. vacri, xamsi; tutra, which need not be land, gugde, xamsi)
lujvo s1 is the ground of land s2=t1 at location t2. Cf. sefta, tumla.
lujvo m1 surveys t1=m2 as m3 (map or measurements) in unit m4 with accuracy m5 see also tedmre
gismu rafsi: tub x1 is a sibling of x2 by bond/tie/standard/parent(s) x3. See also bruna, mensi, tamne.
gismu rafsi: tuk x1 is made of/contains/is a quantity of copper (Cu); [metaphor: reddish, electrical conductor]. See also jinme, lastu, ransu.

gismu rafsi: tul tu'o x1 gulps/swallows. x1 swallows down food/drink. x2 (= tulpinxe, tulcti, ctitu'o (the latter two are more general - for food or beverage); swallow/engulf (= galxycti, galxynerbi'o, galxygre. See also citka, pinxe, galxe.
gismu rafsi: tun x1 (object, usually pointed) pokes/jabs/stabs/prods x2 (experiencer). Agentive (= tungau, tunzu'e). See also balre, dakfu, darxi, fanza, jicla, katna, tikpa.
lujvo c1 is a boot for covering/protecting leg c2=t1, and of material c3. Cf. bracutci, karcutci.
gismu rafsi: tup tu'e x1 is a/the leg [body-part] of x2; [metaphor: supporting branch]. See also stani, zbepi, jamfu, jimca, sanli.
lujvo j1 is a hip attaching attaching leg j2=t1 to body j3=t2. See also tupyjanbo'u for hip bone

gismu rafsi: tru x1 governs/rules/is ruler/governor/sovereign/reigns over people/territory/domain/subjects x2. x2 need not be complete specification of set of governed; reign/rule (= noltru); king/queen/sovereign (= nolraitru); pure democracy (= roltrusi'o), representative democracy (= rolka'itrusi'o), viceroy (= ka'itru), pure communism (= kaurpo'esi'o), board of directors/trustees, steering committee (= trukamni); government (= trugunma, trugri (emphasizing the components), truci'e (emphasizing the organization)). See also catni, minde, tutra, jecta, gugde, ponse, jitro.

gismu rafsi: tci x1 is a tool/utensil/resource/instrument/implement used for doing x2; [form determines function]. (cf. cabra, minji, se pilno, zukte, sazri, basic tool types: salpo, pulni, cfine, klupe, jendu, xislu, vraga; utensils: forca, smuci, dakfu; specifics: balre, mruli, cinza, garna, pijne, pambe, canpa, pilno, vraga)
lujvo t1=p1 is a district of p2 administered by t2. An administrative district is usually a second-level division of a country, hence the reduplicated "-paupau". Cf. turni, gugde.
gismu rafsi: tut x1 is territory/domain/space of/belonging to/controlled by x2. See also catni, turni, jecta, gugde, ponse, steci, tumla.
lujvo s1 pertains to territory of s2=t2 Cultural gismu replacement for geography: From gismu tutra and srana.
lujvo s1 is geography based on methodology s3.
cmavo A logical connective: sumti afterthought whether-or-not.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: gain - loss. See also jinga, selne'u, prali, cirko.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: wonder - commonplace. See also manci, fadni.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: amusement - weariness. See also selzdi, selxajmi, xalbo.
fu'ivla x1 is a lolcat (picture of an animal with a humorous caption) Etymology: Combination of u'i and mlatu and meant to parallel u'ivla.

fu'ivla x1 is a word meaning x2 in language x3 and silly/funny/clever for reason x4 (usually etymological). The word u'ivla is itself an u'ivla, as it is an unconventional portmanteau of u'i and -vla- (a rafsi of valsi) and also a pun on the word fu'ivla. Another example is u'imla.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: courage - timidity - cowardice. See also virnu.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: courage - timidity - cowardice.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: courage - timidity - cowardice.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: repentance - lack of regret - innocence. See also xenru, zugycni.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: repentance - lack of regret - innocence.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: repentance - lack of regret - innocence.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: discovery - confusion/searching. See also facki, cfipu, sisku.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: surprise - not really surprised - expectation. See also spaji.
fu'ivla x1 pertains to the world wide web in aspect x2. See also ueb, kibro, kibypapri, kibyca'o.
cmavo cluster UI*1 attitudinal: surprise - not really surprised - expectation axis.
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: happiness - unhappiness. See also gleki.
fu'ivla x1 is Uyghur in aspect x2 See also tirkce, jungo.
fu'ivla x1 is whisk(e)y distilled from x2. Cf. xalka, jikru, birje, vanju, campania, vo'otka, vanjyjikru, koinka.
fu'ivla x1 is a wiki/collaborative web site with subject/theme/content x2.
fu'ivla x1 is an elm of species/variety x2. see also na'itsi
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: completion - incompleteness. See also mulno, mansa, fanmo, snada.
fu'ivla x1 is poison ivy/oak/sumac / lacquer tree of species x2. see also ponjo cinta, xalkrxuruci, spatrnakardiace, rakcro, srebandu
cmavo UI1 attitudinal: pity - cruelty. See also kecti.
cmavo rafsi: vaz VA location tense distance: near to ... ; there at ...; a medium/small distance from ...
cmavo VUhU3 unary mathematical operator: additive inverse; [- a].
cmavo MOI convert number to scalar selbri; x1 is at (n)th position on scale x2.
cmavo UI3 discursive: in other words - in the same words. See also cneselsku.
cmavo cluster UI*3 discursive: in other words - in the same words.
cmavo BAI vanbi modal, 1st place (conditions 1) under conditions ...; in environment ...
cmavo BAI xamgu modal, 1st place beneficiary case tag complement benefiting from ...
lujvo p1=v1 protests with a sigh about p2 (event/state) to audience p3 with action p4. Cf. vasxu, pante, patyva'u.
lujvo m1=c1 is the dusk of day m2=c2 at location m3=c3. Cf. cermurse.
gismu rafsi: var x1 is a quantity of air/normally-gaseous atmosphere of planet x2, of composition including x3. See also gapci, kijno, trano, tumla, vasxu, xamsi.
lujvo s1 (mass) is a dinner composed of dishes including s2. Cf. cersai, dormijysai, ctesai, citka, cidja.
lujvo s1=v1 is a military officer in army s2. Cf. vajni, sonci, jemja'a.

gismu rafsi: vaj vai x1 (object/event) is important/significant to x2 (person/event) in aspect/for reason x3 (nu/ka). Also: x1 matters to x2 in aspect/respect x3. See also banli, ralju, vamji, dirba, kargu, pajni.
lujvo x1=v1=t1 is most important/most significant to x2=v2 in aspect/for reason x3=v3 among set/range x4=t4. vajni+traji
lujvo f1=v1=t1 is the constitution of f3=v2. Cf. vajni, traji, flalu, zuktruci'e, flatruci'e, pairtruci'e, flacfatrugri, flazautrugri.
gismu rafsi: val vla x1 is a word meaning/causing x2 in language x3; (adjective: x1 is lexical/verbal). See also slaka, bangu, cmavo, cmene, gismu, jufra, rafsi, smuni.
lujvo t1=m1 is the tone of word v1=m2 with characteristics t2=m3. The linguistic tone is used to distinguish a difference in meaning, for example in Chinese. Cf. valsi, tonga, morna.

gismu rafsi: vam va'i x1 (ni) is the equivalent value/worth of x2 [item(s) of value] to x3 for use/appreciation x4. Also: x2 is worth x1 to x3; (for x2 person:) x2 merits (one sense), (adjective:) x2 is worthy (= selva'i for reordered places); merit reward (= nemselva'i); receive merited reward (= vamselne'u); x2 may be a specific object, a commodity (mass), an event, or a property; pedantically, for objects/commodities, this is sumti-raising from ownership of the object/commodity (= posyva'i, posyselva'i for unambiguous semantics). (cf. jdima, jerna, vecnu, dirba, janta, kargu, pleji; see note at jdima on cost/price/value distinction, vajni)
lujvo v1=t1 is the most valuable among items v2=r4 to v3 for purpose v4. Made from vamji + traji.
lujvo v1=t1 is the most valuable among items v2=r4 to v3 for purpose v4. Made from vamji + to'e + traji.
gismu rafsi: vat x1 vomits/regurgitates x2; x1 throws x2 up; [violent] digestive expulsion. (x2 is non-gaseous); See also rigni, jetce, kafke, sputu.
gismu rafsi: vab x1 (ind./mass) is part of an environment/surroundings/context/ambience of x2. (adjective:) x1 is ambient. See also cmavo list va'o, sruri, jibni, jbini, ferti, tcini.

gismu rafsi: vac x1 is an evening [from end-of-work until sleep typical for locale] of day x2 at location x3. This evening (= cabvanci); tomorrow evening (= bavlamvanci); yesterday evening (= prulamvanci). See also cerni, murse, tcika.
fu'ivla x1 is lavender of species/variety x2.
lujvo x1 is a grape of species/variety x2.
gismu rafsi: van x1 is made of/contains/is a quantity of wine from fruit/grapes x2. See also barja, birje, xalka, jikru, fusra.
lujvo j1 is a brandy distilled from v2. Cf. xalka, jikru, birje, vanju, uiski, campania, vo'otka, koinka.
lujvo s1=v1 is vinegar made from v2. Cf. vanju, slami, pelnimre, sarvanju.
lujvo x1 is a hovercraft for carrying x2, propelled by x3, riding on/lifted by x4. see also varkiclafti
lujvo x1 is the front of air mass x2. see also lenku, glare, stali, selzu'i
lujvo mg1 is a fan blowing/moving air mg2=v1 to/towards/onto mg3 from mg4. From vacri and muvgau, or equivalently, vacri, muvdu, and gasnu.
lujvo mi1 is a fan for moving air to destination mu2 from origin mu3 over path/route mu4. Cf. lekmi'i, pambe.
fu'ivla x1 is vanilla. Cf. cakla, ckafi.
lujvo x1 is the atmosphere of planet x2=v2 (default Earth) of composition v3. from vacri xamsi
lujvo s1 is the atmospheric science of planet x2. Cf. vacri, xamsi, saske, varxamsi, xasyske, tutske.

gismu rafsi: vas vau x1 contains/holds/encloses/includes contents x2 within; x1 is a vessel containing x2. [also accommodates, container; containment need not be total; x2 is Contained. in x1 (= selvau for reordered places)]; See also bartu, jbini, nenri, zvati, cpana, botpi, lanka.

gismu rafsi: vax va'u x1 breathes/respires x2 [gas]. (though used to make the Lojban word, clue word vascular is erroneous, actually pertaining to the circulatory system that carries the respired oxygen to the tissues); See also fepri, kijno, vacri.
cmavo VAU elidable: end of sumti in simple bridi; in compound bridi, separates common trailing sumti.
lujvo n2=v1 has difficulty breathing gas v2 under conditions n3; n1=v1 pants. Cf. vasxu, nandu, ta'irva'u.
lujvo d1 chokes v1 by/with d3. Cf. vasxu, dicra, dirva'u.
cmavo rafsi: vel SE 4th conversion; switch 1st/4th places.
cmavo VEhA location tense interval: a small/medium region of space.
cmavo rafsi: ve'e VEhA location tense interval: the whole of space.
cmavo VEhA location tense interval: a tiny region of space.
cmavo VEhA location tense interval: a large region of space.
cmavo cluster BAI* benji modal, 4th place transmit origin ...
cmavo cluster BAI* ciste modal, 4th place as a system with synergy in ...

gismu rafsi: ven ve'u x1 [seller] sells/vends x2 [goods/service/commodity] to buyer x3 for amount/cost/expense x4. x1 is a salesperson/salesman/vendor; x3 buys x2 from x1 (= terve'u for reordered terms); x4 is the price of x2 to x3 (= velve'u for reordered terms); for sale (= fitselve'u, selvenfriti); x2 may be a specific object, a commodity (mass), an event, or a property; pedantically, for objects/commodities, this is sumti-raising from ownership of the object/commodity (= posyve'u, posyselve'u for unambiguous semantics). (cf. canja, dunda, janta, pleji, jerna, kargu, prali, zarci, vamji, jdima; see note at jdima on cost/price/value distinction, fepni, friti, jerna, rupnu)
cmavo cluster BAI* cusku modal, 4th place in expression medium ...
cmavo cluster BAI* detri modal, 4th place on a date according to calendar ...
cmavo cluster BAI* djuno modal, 4th place under epistemology ...
cmavo cluster BAI* finti modal, 4th place creatively; created from ideas/elements ...
cmavo cluster BAI* zgana modal, 4th place (under conditions) observed under observing conditions ...

lujvo x1=d1=v4 is a signal recording and playback tape-type medium (cassette/DAT/tape drive) containing data/sound/image x2=v2 with data storage mechanism/method x3 (analog/digital) Cf. datnysri, srimakyvelvei.
cmavo cluster BAI* klama modal, 4th place via route ...
lujvo x4=b1 runs on surface x2=b2 using limbs x3=b3 with gait x1=b4. ve bajra
lujvo x4=b1 exceeds/is beyond limit/boundary x2=b2 from x3=b3 in property/amount x1=b4 (ka/ni). ve bancu
lujvo x1 is the biting tool with which x2 is bitten at locus x3 by x4.
lujvo x4=b1 is a button/knob/handle on/for item x2=b2, with purpose x3=b3, made of material x1=b4. ve batke
lujvo x4=b1 is a crew/team/gang/squad/band of persons x2=b2 directed/led by x3=b3 organized for purpose x1=b4. ve bende
lujvo x4=b1 transfers/sends/transmits x2=b2 to receiver x3=b3 from transmitter/origin x1=b4 via means/medium x5=b5. ve benji; see also krasi.
lujvo x4=b1 carries/hauls/bears/transports cargo x2=b2 to x3=b3 from x1=b4 over path x5=b5; x4=b1 is a carrier/porter. ve bevri
lujvo x4=b1 is a wall/fence separating x2=b2 from x3=b3, and subdividing x1=b4. ve bitmu
lujvo x4=b1 insures/indemnifies x2=b2 against peril x3=b3 providing benefit x1=b4. ve binra
lujvo x4=b1 is a wave/periodic pattern in medium x2=b2, with wave-form x3=b3, wave-length x1=b4 and frequency x5=b5. ve boxna
lujvo x4=b1 is a bottle/jar/urn/flask/closable container for x2=b2, made of material x3=b3 with lid x1=b4. ve botpi
lujvo x4=c1 is a farm/ranch at x2=c2, of rancher x3=c3 raising/producing x1=c4. ve cange, see also banro
lujvo x4=c1 exchanges/trades/barters commodity x2=c2 for x3=c3 with x1=c4. ve canja
lujvo x1 is an explanation of x2 (event/state/property) to x3 by x4. Cf. ciksi.
lujvo j4 is the birthplace, the parent(s) being j2, the birthdate being j3, of j1. Cf. jbena.

lujvo x1 is an order [biology] with genus x2, family x3, with species x4, within class x5. From jimca, jmive, klesi. For biological cathegory in general (=mivyske klesi), domain (=?), kingdom (=seljimcymivykle), phylum (=jicymivykle), class (=xeljutsi), order (=this definition), family (=terjutsi), genus (=seljutsi), species (=jutsi)
lujvo x1 is a digging limb/tool for digging material x2 up/out of x3 (source/hole) with agent x4. Cf. canpa.
lujvo x1=k4 is a route that leads to x2=k2, from x3=k3, travelled by x4=k1 by means x5=k5.
lujvo s4 is a description of s2 to audience s3 by describer s1. Cf. pinka, selsku, pixra.
lujvo x1 is the time zone where x2 happens on day x3 at time x4.
lujvo x1 is jetlagged with symptoms x2 going to x3 from x4.
lujvo x1 is the sales price of x2 to x3 from/at vendor x4.
lujvo z3=v4 is the sales quota for v1=z1 to sell v2 to v3. Cf. vecnu, zukte, vencu'u, cumnunve'u.
lujvo v1 is the result/remnant/remainder when v2 is removed/subtracted/deducted/taken away from v3 by v4. Cf. vimcu.
cmavo cluster BAI* zmadu modal, 4th place (relative!) more than/exceeding by amount ...
cmavo cluster BAI* mleca modal, 4th place (relative!) less than by amount ...
lujvo c1 is a market (system) interrelated by structure c2 (social relations / institutions / procedures / infrastructures) of components c3=v2 (goods/services/information) displaying c4 (economy).
lujvo c1 is/are the sales function/activities of c2=v1 selling v2 to v3; c1 is sales. Cf. vecnu, cuntu, selvensro, janta, faircu'u, zbacu'u.
gismu rafsi: vef x1 takes revenge on/retaliates against x2 (person) for wrong x3 (nu) with vengeance x4 (nu). Also avenge; (adjective:) x1 is vengeful. See also sfasa, cnemu.
gismu rafsi: ves x1 is spring/springtime [warming season] of year x2 at location x3; (adjective:) x1 is vernal. See also citsi, crisa, critu, dunra.
lujvo x1=vr1 is a record of x2=ve1 [seller] having sold x3=ve2 [goods/service/commodity] to buyer x4=ve3 for amount/cost/expense x5=ve4, stored on medium x6=vr4. Cf. vecnu, vreji
lujvo x1 is a mailer about v2 from x3=v1 for audience x2=v3. Cf. vecnu, xatra, cuntu, zaircu'u, zairsnucu'u, venynoicu'u, venxatrycu'u, zacfoncu'u, faircu'u, vencu'u.

lujvo c1 the direct mail business/activity/function for goods/products/services/activities v2 from/by x3=v1 to audience x2=v3. Cf. vecnu, xatra, cuntu, zaircu'u, zairsnucu'u, venynoicu'u, venxa'a, zacfoncu'u, faircu'u, vencu'u.
lujvo n1 is an advertisement about n2=v2 by n3=v1 to intended audience n4=v3. Cf. vecnu, notci, venynoicu'u, zairsnucu'u, karni, cradi, tivni.

lujvo c1 the advertising business/activity/function about goods/products/services/activities n2=v2 from/by n2=v1 to audience n4=v3. Cf. vecnu, notci, cuntu, venynoi, zaircu'u, zairsnucu'u, venxatrycu'u, zacfoncu'u, faircu'u, vencu'u.
lujvo z1 is a vending machine offering v2 to v3 for sale cost v4 under condition z3.
cmavo cluster BAI* panra modal, 4nd place (standard/geometry) similarly; similar by standard ...
cmavo cluster BAI* pruce modal, 4th place (set of stages) passing through processing stages ...
cmavo cluster BAI* traji modal, 4th place (set) -est; most extremely; superlative among ...
gismu rafsi: ver ve'a x1 is a child/kid/juvenile [a young person] of age x2, immature by standard x3. Not necessarily human. See also cifnu, makcu, citno, panzi, nanla, nixli, se rirni, bersa.
lujvo c1 is the childhood (time of being a child) of v1. Cf. cedra, verba, kamve'a.
lujvo c1 is a crib made of c2 for a child c3=v1 of age v2. not necessarily with bars; see also slicka
lujvo b1=c3 is a native language of b2=v1=c1 to express b3.
cmavo cluster BAI* tamsmi modal, 4th place similarly; sharing ideal form in property ... tamsmi is x1 resembles x2 sharing ideal form/shape x3 in property x4
cmavo cluster BAI* tcika modal, 4th place (for letters) as a time at location ...
cmavo rafsi: viz VA location tense distance: here at ... ; at or a very short/tiny distance from ...
cmavo cluster VA* sumti question asking for a location: at/near what?.
cmavo VIhA dimensionality of space interval tense: 2-space interval; throughout an area.
cmavo VIhA dimensionality of space interval tense: 4-space interval; throughout a spacetime.
lujvo c1=v2 invites c3=v1 to v2 (place/event) in manner c4. Cf. vitke, cpedu, zvacpe.
cmavo VIhA dimensionality of space interval tense: 1-space interval; along a line.
cmavo COI vocative: wilco (ack and will comply).
cmavo VIhA dimensionality of space interval tense: 3-space interval; throughout a space.
gismu rafsi: vib x1 is a/the vagina [body-part] of x2. See also cinse, gletu, pinji, plibu, vlagi, mabla.
lujvo v1=r1 cuts (removes during editing) v2=r2 from v3 leaving v4. Cf. vimcu, ralte, fukra'e, fukpu'i.
lujvo v2=l3 is trash/rubbish/garbage/refuse removed from v3=l2 by v1=l1 (agent)
gismu x1 is a video monitor/CRT/screen [machine] serving function x2. See also skina, ve tivni.
lujvo s1 is a pixel of screen s2=v1.
gismu rafsi: vir x1 is a virus of species/breed/defining property x2 capable of infecting [at] x3. See also jurme.
gismu rafsi: vif (adjective:) x1 is fresh/unspoiled. See also fusra.
lujvo b1 is an aircraft carrier carrying b2, propelled by b3. Cf. vinji, bloti, ni'ablo, brabrajamblo, brajamblo, cmajamblo, badjamblo.
lujvo s1 maneuvers/pilots/is a pilot of aircraft v1=s2. Cf. vinji, sazri.
lujvo s1 is a paratrooper in military unit s2. Cf. vinji, sonci.
lujvo t1 is an airport in transport system t2 for aircraft of type v2 propelled by v3 from vinji tcana.
gismu rafsi: vim vi'i x1 [body] excretes waste x2 from source x3 via means/route x4. See also cigla, kalci, pinca, xasne.
gismu rafsi: vik x1 is thick/viscous under conditions x2. See also denmi, snipa.
lujvo x1 is mucus produced by organ/membrane x2 in body x3
lujvo x1 is mistletoe of species/variety x2.
lujvo m1 is very/extremely violent. Cf. vlile, mutce.
lujvo t1=v1 is a storm at place/region t2. Cf. vlile, tcima.

gismu rafsi: vic vi'u x1 removes/subtracts/deducts/takes away x2 from x3 with/leaving result/remnant/remainder x4. Also appropriates, confiscates; alienation is inherent. See also lebna, muvdu, cpacu, canci, cliva, jdika.

lujvo x1=k1 is a loo/water closet/[room with toilet], in which x2=v1 excretes x3=v2, in home/building/structure x4=k2 surrounded by partitions/walls/ceiling/floor x5=k3 (mass/jo'u) From vimstizu. As distinct from lumku'a, which is a room that primarily features washing facilities, this is a room that primarily features a means of relieving one's self.
lujvo s1 is a toilet for v1 to excrete v2 from source v3 via means/route v4
gismu rafsi: vid x1 is poisonous/venomous/toxic/a toxin to x2. See also since.
gismu rafsi: vij x1 is an airplane/aircraft [flying vehicle] for carrying passengers/cargo x2, propelled by x3. See also vofli, sabnu.
fu'ivla x1 is a double bass / contrabass

lujvo c1 (mass) is a hierachical / subordinate system / tree (computer science sense) interrelated by hierachical property / property determining subordinate relationships / subordination in aspect [or organization principle] c2 = v2 (ka) among components c3 displaying common property c4 (ka) with leaves v1 and topmost / root element v3. Made from vipsi + ciste.
lujvo k1=v1 is a subsidiary company to k2=v3 chartered/mandated for purpose k3. From vipsi, kagni.
lujvo v1=t1 is the appointed governor/governor-general/lieutenant-governor over territory t2 representing principal v3 Cf. vipsi, nobli, turni, nolraitru, vliraitru, gugja'a, truralju, trupauja'a.
gismu rafsi: vip x1 is a deputy/vice/subordinate in aspect [or organization principle] x2 (ka) to principal x3. Also assistant, adjutant. See also krati, sidju.
lujvo g1=v1 is a state/province/canton of federal state v3. Cf. vipsi, gugde, gugypau.
gismu rafsi: vri x1 is brave/valiant/courageous in activity x2 (event) by standard x3. See also terpa, darsi.
lujvo s1=v1 is virology of viruses s2 based on methodology s3. Virology is the study of viruses. See also vidru, jumske.
lujvo f1=v1 spots f3=v2 under condition v3. Cf. facki, viska.

gismu rafsi: vis vi'a x1 sees/views/perceives visually x2 under conditions x3. Also (adjective:) x1 is visual; x3 can include ambient lighting, background, etc. which may affect what is perceived; note that English "see" often means "look" or a more generic "observe", or even "understand, know". See also catlu, jvinu, kanla, minra, simlu, djuno, jimpe, zgana, ganse.
fu'ivla x1 is a bison of species x2
lujvo t1 is an optical tool used by v1 to see v2. Cf. viska, tutci, le'otci, barkalyle'o, darvistci. Includes but is not limited to glass-based spectacles.
gismu rafsi: vit x1 is irregular/occasional/intermittent in property/action/aspect x2. See also ranji, rufsu, suksa.
gismu rafsi: vi'e x1 is a guest/visitor of x2 at place/event x3; x1 visits x2/x3. See also friti, klama, zasni, xabju, zvati.
gismu rafsi: vi'o x1 is permanent/lasting/[eternal] in property x2 (ka) by standard x3 [time-span/expectant one]. Also everlasting. See also stodi, cimni, zasni, manfo, stali.
lujvo b1 brings cargo b2 here from x3=b4 over path x4=b5.
lujvo c1 is a dictionary concerning c3 authored by c3 intended for c4 in medium c5.
gismu rafsi: lag x1 is a/the vulva [body-part] of x2. See also cinse, gletu, pinji, plibu, vibna, mabla.
lujvo g1 is a verse/stanza with property (ka) g2 meaning v2 in language v3. Cf. valsi, girzu, vlali'i, jufmei, pempau.
lujvo l1 is a line of text defined by set of words/string l2 meaning x3=v2 in language x4=v3. Cf.valsi, linji, lerpinsle, jufra, jufmei, vlagri, pempau.

fu'ivla x1 [mass/sequence] plays the Lojban word chaining game (vlalinkei) with ruleset x2 and winner x3 with resulting sentence x4 against world champion x6 for fabulous cash prize x7 and endorsement deal(s) x8 groupies x9 (except they probably go earlier), played at time x10 at location x11 and honorific title x12 breaking record(s) x13 with mindless spectators x14 taking time x15 [amount] containing most frequently used word x16 (zo) and not using perfectly good words x17 (zo) displaying new strategy/trick x18 supervised by x19 with referee x20 and used message transmission system x21 time limit per move x22 shortest move of the game x23 broadcast on TV network(s) x24 with Neilson ratings x25 supplanting previously most watched show x26 winning new fans x27 who formerly played x28 which is inferior for reasons x29 by standard x30 with banned words x31 with words winning additional points x32 with climax of suspense x33 and best comeback x34
lujvo s1 is verbatim/to the letter. Used of text. Cf. valsi, satci, sitna, jufra
lujvo s1=v1 (agent) reproaches s2 for infraction s3 (event/state/action) from valsi sfasa
lujvo x1=l1 is a dictionary with words x2=l2=v1 in order x3=l3, medium x4=l4, and language x5=v3. See also: valsi, liste
lujvo t1 is the pattern/shape of word v1=t2 with meaning v2 in language v3. Cf. valsi, tarmi, rafsi, rafske
lujvo k1 (tool/blade/force) rips/tears/shreds k2 (object) into pieces k3
gismu rafsi: vil x1 is an event/state/act of violence. See also suksa, jursa.
gismu x1 is a logical alternation/disjunction, stating that x2 (du'u) and/or x3 (du'u) is/are true. See also kanxe, cmavo list a, ja, gi'a, gu'a.
gismu rafsi: vli x1 has the power to bring about x2 under conditions x3; x1 is powerful in aspect x2 under x3. Also potent, has control/mastery. See also tsali, jitro, ruble.
lujvo tu1=tr1=v1 is a dictator over/in subjects/territory tu2 under conditions v3. Cf. kustru, kusyja'a, nonkantru.
lujvo x1=v1 influences the power dynamics of situation x2=v3 towards end x3=v2 through means of influence x4. From vlipa, xlura.
cmavo KOhA4 pro-sumti: repeats 1st place of main bridi of this sentence.
cmavo KOhA4 pro-sumti: repeats 2nd place of main bridi of this sentence.
cmavo KOhA4 pro-sumti: repeats 3rd place of main bridi of this sentence.
cmavo KOhA4 pro-sumti: repeats 4th place of main bridi of this sentence.
fu'ivla x1 is a vodka distilled from x2. Cf. xalka, jikru, birje, vanju, uiski, campania, vanjyjikru, koinka.
cmavo KOhA4 pro-sumti: repeats 5th place of main bridi of this sentence.
gismu rafsi: vol voi x1 flies [in air/atmosphere] using lifting/propulsion means x2. See also cipni, klama, vinji.
cmavo NOI non-veridical restrictive clause used to form complicated le-like descriptions using "ke'a".
cmene x1 is a kite. From falnu, vofli (f2, f3, v2 subsumed). See also volfanjacta'o.
lujvo k1=v1 flies to destination k2 from origin k3 to destination k4 using means/vehicle k5=v2.
cmavo cluster PA* number/quantity: 4,000 expressed with comma.
gismu rafsi: vok vo'a x1 is a voice/speech sound of individual x2. See also sance, tirna, bacru.
lujvo voice x1=s1=v1 of individual x3=v2 oscillates at frequency x2=s2.
lujvo s2 is phonetics based on methodology s2.
lujvo k1 is a minimal phonological feature of language k2=g2.
lujvo s1 is phonology based on methodology s3.

lujvo t1=d1=f1=v1 is a board for use in water/(wind/kite)surfingboard/bodyboard/wakeboard of material/property t2. From tanbo, djacu, falnu, vofli (f2, f3, v2 subsumed). See also sufingboard (=bonjacta'o), windsurfingboard (=fanjacta'o), wakesurfingboard (=blobonjacta'o).
fu'ivla x1 is a wombat (family Vombatidae) of species/breed x2
cmavo cluster MOI* quantified selbri: convert 4 to ordinal selbri; x1 is fourth among x2 ordered by rule x3.
lujvo x1 is a 4-dimensional spacetime/region occupied by x2 . See also vi'e
lujvo x1 is a Thursday of week x2 in calendar x3.
lujvo d1 is a caltrop (tetrahedral nail) of size d2 made of d3.
lujvo x1 is April/the fourth month of year x2 in calendar x3. Cf. pavmasti, nanca.

lujvo j1 has the rank of Lieutenant Colonel/Commander/Wing Commander (equivalent of NATO OF-4) in military unit /organization j2. Cf. vo, moi, jatna, jemja'a, vairsoi, mumymoija'a, cibmoija'a. Based on STANAG 2116: NATO Codes for Grades of Military Personnel.
lujvo m1=d1 is the ring finger of d2. Cf. degji.
fu'ivla x1 swindles x2 into state/event x3 by promising x4; x1 commits 419/advance fee fraud. generally x1 is Nigerian, but may be in another country; see also tcica

lujvo p1 is the fourth closest planet (default is Mars if p2 is the Sun) revolving around p2 (default is the Sun), with planetary characteristics p3, orbital parameters p4. Cf. vonplin, pavyplini, relplini etc.; see also terdi, solri, mluni, lunra, plinycma, tarci'e.
lujvo d2 is quadrille music accompanying dancers d1 (individual, mass). Cf. dansu, seldansu, vonynundansu.
lujvo t2 is four-legged with legs t1. Cf. vo, tuple.
lujvo n1 is a quadrille with dancers d1 to music/rhythm d2. Cf. dansu, nundansu, vonseldansu.
lujvo p1=v1 is a passage between p2=v2 and p3=v3. Cf. vorme, pluta.

gismu rafsi: vor vro x1 is a doorway/gateway/access way between x2 and x3 of structure x4. Note: emphasis on route nature; solid door (= vrogai/vrobi'u/vrozu'itci). See also canko, ganlo, kalri, murta, pagre, bitmu, kuspe.

lujvo b1=v1 is a switch/actuating lever on/for item b2, with purpose b3, made of material b4. Though there has been a great amount of debate in Lojbanistan over the need for a lujvo as such, I thought I would submit it anyway.
gismu rafsi: vra x1 is a lever [tool] [of apparatus] for doing x2 [function/action], with fulcrum x3 and arm x4. See also tutci, pulni.
fu'ivla x1 is kelp of genus/species x2
gismu rafsi: rej vei x1 is a record of x2 (data/facts/du'u) about x3 (object/event) preserved in medium x4. See also sorcu, datni, papri.
lujvo p1 lays p2=v1 on/at surface/locus p3=v2. Cf. punji, vreta.
gismu rafsi: vre x1 lies/rests/reclines/reposes on x2; x1 is reclining/recumbent/lying on x2. See also cpana, surla, zutse, ckana, lazni.
gismu x1 (set/mass/ind.) is miscellaneous/various/assorted in property x2 (ka). See also klesi, girzu, frica, simsa, panra.
lujvo c1 is liberal/open-minded with regard to beliefs k2 about subject k3 under conditions c3 From vrici, krici, curmi. Cf. dzejdasra, vricykricrutrusi'o.

lujvo s1 is a liberal political ideology as applied by t1=c1 among/in people/territory/domain t2 based on the works of thinker si3 From vrici, krici, curmi, turni, sidbo. Cf. vricykricru, ka'irtrusi'o, dzejdasratrusi'o, fairpaltrusi'o, guntrusi'o, natpamtrusi'o, tsarainaitrusi'o.
lujvo c1=v1 is a French window/side-hinged window. vorme canko; typically in pairs extending to the floor
lujvo d1 knocks at door d2=v1 to v3. Cf. vorme, darxi.
lujvo g1 is a door/gate (movable barrier) in portal/doorway (opening) v1=g2 between v2 and v3, in structure v4. Cf. vorme, gacri, li'avro, kumfa, dinju, pagre
lujvo k1=v1 is the threshold defining access through the boundary between k2=v2 and k3=v3. Cf. vorme, korbi, vroloi.
lujvo l1 is the threshold/doorsill of doorway/gateway l2 between v2 and v3 of structure v4. Cf. vorme, loldi, vrokoi.
lujvo c1 is a horn/buzzer/siren producing strident noise c2=s1, operated by c3. savru cabra
gismu rafsi: vud vu'e x1 is virtuous/saintly/[fine/moral/nice/holy/morally good] by standard x2. Holy/saintly (= cesyvu'e). Virtue the attribute is "ka vrude". See also palci, xamgu, marde, zabna.
lujvo m1=s1 is a squeak/creak/quiet noise to s2. Cf. savru, milxe.
lujvo c1 makes/produces a rustling/crackling sound by process c3. Cf. savru, rapli, kinli, cupra, vruvricypra.

gismu rafsi: vus vu'i x1 (ka) is a taste/flavor of/emitted by x2; x2 tastes of/like x1. Also: x2 tastes of seasoning x1, x1 is a seasoned flavor of x2 (= tsapyvu'i); vrusi may overlap the senses of taste and smell, since the latter is a significant component of taste. See also kukte, tsapi, cpina.
lujvo c1 makes/produces a rich complex sound by process c3. Cf. savru, ricfu, cupra, vrurapkilpra.
cmavo rafsi: vuz VA location tense distance: far from ... ; yonder at ... ; a long distance from ...
cmavo FAhA1 location tense relation/direction; west of.
cmavo UI5 attitudinal modifier: virtue - sin. See also vrude, zungi.
cmavo cluster UI*5 attitudinal modifier: virtue - sin.
cmavo LAhE sumti qualifier: the sequence made from set or composed of elements/components; order is vague.
lujvo z1 tastes v2 using taste buds z3 under conditions z4. Cf. vrusi, zgana, vusyga'e, kukte.
cmavo VUhO joins relative clause/phrase to complete complex or logically connected sumti in afterthought.
cmavo VUhU1 n-ary mathematical operator: minus; subtraction operator; [(((a - b) - c) - ...)].
lujvo vr1=vi1 is a hero/heroic in doing vi2 by standard vr2=vi3.
lujvo v1=p1 is fair / does justice to p2 by standard v2.
gismu rafsi: vur vu'o x1 reflects Ukrainian language/culture/nationality in aspect x2. See also slovo, softo.
lujvo v1=b1 is the Ukrainian language used by b2 to express/communicate b3 (si'o/du'u, not quote). Cf. vukro, bangu, bangukuru.
lujvo g1 tastes g2=v1 (flavor) emitted by v2. Cf. vrusi, ganse, kukte, vu'izga.
fu'ivla x1 reflects Han Chinese [Mandarin, Cantonese, Wu, etc.] culture/nationality/language in aspect x2. Cf. jungo, jugygu'e, jugbau, djunguos, gugdecunu, gugdetuve.
lujvo v1 is an envelope for/containing letter xa1=v2. Cf. xa'argai.
lujvo b1=xa1 settles in xa2 Cf. xabju, zdani.
lujvo j1 is the home address of xa1=j1 with address system j3.
gismu rafsi: xa'u x1 dwells/lives/resides/abides at/inhabits/is a resident of location/habitat/nest/home/abode x2. See also ginka, zdani, zvati, stuzi, jmive, stali, vitke.
lujvo xa1=m1 is the mate of xa1=m2 with property m3 in pair xa2.
lujvo x1 is most/a majority/more than half of x2 in property x3 by amount x4 by standard x5. See also so'e, xabme'a
lujvo x1 is a minority/less than half of x2 in property x3 by amount x4 by standard x5. See also xabmau
lujvo x1 is exactly/approximately a quarter of x2 by standard x3. Cf. xadba.
lujvo xa1=c1 is a gun/cannon/firearm launching projectile c2 propelled by c3, for use against xa2 by xa3. jvajvo definition; Gismu deep structure is "xarci gi'e cecla"
lujvo g1=x1 is a club/cudgel/truncheon/bludgeon made of g2 used against x2 by x3. Cf. xarci, grana.
gismu rafsi: xab x1 is exactly/approximately half/semi-/demi-/hemi- of x2 by standard x3. See also mulno, pagbu.

lujvo xa2=b1=m1 is adolescent/pubescent/in puberty/maturing in physical/bodily development-quality m2 (ka). Cf. xadni, binxo, makcu, bixma'u, bavyfarvi, citnau. Between prepubescent child and post-pubescent adult.
lujvo x1=m1 is the waist of x2=m2.
gismu rafsi: xad x1 is a/the body/corpus/corpse of x2; (adjective:) x1 is corporal/corporeal. See also menli, pruxi, sluji, mulno, cutne.
lujvo c1=xa1 is tall / has a long body by standard c3. Made from clani + xadni.
lujvo c1 is/are a/the physical sport(s) exercised/played by x2. Cf. xadni, kelci, ciste.
lujvo j1=xa2 competes with opponent j2 in sport/athletics j3 for gain j4=p3. Cf. zajba, bajyjvi, boltipyjvi, karcyplijvi.
gismu x1 hungers for x2; x1 needs/wants food/fuel x2. See also cidja, citka, djica, nitcu, taske.
lujvo j1 is optimistic about j3. Cf. xamgu, jijnu, xlajijnu.
lujvo xa1=z1 is better than z2 for xa2 by standard xa3, by amount z4. Cf. xamgu, zmadu, xlame'a, xauzma, xagmau, xagrai. The canonical form is xauzma.
lujvo xa1=m1 is worse than/not as good as m2 for xa2 by standard xa3, by amount m4. Cf. xamgu, mleca, xlamau, xauzma, xagmau, xagrai.
lujvo t1=x1 is the best among set/range t4 for x2 by standard x3. Cf. xamgu, traji, mecyxlarai, xauzma, xagmau, xagme'a, zanrai.
gismu x1 is a oboe/clarinet/saxophone [reed musical instrument] with reed x2. See also zgike.
fu'ivla x1 is a clarinet with reed x2. Cf. xagri, zgica'a.
fu'ivla x1 is a saxophone with reed x2. Cf. xagri, zgica'a.
lujvo x1 is a reed of species/variety x2. see also selxagri, junkace
lujvo f1 progresses towards f2=x1 from f3 through stages f4. Cf. farvi, banro.
lujvo g1 (agent) improves z1=x1 for x2 by amount z3. Cf. xamgu, zenba, gasnu, xagzenri'a.
lujvo r1 (event/state/process) improves z1=x1 for x2 by amount z3 under conditions r3. Cf. xamgu, zenba, rinka, xagzengau.
lujvo g1 causes event x1 which injures/harms/damages victim x2 in property x3 (ka) resulting in injury x4 (state). Made from xrani + gasnu.

gismu rafsi: xam x1 is funny/comical to x2 in property/aspect x3 (nu/ka); x3 is what is funny about x1 to x2. Also: x1 is a comedian (= xampre, xamseljibri for a professional comedian). (x1 can be a person/object or an abstraction; be careful about possible sumti-raising); See also bebna, cisma, cmila, fenki, zdile.
lujvo c1=x1 is a/the grunt of a pig/hog/swine of species x2 expressing c3 (property). Cf. xarju, cmoni.
lujvo z1 is the snout of pig/hog/swine/[boar] z2=x1 of species x2, with nostril(s)/nasal passage(s) z3. Cf. xarju, nazbi.
cmavo cluster PA* number/quantity: 6,000 expressed with comma.
gismu rafsi: xak x1 (event) uses up/depletes/consumes/[wastes] x2 [resource]. Waste (= fesxaksu, dusxaksu). See also citka, festi, daspo, livla, pinxe.
lujvo x1=b1 is a saloon/pub/bar primarily serving alcoholic beverages to x2=b3. xalka+barja
lujvo x1 is drunk/tipsy in manner x2 from drinking x3 (alcohol).
gismu x1 uses levity/is non-serious/frivolous about x2 (abstraction). See also junri, linto.
gismu rafsi: xal x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of alcohol of type x2 from source/process x3. See also birje, jikru, vanju.
lujvo xa1=c1 is alcoholic of alcohol type xa2 from source/process xa3.
gismu x1 (person) is panicked by crisis x2 (event/state). See also ckape, snura, terpa, xanka.
lujvo n1 is alcohol poisoning of x2=v2 from alcohol type x3=xa2.
lujvo p1 drinks to much alcohol of type p2 from p3 by standard d3; p1 is a drunk from xalka pinxe dukse c.f. xalbebna
fu'ivla x1 pertains to the Sikh culture/religion/ethos in aspect x2
lujvo v1 throws up v2 due to alcohol of type xa2.
lujvo g1 does/brings about event/state g2=xa1 which is funny/comical to xa2 in property/aspect xa3 (nu/ka).
gismu rafsi: xag xau x1 (object/event) is good/beneficial/nice/[acceptable] for x2 by standard x3. Acceptable (= mlixau, norxau, xaurselcru). See also melbi, xlali, vrude, zabna.
cmavo cluster MOI* quantified selbri: convert 6 to ordinal selbri; x1 is sixth among x2 ordered by rule x3.

gismu rafsi: xap xa'o x1 is x2 ampere(s) [metric unit] in current (default is 1) by standard x3. See also dikca, flecu, centi, decti, dekto, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, xexso, zepti, zetro.

gismu rafsi: xas x1 is a sea/ocean/gulf/[atmosphere] of planet x2, of fluid x3; (adjective:) x1 is marine. Also atmosphere (= varxamsi, varsenta). See also daplu, djacu, lalxu, rirxe, tumla, vacri, zbani, ctaru.
lujvo x1 tells/expresses joke x2 (sedu'u/text/lu'e concept) for audience x3 via expressive medium x4. Cf. zdilisri.
lujvo b1 is a Signed Language used by x2=b2 to express/communicate b3 (si'o/du'u, not quote).
gismu rafsi: xan xa'e x1 is a/the hand [body-part] of x2; [metaphor: manipulating tool, waldo]. (adjective:) x1 is manual. See also birka, degji, jitro, xlura, jamfu, tamji.

lujvo j1 is a bracelet adorning j2=xa1=c1. Bracelets are used not only for fashion but also for medical and identification purposes, such as allergy bracelets and hospital patient-identification tags. Cf. jadni.
lujvo x1=c1 is a wrist of x2=c2. Cf. xance, cidni, birka.
lujvo c1 is a fingernail of finger c2=d1 of body d3. Cf. jgalu, degycalku, jmadegycalku, jmatajycalku, xantajycalku.
lujvo g1 masturbates/fucks g2 with her/his hand(s). Cf. sezgle, xanse'agle, gaxygle, runpinji, desmi'i.
fu'ivla x1 is a hangul (Korean alphabet) of sound x2. Cf. lerfu, lerldjamo, bangrxangu, bangrxanguke, bangrtcosena, banku'oru.
lujvo s1 hold hands/are hand-in-hand. Cf. xance, jgari, simxu.
lujvo m1=j2 is a moose/Eurasian elk of species m2 Alces alces noted for its hand-shaped antlers. See also mirlruapiti
gismu x1 is nervous/anxious about x2 (abstraction) under conditions x3. See also xalni, terpa, raktu.
lujvo x1=d1 is anxious/earnestly desirous for x2=d2 (abstract), the purpose being d3. Cf. xanka, djica.
lujvo x1 is x2 handfuls in volume/amount (default is 1) by standard x3.

gismu rafsi: xar x1 [concept] exists in the imagination of/is imagined by/is imaginary to x2. Also (adjective:) x1 is mental (one sense), x1 is unreal (one sense); in spite of the synonym, note that x1 is imaginary does not imply that it doesn't exist in the real world; the definition is crafted so that one can talk about imaginary things without claiming that they thereby don't exist. See also fatci, senva, sucta, zasti, cfika, dacti, menli, sidbo.
lujvo g1=s1=xa2 fist-fucks/performs fisting on g2 in opening s3. Cf. bolxa'e, gaxygle.
lujvo c1 is the thumbnail of body t3=j2. Cf. jgalu, tajyja'u, jmatajycalku, degycalku, xandegycalku.
lujvo x1=g3 is a flashlight/portable light source for illuminating g2, emitting light form x3=g1. Cf. selbeika'e, selbeifonxa, selbeiskami.
gismu x1 is an elephant of species/breed x2. See also mabru, barda.
lujvo m1 is elephant/mammoth ivory from species/breed xa2. Cf. odbenu, xiptamu.
lujvo z1=x2 gives applause to plan/action z2 (object/event). Cf. xance, savru, zanru, ki'arzau.
gismu rafsi: xac xa'i x1 is a weapon/arms for use against x2 by x3. Gun/cannon (= celxa'i). See also jenmi, sonci, catra.
fu'ivla x1 is an artichoke of species/variety x2.
gismu rafsi: xaj x1 is a pig/hog/swine/[boar] [pork/ham/bacon-producer] of species/breed x2. Sow (= fetxarju), boar (= nakyxarju), pork (= xajre'u), piglet (= citxarju). See also mabru, cange.

gismu x1 is stubborn/willfully opposing/resisting x2 about x3 (event/state). x2 may be a person, a state or condition, or a force; the essence is willful resistance. See also tinsa, pante, bapli, fapro.

lujvo p1 = x2 imagines / visualizes imaginary subject / concept p2 = x1. Not limited to visual imagination. Made from xanri + pensi; technically should be selxarpei, but I can't see "xanri pensi" having any other meaning.
lujvo xa1=p1 is a character/role/imaginary person created by xa2.
lujvo k1 is a beach/coast of sea xa1=k2 on landmass k3.
gismu x1 is a donkey/jackass of species/breed x2. See also xirma, kumte.
gismu x1 is a/the sweat/perspiration from body x2, excreted by gland(s)/organs x3. See also pinca, vikmi, cigla.
lujvo x1 is under sea x2 in reference frame x3.
lujvo c1 is a sea worm of species c2. Cf. curnu, xamsi, curfi'e.
lujvo d1 is a torpedo launched by d2. Cf. xamsi, danti, jbama, xasyjbama.
lujvo j1 is a sea mine with explosive material/principle j2. Cf. xamsi, jbama, xasydanti.
lujvo j1 is a crab/lobster/crayfish/shrimp/krill/[marine crustacean] of species j2. Cf. xamsi, jukni, cakyjukni, braxiura, nerfopi.
lujvo s1 is the oceanography/marine science of planet x2. Cf. xamsi, saske, varxasyske.

gismu rafsi: xa'a x1 is a letter/missive/[note] to intended audience x2 from author/originator x3 with content x4. (cf. notci, which has places in a different order; the emphasis in xatra is on the communication between author and recipient, and not the content, which in a letter may not easily be categorized to a 'subject'; ciska, mrilu, papri)
gismu rafsi: xat x1 is 10^{-18} of x2 in dimension/aspect x3 (default is units).
lujvo xa1=z1 is better than z2 for xa2 by standard xa3, by amount z4. Cf. xamgu, zmadu, xagmau, xagrai. The xagmau form is far more frequently used.
lujvo x1 is a Saturday of week x2 in calendar x3.
lujvo x1 is June/the sixth month of year x2 in calendar x3. Cf. pavmasti, nanca.

lujvo j1 has the rank of Brigadier General/Brigadier/Rear Admiral/Commodore (equivalent of NATO OF-6) in military unit /organization j2. Cf. xa, moi, jatna, jemja'a, vairsoi, zelmoija'a, mumymoija'a. Based on STANAG 2116: NATO Codes for Grades of Military Personnel.
cmavo cluster PA* number/quantity: 64,000 expressed with comma.

lujvo p1 is the sixth closest planet (default is Saturn if p2 is the Sun) revolving around p2 (default is the Sun), with planetary characteristics p3, orbital parameters p4. Cf. xavyplin, pavyplini, relplini etc.; see also terdi, solri, mluni, lunra, plinycma, tarci'e.
lujvo c1=da1 is a Vulpix [six-tailed fox Pokémon]
gismu rafsi: xaz zdo x1 reflects Asiatic culture/nationality/geography in aspect x2. See also polno, friko, jungo, rusko, ropno.
cmavo rafsi: xel SE 5th conversion; switch 1st/5th places.
cmavo cluster BAI* benji modal, 5th place (medium) transmitted via ...

gismu rafsi: xen xei x1 hates/despises x2 (object/abstraction); x1 is full of hate for x2; x2 is odious to x1. x1 is hateful (one sense); x2 is hateful (different sense). See also djica, nitcu, rigni, prami, nelci.
gismu rafsi: xeb bro x1 reflects Hebrew/Jewish/Israeli culture/nationality/language in aspect x2. See also filso.

gismu rafsi: xet cto x1 is a hundred [100; 10^2] of x2 in dimension/aspect x3 (default is units). Cf. grake, mitre, snidu, stero, delno, molro, kelvo, xampo, gradu, litce, merli, centi, decti, dekto, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xexso, zepti, zetro.
gismu rafsi: xej xe'a x1 is a/the jaw [body-part] of x2. See also stedu.
lujvo c1 is a/the chin [body part] of x2. Cf. xedja, cnita.
lujvo r1=x2 is an alligator/caiman of species/type r2 cf. krokodilo This is family Alligatoridae.
lujvo x1 is the beard of x2.
cmavo cluster BAI* klama modal, 5th place by transport mode ...
lujvo c1 is a blackbird of species c2. Cf. xekri, cipni, cipnrkorvo, cipnrpika.
gismu rafsi: xek xe'i x1 is black/extremely dark-colored [color adjective]. See also blabi, grusi, manku, skari, xekri, kandi, carmi, blanu, bunre, cicna, crino, narju, nukni, pelxu, xunre, zirpu.

lujvo x1 is is made of/contains/is a quantity of a black/very-dark colored carbonated beverage/soda of cola-flavor, of brand x2. Not any black, carbonated beverage, but one with cola-flavor, like Coca-Cola (=kokaKOlys), Pepsi, Julmust (=a soft drink that is mainly consumed in Sweden around Christmas;=(sfe'ero) xisyjbenunsla xeksodva) or similar. Another flavor may be added and expressed as a tanru, as long as the combination doesn't differ too much from the characteristics of xeksodva.
lujvo x1 is ho-shou-wu/fleeceflower of variety x2.
lujvo x5=b1 transfers/sends/transmits x2=b2 to receiver x3=b3 from transmitter/origin x4=b4 via means/medium x1=b5. xe benji; see also bevri, ve cusku.
lujvo b2 (person/animal/plant) digests p2 with output p3 passing through stage p4. Cf. citka, tunlo, befru'e, djaruntygau, djaruntyrango.
lujvo x5=b1 carries/hauls/bears/transports cargo x2=b2 to x3=b3 from x4=b4 over path x1=b5; x5=b1 is a carrier/porter. xe bevri
lujvo x5=b1 is a wave/periodic pattern in medium x2=b2, with wave-form x3=b3, wave-length x4=b4 and frequency x1=b5. xe boxna
lujvo j2 is a radio band with borders j1.

lujvo x1 is a class [biology] with genus x2, family x3, order x4, and with species x5. For biological cathegory in general (=mivyske klesi), domain (=?), kingdom (=seljimcymivykle), phylum (=jicymivykle), class (=this definition), order (=veljutsi), family (=terjutsi), genus (=seljutsi), species (=jutsi).
lujvo Using means/vehicle x1, to x2, from x3, via x4, goes x5.
gismu rafsi: xes x1 reflects Greek/Hellenic culture/nationality/language in aspect x2. See also latmo, ropno.
fu'ivla x1 is Swiss in aspect x2.
gismu rafsi: xed xe'o x1 (person) is kind to x2 in actions/behavior x3. See also cinmo, kecti, pendo, kusru.
gismu rafsi: xer xe'u x1 regrets/rues (abstraction) x2; x1 is regretful/rueful/sorry/[remorseful] about x2. Also: x1 feels remorse about x2 (= zugyxe'u). (cf. cmavo list .u'u, zungi)

gismu rafsi: xex x1 is 10^{18} of x2 in dimension/aspect x3 (default is units). Cf. grake, mitre, snidu, stero, delno, molro, kelvo, xampo, gradu. litce, merli, centi, decti, dekto, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, zepti, zetro.
cmavo XI subscript; attaches a numer of letteral string following as a subscript onto grammar structures.
fu'ivla x1 is a gibbon of species x2. cf. smani
fu'ivla x1 is a gibbon of species x2. Cf. smani, birdadykla.
lujvo xa1=c1 is an artillery gun for use against xa2 by xa3, launching projectile c2 propelled by c3. Cf. xislu, cecla, xarci, xumjimcelxa'i, gutyjamkarce, xiljamkarce, karcycelxa'i, sorjaknykarce.
lujvo c1=xi3 is a wheel tyre/tire. The rubber source can be expressed with "ra'i ...", the composition with "ma'e ...".
lujvo k1 is a military armoured car propelled by k3. Cf. xislu, jamna, karce, jamkarce, gutyjamkarce, sonjamkarce, tsakarce, karcycelxa'i.

lujvo t1=xi1 is a board with wheels/skateboard/longboard/snakeboard [default skateboard], of material/property t2 with wheels [material/property] xi3. From tanbo, djacu, boxna (b2-b5 subsumed). Also longboard (=clani xilta'o), streetboard, snakeboard etc.

lujvo v1=x1 is a rotavirus of species/breed/defining property v2 capable of infecting [at] v3. x2 may be abu (A), by (B), cy (C),dy (D) or ebu (E). Rotavirus A, the most common, causes more than 90% of infections in humans. See also vidru, norvokovidru and remjinkytoldu'evidru.
lujvo x1=b1 is the Hindi language used by b2 to communicate b3 Cf. xindo, bangu, banxe'inu.

gismu rafsi: xin x1 reflects Hindi language/culture/religion in aspect x2. Defaults to not include Urdu; Indian (Bharat) nationality may be implied (when constrained by xingu'e). See also srito, xurdo, bengo.
lujvo x1=g1=b1 is the Indian English language used by b2 to express/communicate b3 (si'o/du'u, not quote). Cf. glico, bangu, bangenugu, glibau, xinbau.
lujvo x1=g1 is India. Cf. xindo, gugde, gugde'inu.
gismu rafsi: xim x1 is a quantity of ink of color/pigment x2 used by writing device x3. See also penbi.
fu'ivla x1 is a hippopotamus of species/breed x2. Cf. ri'erxi'a, xanto, odbenu, xantydenmai.
lujvo m1 is a mass of set m2 with an odd number of members m3 see also landegmei
fu'ivla x1 is a hiragana (Japanese syllabary) of sound x2. Cf. lerfu.
gismu rafsi: xir xi'a x1 is a horse/equine/[colt/mare/stallion/pony] of species/breed x2. (adjective:) x1 is equine/equestrian. See also sufti, xasli, kumte.
lujvo x1 is a noble with nobility standard x2.
lujvo s1 is a horse cavalryman of army s2. Cf. xirma, sonci, dzusoi.
lujvo z1 is a stable for horse/equine/[colt/mare/stallion/pony] z2=x1 of species/breed
lujvo n1 is Easter celebrated by s1 with activities s3 from xriso cliva nu salci c.f. xisyjbenunsla
gismu rafsi: xil xi'u x1 is a wheel [tool] of device/vehicle x2, made of materials/having properties x3. See also carce, karce, pulni, tutci.

gismu rafsi: xip x1 reflects Hispano-American culture/nationalities in aspect x2. Refers to Spanish-speaking Latin-American countries, not Brazil/Guyana. See also merko, mexno, spano, ketco, bemro, gento.
lujvo n1 is Christmas Eve of Christmas Day n2 at location n3. Cf. xisyjbenunsla, xisyjbedetri.
lujvo d1 is Christmas Day at location d3 in calendar d4. c.f. xisyjbenunsla, xisyjbecte
lujvo n1 is the Christmas celebrated by s1 with activities s3. Cf. xisyjbedetri, xisyjbecte, xislivnunsla, cmuxi'ojbetersla.
lujvo d1 is spiteful/malevolent/malicious/mean to/towards x2. Cf. fengu, palci.
lujvo x1 suffers from x2 (event, process, object).
lujvo f1=xl1 is unlucky/unfortunate for f2=xl2 by standerd xl3.
lujvo j1 is pessimistic about j3. Cf. xlali, jijnu, xlajijnu, tradutxu'a.

gismu rafsi: xla x1 is bad for x2 by standard x3; x1 is poor/unacceptable to x2. Be careful to distinguish between a bad/unacceptable event, and a bad/unacceptable agent: x1 does poorly (= lenu ko'a gasnu cu xlali and not normally ko'a xlali). See also palci, mabla, xamgu, betri.
lujvo x1=m1 is worse than m2 for x2 by standard x3, by amount m3. Cf. xlali, zmadu, xagme'a, xlarai.
lujvo x1=m1 is better/[less bad] than m2 for x2 by standard x3, by amount m4. Cf. mleca, xlali, traji, xagmau, xlamau, xlarai, mecyxlarai.
lujvo j1 is cynical/suspicious about the motives of m3 with regard to action/event m2=j3. Cf. xlali, mukti, jijnu, xlajijnu, remxei.
lujvo t1=x1 is the worst among set/range t4 for x2 by standard x3. Cf. xlali, traji, xlamau.
lujvo t1=xl1 is bad weather at place/region t2 for x3=xl2 by standard x4=xl3. Cf. carvi, xa'urti'a.
lujvo x1 is September of year x2 in calendar x3. Cf. sozymasti, kanbyma'i, nanca.

gismu rafsi: xlu x1 (agent) influences/lures/tempts x2 into action/state x3 by influence/threat/lure x4. Also impresses; x4 is alluring (= trivelxlu for place reordering); x3 may be an achieved action/state, or an attempt to perform an action/enter a state). (x3 and x4 are normally events or states); See also djica, mukti, trina, jitro, sazri, tcica, xance, stidi, kajde, maksi.
cmene Xod. A name used by Charles Hope.
fu'ivla x1 is an ocotillo of species x2
cmene Hong Kong. Cf. xyngon, cangan, jungo, tcadu.
fu'ivla x1 is sesame of species/variety x2. syn. jerjelino, simsimu
fu'ivla x1 is a saddlebag/pair of saddlebags to use on animal/vehicle x2.
gismu rafsi: xol xoi x1 is a hotel/inn/hostel at location x2 operated by x3. See also barja, gusta.
gismu rafsi: rab x1 reflects Arabic-speaking culture/nationality in aspect x2. See also sadjo, semto, lubno, rakso, sirxo.
lujvo c1=p3 draws picture c2=p1 on medium c3=p4 with implement c4 depicting p2. Cf. pixra, ciska, xraselci'a, xratai, kacmyxra, kacmyterxra, kacmyxragau, kacmyxrazu'e.
lujvo k1=p4 is an illustrated magazine/journal with content k2=p1 published by k3 for audience k4.
gismu rafsi: xai x1 (event) injures/harms/damages victim x2 in property x3 (ka) resulting in injury x4 (state). Also hurts. See also cortu, daspo, spofu, katna, porpi.
lujvo c2=p1 is drawn by artist c1=p3 on medium c3=p4 using implement c4 depicting p2. Cf. pixra, ciska, xraci'a, xratai, kacmyxra, kacmyterxra, kacmyxragau, kacmyxrazu'e.
lujvo t1=p1 is an image of t2=p2 created by agent p3 on medium p4. Cf. pixra, tarmi.
lujvo b1=m1=s1 is creole used by b2 to express/communicate b3, created from sources including m2. Cf. sapxrebau.
lujvo x1=min1 is a blender/mixer for ingredients x2=mix2 to produce mixture x3=mix1. not necessarily for food. Cf. mixre, minji.
gismu rafsi: xis xi'o x1 pertains to the Christian religion/culture/nationality in aspect x2. See also jegvo, lijda.
fu'ivla x1 is the Christian Bible of Christian denomination x2
lujvo x1 is buckwheat of variety x2. syn. gruxruba
gismu rafsi: xub x1 is a quantity of buckwheat/rhubarb/sorrel grass of species/strain x2. See also spati.
lujvo b1=x1 takes/carries back b2=x2 to origin/earlier state b3=x3 from b4=x4 over path b5. Cf. xruti, bevri.
lujvo c1 requests/asks c2 to go back/return to x2 from x3. Cf. xruti, cpedu. Based on proposed redefinition of xruti by xorxes: x1 returns to x2 from x3.
lujvo g1 causes x1 to return to state x2 from state x3. Cf. xruti, gasnu. Based on proposed redefinition of xruti by xorxes: x1 returns to state x2 from state x3.
gismu rafsi: xuk x1 is a turkey [food/bird] of species/breed x2. See also cipni.
lujvo x1=xr1=xr2=k1 returns to earlier location x2=xr3=k2 from x3=xr4=k3 via route x4=k4 using means/vehicle x5=k5. See also se'ixru.
gismu rafsi: rul x1 is a/the flower/blossom/bloom [body-part] of plant/species x2; (adjective:) x1 is floral. See also spati.
fu'ivla x1 is a quantity of ranunculus/buttercup/spearwort/water crowfoot of species/strain x2 Cf. matnyxrula.
fu'ivla x1 is a quantity of lavender of species/strain x2

gismu rafsi: xru x1 (agent) returns x2 to origin/earlier state x3 from x4; x1 moves/gives x2 back to x3 from x4. x2 goes back/reverts/Retreats. to x3 (= se'ixru for agent self-returning to a previous location/situation: renumber places in the lujvo); (x3 may be a location or a person or an event/situation; the latter may also be expressed with krefu or rapli and a causative like rinka/rikygau). See also benji, krefu, rapli, rinka.
lujvo x1 is an element of compound x2.
gismu rafsi: xum xu'i x1 is an instance of substance/chemical/drug x2 (individual or mass) with purity x3. See also curve, cidro, marna, nimre.
lujvo x1 is meleagrology based on methodology x2.
lujvo x1=t1 is an iron for straightening cloths x2=b1=xu1 of material x3=b2.

lujvo x1 = c1 is a gun/chemically launched metal slug throwing weapon for use against x2 by x3; weapon fires metallic objects x4 using chemical propellant x5. Cf. xilcelxa'i, mi'ircelxa'i, clacelxa'i, janjaknyxa'i, celgunta. Made from xukmi + jinme + cecla + xarci.
fu'ivla x1 is a quantity of concrete made from ingredients x2.
lujvo x1 is chemistry based on methodology x2.
lujvo s1 is a molecule of chemical x2. c.f. selci, xukmi, ratni, lektoni, protoni, nurtoni.
lujvo r1=x1 catalyzes chemical reaction r2=s2 under conditions r3. Cf. sutri'a, selfusra.
lujvo t1 is a chemical compound of t2 and t3.
lujvo b1=x1 is pink. Cf. xunre, blabi, labyxu'e.
gismu rafsi: xun xu'e x1 is red/crimson/ruddy [color adjective]. See also skari, blabi, xekri, kandi, carmi, nukni, narju, rozgu, zirpu.
lujvo x1 is a cherry [berry] of species/variety x2 Cf. smela
lujvo x1=b1 is the Urdu language used by b2 to express/communicate b3 (si'o/du'u, not quote). Cf. xurdo, bangu, bangurudu.
gismu rafsi: xur xu'o x1 reflects Urdu language/culture/nationality in aspect x2. See also kisto, srito, xindo.

gismu rafsi: xus xu'a x1 (agent) asserts/claims/declares x2 (du'u) is true [can be used for epistemology of authority]. Also: x1 states/says that/affirms/purports to know that x2. (cf. natfe which is propositional and non-agentive, nupre)
fu'ivla x1 is vetiver of species/variety x2.
gismu rafsi: xul x1 is smooth/even/[soft/silky] in texture/regularity. See also plita, rufsu, tengu, dikni, pinta, sakli, spali.
cmene Hong Kong. Cf. cangan, xonkon, jungo, tcadu.
cmavo Y hesitation noise; maintains the floor while speaker decides what to say next.
cmavo ZI time tense distance: medium distance in time.
cmavo UI2 evidential: I observe. See also zgana, lanli.
cmavo BAhE forethought nonce-word indicator; indicates next word is nonce-creation and may be nonstandard.
cmavo rafsi: zaz NU1 abstractor: state (event) abstractor; x1 is continuous state of [bridi] being true.
cmavo rafsi: za'o ZAhO interval event contour: continuing too long after natural end of ...; superfective | ---->.
cmavo cluster MAI* discursive: further utterance ordinal
cmavo cluster ROI* again; in addition to the first time; for the (> 1)th time See krefu, rapli
gismu rafsi: zan za'a x1 is a favorable connotation/sense/way-of-looking-at x2 used by x3. See also funca, mabla, xamgu, vrude.
lujvo c1 the telemarketing business/activity/function for goods/products/services/activities z2. Cf. zarci, fonxa, cuntu, zaircu'u, zairsnucu'u, venynoicu'u, venxatrycu'u, vencu'u.
lujvo p1=z1 is a market place/square/area managed by p2 for selling/trading z2 by traders z3. Cf. zarci, panka, gubypanka, zdipanka, fanrypanka, kagnypanka.
lujvo t1 is the thigh of t2=z2. The thigh is the area between the pelvis and the knee. Anatomically, it is part of the lower limb. Cf. tuple.
cmavo LAU 2-word letteral/shift: alternate alphabet selector follows.
lujvo c1 is a marketing /business/activity/function for goods/products/services/activities z2. Cf. zarci, cuntu, zairsnucu'u, venynoicu'u, venxatrycu'u, zacfoncu'u, faircu'u, vencu'u.

lujvo c1 is the marketing communications business/activity/function supporting the sales/promotion of goods/products/services/activities z2. Cf. zarci, casnu, cuntu, zaircu'u, venynoicu'u, venxatrycu'u, zacfoncu'u, faircu'u, vencu'u.
lujvo z1=s1 is a shop/store of market/mall s2, selling x3=z2, operated by x4=z3. Cf. vecnu, ja'orca'o.
gismu rafsi: zaj x1 is a gymnast at/performs gymnastics feat x2. See also sluji, dansu.
fu'ivla x1 is a spiny anteater of species x2. see also jesymabru, ornitorinku
lujvo t1 is a patty of ground/pulverized material t2=z2, shape t3, thickness t4.
gismu rafsi: zal x1 [individual or mass of hard surfaces] grinds/pulverizes/crushes x2 into powder x3. May need mosra tanru. See also daspo, purmo, marxa, pulce, canre, molki.
lujvo b1 is naïve about z2 from zabna bebna
lujvo f1=z2 (event/property) is determined by the good luck/fortune of f2. Cf. zabna, funca, {malfu'a).
lujvo zm1=za1 is better than zm2 in property za2 according to standard za3 by amount zm4. Cf. zabna, zmadu, xagmau, xauzma.
lujvo t1=z1 is most favourable among set/range t4 in property z2 according to standard z3. Cf. zabna, traji, zanmau, xagrai, mecyxlarai.
gismu rafsi: zar zau x1 approves of/gives favor to plan/action x2 (object/event). See also cmavo list zau, natfe.
lujvo f2 is lucky/fortunate in f1=z2 (event/property). Cf. zabna, funca, selfu'a, malselfu'a.
lujvo x1 is welcomed by x2 to place/event x3. See also zabna vitke; fi'i

gismu rafsi: zac zai x1 is a market/store/exchange/shop(s) selling/trading (for) x2, operated by/with participants x3. Also: mall, marketplace, shopping center, cooperative, bazaar, trading post, mart; the concept is the function of selling/exchanging coupled with a location, and is more oriented to the larger concept of marketplace than the stalls/shops that comprise it, though it does not exclude the latter individual shops (= zaisle); x3 may include both owners/proprietors and customers in some markets, but in most contexts refers only to the operators. See also vecnu, canja, dinju, banxa.
lujvo z1=c1 accepts z2=c2 (object/event) from source c3. Cf. zanru, cpacu, friti, sarxe, fitytu'i, radji'i, cpazau.
gismu rafsi: zag za'u x1 is a/the buttock(s)/arse/rear/seat [body-part] of x2; [metaphor: rounded surface, support]. Also ass, behind, butt. See also ganxo, mabla.
lujvo s1 is temporary memory for fact(s) s2=m2 in containment s3.
gismu rafsi: zas x1 is temporary/not permanent/expected to change in property x2 (ka) by standard/expectant x3. Also transient. See also vitno, stodi, cenba, galfi, binxo, stika, stali, tcini, vitke.
gismu rafsi: zat za'i x1 exists/is real/actual/reality for x2 under metaphysics x3. Words usable for epistemology typically have a du'u place. x1 is physical (one sense). See also fatci, xanri.
lujvo s1 pauses/temporarily halts activity/process/state s2. Cf. denpa.
lujvo x1 rents x2 [goods/service/commodity] to x3 for cost x4 for duration x5 Cf. zasni, vecnu
lujvo f1 discovers the existence of x2=z1 under metaphysics z3.
lujvo r1=z1 exists over interval r2. r1=z1 is r2 years/days etc. old. Not restricted to biological forms. Cf. zasti, ranji, temci, ditcu, jbena, morsi, cfari, fanmo, jmive.
cmavo BAI zanru modal, 1st place approved by ...
lujvo c1=z1 praises z2 (object/event) for audience c3 via expressive medium c4.
gismu rafsi: bab x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of soap from source x2 of composition including x3. See also lumci, fonmo.

lujvo c1 is a/the production/building/assembling function/activities involving person(s) c2=z1(ind./mass) making/building/assembling z2 out of z3. Cf. zbasu, cuntu, zbaske, terzbasro, selvensro, zbagundi, fanrygundi.

lujvo c1 is/are the function/activities involving persons c2 developing products f2=z2 made by z1; c1 is product development. C.f. zbasu, farvi, zbaske, vencu'u, zbacu'u, faircu'u, dintrocu'u, dinveicu'u.
lujvo g1 is a/the industry sector of z1 building/assembling/constructing g2=z2 z3=g3. Cf. zbasu, gundi.
gismu x1 is a bay in/of coast/shoreline x2. See also lalxu, xamsi.
lujvo s1 is the engineering/technology of/behind products z2 made of materials/parts/components z3. Cf. zbasu, saske.
gismu rafsi: zba x1 makes/assembles/builds/manufactures/creates x2 out of materials/parts/components x3. Should not be used to express causation. Cf. cupra, larcu, rutni, finti, gundi.
gismu rafsi: zbe x1 is a pedestal/base/stand/pallet supporting x2 (object/event), of materials/properties x3. Pallet (= lafyzbe). See also jamfu, jicmu, jubme, tuple, ckana, cpana, loldi, sanli.
lujvo b1 is a handkerchief of type/material b2. Cf. daskybu'u.
lujvo k1 is a/are whisker(s)/hair on/in the nose of k2=n2. Cf. nazbi, kerfa, gaskre, runkre.
lujvo s1 sniffles fluid/gas/powder s2 through the nose. Cf. nazbi, sakci, zbisnava'u.
lujvo z2=j2 is a rhinoceros of species/type x2 from http://www.lojban.org/tiki/jbovlaste+import%3A+mammal+class+lang+en
lujvo v1 breathes gas v2 producing nasal sound; v1 snorts. Cf. nazbi, sance, vasxu, zbisakci, sipsavgau.
lujvo c1 is homeless. Cf. zdani, claxu, xabju, ginka
lujvo v1 is a hall door/front door of nest/house/lair/den v2=z1=c2.
lujvo x1 is a slipper/houseshoe for covering/protecting/keeping warm [feet] x2, and of material x3.
lujvo x1 is a building that is the house/home/nest/den of/for x2. From zdani dinju.
lujvo n1 is indoors. Cf. zdabartu, dijbartu.
gismu rafsi: zda x1 is a nest/house/lair/den/[home] of/for x2. Home (= tercnizda), house (constructed building) (= zdadi'u). See also dinju, ginka, kumfa, se xabju.
lujvo s1 is a house servant in/of house z1 owned by person s2=z2. Cf. zdani, selfu.
lujvo z2=c1=b1 is bored, lacking amusement c2=z1.
lujvo x1 is a swing (hanging seat) Cf. zdile, kelci, zdipincarcukla, zdirajycarcukla,zdima'aterte'e
lujvo x1=g1 entertains (agentive) x3=z2 with x2=z1; g1 makes z1 entertaining/amusing for z2 in property/aspect z3

gismu rafsi: zdi x1 (abstract) is amusing/entertaining to x2 in property/aspect x3; x3 is what amuses x2 about x1. Also: x1 occupies x2 pleasantly; x1 is fun for x2; x2 is amused by x1; x2 has fun (at) doing x1; x1 is an amusement/entertainment/game for x2. See also cinri, panka, xajmi for funny, kelci.
lujvo l1=z1 is an anecdote/funny story/joke about plot/subject/moral l2 by storyteller l1 to audience l4=z2, amusing in aspect x5=z3. Cf. xamsku.
lujvo x1 is a roller-coaster Cf. zdile, kelci, zdipincarcukla, zdirajycarcukla, zdidadysli
lujvo p1 is a park managed by polity/community p2 for use by z2, with amenities/amusements z1. Cf. zdile, panka, gubypanka, zacpanka, fanrypanka, kagnypanka.
lujvo x1 is a merry-go-round Cf. zdile, kelci, zdirajycarcukla, zdidadysli, zdima'aterte'e
lujvo x1 is a Ferris wheel Cf. zdile, kelci, zdipincarcukla, zdirajycarcukla, zdidadysli, zdima'aterte'e
fu'ivla x1 is a chinaberry of variety x2. See also margosa.
lujvo x1 is a Bactrian camel of breed x2. Cf. kumte, rabykumte, tcokumte, mabru.
lujvo z1=t1 is Asia. Cf. braplu, rontu'a, bemtu'a, tcotu'a, sralytu'a, frikytu'a, ziptu'a.
fu'ivla x1 is a durian (Durio zibethinus) of breed x2 See tcempedake
cmavo ZEhA time tense interval: a medium length of time.
cmavo cluster ZEhA* time tense: a medium time interval offset towards the future; (tense/modal).
cmavo cluster ZEhA* time tense: a medium time interval spanning the present; (tense/modal).
cmavo cluster ZEhA* time tense: a medium time interval offset towards the past; (tense/modal).
cmavo rafsi: ze'e ZEhA time tense interval: the whole of time.
lujvo x1 is an evergreen tree of species/variety x2. see also pezyfaltricu, ckunu
cmavo ZEhA time tense interval: an instantaneous/tiny/short amount of time.

lujvo d2 is/are the short-term indebtedness/liabilities of company/corporation/firm d1 to creditor(s) d3 for the provision of goods /services/loans d4. Cf. ze'i, dejni, zei, seldejni, kagyseldejni, ze'u zei seldejni, terdejni, paurseldejni, dejyterze'a.
cmavo rafsi: zev ze'o FAhA4 location tense relation/direction; beyond/outward/receding from ...
cmavo ZEhA time tense interval: a long amount of time.

lujvo d2 is/are the long-term indebtedness/liabilities of company/corporation/firm d1 to creditor(s) d3 for the provision of goods /services/loans d4. Cf. ze'u, zei, seldejni, kagyseldejni, ze'i zei seldejni, terdejni, paurseldejni, dejyterze'a.
cmavo ZEI joins preceding and following words into a lujvo.
cmavo cluster PA* number/quantity: 7,000 expressed with comma.

gismu rafsi: zer zei x1 (event/state) is a punishable crime/[taboo/sin] to people/culture/judges/jury x2. Taboo (= kluzei, cacyzei); sin (= madzei, jdamadzei); heresy (= jdazei). See also flalu, sfasa, zungi, palci, lijda, pajni, javni, tcaci, marde, pulji, tinbe.
lujvo x1 is a Sunday of week x2 in calendar x3. Sunday is either day seven or day zero, depending on your perspective.
lujvo x1 is July/the seventh month of year x2 in calendar x3. Cf. pavmasti, nanca.

lujvo j1 has the rank of Major General/Rear Admiral/Air Vice-Marshal (equivalent of NATO OF-7) in military unit /organization j2. Cf. ze, moi, jatna, jemja'a, vairsoi, bivmoija'a, xavmoija'a. Based on STANAG 2116: NATO Codes for Grades of Military Personnel.

lujvo p1 is the seventh closest planet (default is Uranus if p2 is the Sun) revolving around p2 (default is the Sun), with planetary characteristics p3, orbital parameters p4. Cf. zelplin, pavyplini, relplini etc.; see also terdi, solri,mluni, lunra, plinycma, tarci'e.
cmavo cluster MOI* quantified selbri: convert 7 to ordinal selbri; x1 is seventh among x2 ordered by rule x3.
gismu rafsi: zen ze'a x1 (experiencer) increases/is incremented/augmented in property/quantity x2 by amount x3. See also jdika, zmadu, banro, jmina.
lujvo x1 increases/augments x2 (experiencer) in property/quantity x3 by amount x4. See also zenba, zenri'a, stika.
lujvo r1 (event/state) increases/increments/augments x2=z1 in property/quantity x3=z2 by amount x4=z3. Cf. zengau.

gismu rafsi: zep x1 is 10^{-21} of x2 in dimension/aspect x3 (default is units). (cf. grake, mitre, snidu, stero, delno, molro, kelvo, xampo, gradu. litce, merli, centi, decti, dekto, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, xexso, zetro)
lujvo x1 is guilty of crime x2 accountable to judge/authority x3. Cf. zernalfu'e.
lujvo x1 accuses x2 of charge/crime x3 before judge/authority x4. See also zerfu'e, xusra
lujvo g1 (person/agent) commits a crime g2=z1, punishable to people/culture/judges/jury x3=z2. Cf. zerxaigau, zerxai.
lujvo j1 borrows j2 from j3 without permission of z2.
lujvo k1 is a poacher on prey/quarry/game k2, punishable to people/culture/judges/jury x3=z2.
lujvo l1 steals l2 from l3, which is a crime according to z2.
fu'ivla x1 is zerumbet/shell ginger of species/variety x2. This is Alpinia zerumbet. Zingiber zerumbet (awapuhi) is krelu'i zingibero. See also glangala.
lujvo f1 is innocent/not guilty of crime x2=f2=z1 (action/state) to judge/authority f3. Cf. zerfu'e.
lujvo xr1=z1 is a violent crime, injuring/harming/damaging victim xr2 in property xr3 (ka), resulting in injury xr4. Cf. zergau, zerxaigau.
lujvo g1 commits a violent crime g2=z1=xr1, injuring/harming/damaging victim x3=xr2 in property x4=xr3 (ka), resulting in injury x5=xr4. Cf. zergau, zerxai.

gismu rafsi: zet x1 is 10^{21} of x2 in dimension/aspect x3 (default is units). Cf. grake, mitre, snidu, stero, delno, molro, kelvo, xampo, gradu, litce, merli, centi, decti, dekto, femti, gigdo, gocti, gotro, kilto, megdo, mikri, milti, nanvi, petso, picti, terto, xatsi, xecto, xexso, zepti.
lujvo k1 comes/goes out/forth towards destination k2 from origin k3 via route k4 using means/vehicle k5. Cf. ze'o, klama, barkla.
lujvo x1 is the parallax of x2 as seen by x3 who moves to x4 from x5 Cf. kesyske

gismu rafsi: zga x1 observes/[notices]/watches/beholds x2 using senses/means x3 under conditions x4. Behold/watch/gaze (= vi'azga); guard/watchman/sentinel (= zgaku'i, jdeku'i). See also cmavo list ga'a, ganse, viska, catlu, tirna, pencu, sumne, kurji, canci, catlu, jarco, lanli, pinka, simlu.
lujvo t1=z1 listens to t2=z2 against background noise t3 under conditions z4. Cf. tinju'i.
lujvo v1 is a surveillance aircraft of type/for carrying v2, propelled by v3. Cf. zgana, vinji, jamvinji.
lujvo x1=c1 is a musical instrument played by x2=c3. Cf. zgike, cabra.
lujvo f1 is a musical event with music x2=z1 performed/produced by x3=z2 (event).
lujvo f1 composes music f2=z1 for purpose f3.
lujvo x1=z2=g1 is a band that has members x2 and plays music x3=z1. See also zgike, girzu
lujvo k1 is a music note (tone). Cf. zgike, kantu, zgika'usni.
lujvo s1 is a music note (symbol). Cf. zgike, kantu, sinxa, zgika'u, zgica'a.
lujvo k1 is a glass harp/musical glass, performed by z2 (event).

gismu rafsi: zgi gi'e x1 is music performed/produced by x2 (event). x2 event may be person playing instrument, singing, musical source operating/vibrating, etc.; instrument (= zgica'a); play an instrument (= zgica'apli, zgiterca'a, selzgigau, selzgizu'e); song (= sagzgi, selsa'a); voice, as used musically (= zgivo'a); composed music (= finzgi). See also damri, dansu, flani, janbe, jgita, pipno, rilti, tabra, tonga, xagri, siclu.
lujvo x1=p1 plays x3=z1 on x2=p2 see also zgitci, zgica'a
fu'ivla x1 is a form of pop music performed by x2 with characteristics x3. Cf. te'ekno, zgike, sanga.
lujvo f2=z1 is a musical composition composed by f1for function/purpose f3 from existing elements/ideas f4. Cf. zgike, finti, zgifi'i, simfoni, konceto.
lujvo s1 is musicology with methodology s2.
lujvo t1 is a music instrument used for producing sound t2=z1. Cf. zgike, tutci.
fu'ivla x1 is a damselfly of species x2. Cf. ansoptera, odnata, laxsfani, sfani, cinki.
cmavo ZI time tense distance: instantaneous-to-short distance in time.
cmavo ZIhE joins relative clauses which apply to the same sumti.
lujvo j1 is the right for z1 to do z2 (event/state). Cf. zifre, javni, selzi'e, nunzi'e, kamyzi'e, rarzi'ejva, prezi'ejva.
lujvo z1=b1 becomes free to do/be x2 (event/state) under conditions x3. Cf. zifre, binxo.
lujvo v1 is a fu'ivla-form word meaning v2 (in Lojban); v1 is morphologically a fu'ivla. Generalization of fu'ivla to include non-borrowings; specialization of fu'ivla to exclude non-Lojban words.
lujvo j1 is the right for z1 to do z2 (event/state). Cf. zifre, javni, selzi'e, nunzi'e, kamyzi'e, rarzi'ejva, prezi'ejva.
cmavo rafsi: zil KOhA7 pro-sumti: fills a sumti place, deleting it from selbri place structure;changes selbri semantics.
lujvo x1 releases x2 to do/be x3 under conditions x4. Cf. zifre, curmi, toljgari.

gismu rafsi: zif zi'e x1 is free/at liberty to do/be x2 (event/state) under conditions x3. Also unrestricted, unfettered, unconstrained; (adjective:) independent; (adverb:) willingly, voluntarily, freely, may, optionally; (potential:) x1 voluntarily does x2. See also pinfu, rinju, bilga, curmi, kakne, frili.
lujvo z1=j1 is a sovereign state having supreme, independent authority over j2 (people/territory). Cf. jecta.
fu'ivla z1 is a line with the shape of a zigzag.
lujvo x1=d1 is information gathered/produced by method/from source x2=d3. not necessarily meaningful or about anything
lujvo f2 (ka) is an ordinary / common / general / typical / usual property among f3. Made of zi'o + fadni. See also kampu for the fully-universal sense.
lujvo x1 numbers/adds up to/consists of x2 (number) counting by units x3; x1 are x2 in number.
lujvo x1 has probability x2 of occurring. See also cu'o, la'erlai
lujvo t1 is a tanru component. Cf. tanru, zi'o, seltau, tertau.
fu'ivla x1 is Zimbabwean in aspect x2. see also zimbabues
fu'ivla x1 is ginger of species x2. see also kurkuma, glangala
gismu rafsi: zin zi'i x1 is a quantity of/contains/is made of zinc (Zn); [metaphor: hard metal]. See also jinme.
lujvo x1=dzipo1=cipni1 is a penguin of species x2=cipni2.
lujvo d1=t1 is Antarctica from dzipo tumla c.f.zdotu'a rontu'a tcotu'a sralytu'a frikytu'a bemtu'a
gismu rafsi: zir zi'u x1 is purple/violet [color adjective]. See also skari, blabi, xekri, kandi, carmi, nukni, blanu, xunre.
lujvo x1 is a plum [fruit] of species/variety x2 Cf. smela
lujvo x1=z1 is crimson/carmine/ruby/cerise/deep red. Cf. zirpu, xunre.

gismu rafsi: ziv vle x1 (agent) invests resources x2 in investment x3 expecting return/profit x4 (object(s)/event). [also ties up/Risks/gambles. x1 is an investor; x2 are invested assets of x1; bond (= jertervle)]; See also prali, canja, jbera, dejni, ponse.
gismu rafsi: zma mau x1 exceeds/is more than x2 in property/quantity x3 (ka/ni) by amount/excess x4. Also positive (= nonmau). See also cmavo list mau, mleca, zenba, jmina, bancu, dukse, traji.
lujvo x1 is greater than or equal to x2 in property/quantity x3 by amount/excess x4. See also su'o
lujvo z1=n1 is a positive number relative to origo z2. Cf. ni'u, nonmecna'u, fatna'u, mecna'u, nonmau, ma'u.
lujvo n1 prefers n2=z1 over z2, because of property/quantity z3, by margin z4. Cf. zmazau.
gismu rafsi: zmi x1 is automatic in function x2 under conditions x3. See also macnu.
cmavo ZO quote next word only; quotes a single Lojban word (not a cmavo compound or tanru).
cmavo rafsi: zon zo'a FAhA4 location tense relation/direction; tangential to/passing by ...
cmavo KOhA7 pro-sumti: an elliptical/unspecified value; has some value which makes bridi true.
cmavo rafsi: zor zo'i FAhA4 location tense relation/direction; nearer than .../inward/approaching from ...
cmavo UI5 attitudinal modifier: humorously - dully - seriously. See also xajmi, junri.
cmavo cluster BY* letteral: humor symbol, ":-)" and its related forms expressing humor (letteral).
cmavo cluster UI*5 attitudinal modifier: humorously - dully - seriously.
cmavo cluster UI*5 attitudinal modifier: humorously - dully - seriously.
cmavo ZOhU marks end of logical prenex quantifiers/topic identification and start of sentence bridi.
cmavo ZOI delimited non-Lojban quotation; the result treated as a block of text.
cmavo ZI time tense distance: long distance in time.
cmavo FAhA2 location tense relation/direction; leftwards/to the left of ...
cmavo BAI zukte modal, 1st place (purposed agent) with goal-seeking actor ...
lujvo z1=d1 intends/wishes to do z2=d2 for z3=d3.
cmavo KOhA7 pro-sumti: the typical sumti value for this place in this relationship; affects truth value.
cmavo rafsi: zum NU1 abstractor: activity (event) abstractor; x1 is abstract activity of [bridi] composed of x2.
cmavo UI3 discursive: on the one hand - on the other hand. See also karbi, frica, dukti
cmavo cluster UI*3 discursive: on the one hand - on the other hand.
lujvo r1=z1 is busy doing z2 for purpose/goal z3. Cf. zukte, ricfu, tolcando.
lujvo z1=p1 is a volitional thinker consdering taking action z2=p2 toward end/goal z3 cf. zukte, pensi, bavgaupei
lujvo p2=z2 is a policy of p3=z3 (nu) prescribed by p1.
lujvo s1=z1 honors s2 with action z2.
lujvo t1 is the manner of action t2=z2 under condition t3. Cf. tadji, zukte.
lujvo m1=z1 is [busy doing]/[working hard at] z2 for purpose/goal z3. Cf. zukte, mutce.

gismu rafsi: zuk zu'e x1 is a volitional entity employing means/taking action x2 for purpose/goal x3/to end x3. Also acting at, undertaking, doing; agentive cause with volition/purpose; also x3 objective, end. See also cmavo list zu'e, bapli, gunka, jalge, krinu, mukti, rinka, snuti, gasnu, fasnu, minji, prenu, ciksi, jibri, pilno, pluta, tadji, tutci.
lujvo s1 gives advice z2 to s3=z1. Cf. stidi, ctuca, friti, kajde.

lujvo c1=t1=z1 is the executive branch of the government of people/territory/domain/subjects t2 of organizational type c2 with components c3. Cf. zukte, turni, ciste, truci'e, flatruci'e, pairtruci'e, flacfatrugri, flazautrugri, vajraifla.
lujvo b1=z1 goes jogging on surface b2 for purpose z3. To run volitionally and steadily, especially for exercise.
lujvo k1 has volition/is a volitional entity.
lujvo xa1=z1 is a/the left hand of xa2=z2, which faces/in-frame-of-reference z3. Cf. prityxa'e.
gismu rafsi: zmu x1 is a quantity of maize/corn [grain] of species/strain x2. See also gurni.
gismu rafsi: zug x1 feels guilt/remorse about x2 (abstraction). (cf. cmavo list .u'u, cinmo, xenru, zekri)

gismu rafsi: zul x1 is to the left/left-hand side of x2 which faces/in-frame-of-reference x3. Also x3 is the standard of orientation for x2. See also cmavo list zu'a, pritu, mlana, crane, trixe, farna.
lujvo s1 is a consonant sound made by articulation z1 (event/state).

gismu rafsi: zun zu'i x1 (evt./state) interferes with/hinders/disrupts x2 (evt./state/process) due to quality x3 (ka). Also blocks, obstructs, baffles; not necessarily forcing cessation. See also fanta, dicra, fliba, fanza, raktu, klina, bandu, cfipu, ganlo.
gismu rafsi: zut tse x1 sits [assumes sitting position] on surface x2. See also stizu, cpana, vreta.
lujvo c1 requests/invites z1=c3 [to attend]/[be present at] z2 (event/location) in manner/form c4. Cf. zvati, cpedu, vi'ecpe.
lujvo x1=facki1 finds/locates x2=zvati1=facki3 (object) at x3=zvati2 (event/location) (= tolcri) See zvati, facki.
lujvo l1 is a list/catalog/register of objects/events l2=z1 (sequence/set) present at/attending x3=z2 (event/location).

gismu rafsi: zva x1 (object/event) is at/attending/present at x2 (event/location). Atemporal; location equivalent of cabna. Refers to a nonce location for an object/activity that is mobile. (cf. especially stuzi for an inherent/inalienable location, jbini, nenri, se vasru, cpana, diklo, jibni, cabna, lamji, tcini, xabju, jmive, jundi, vitke)
